column19: Kaiten Mail is a gorgeous and incredibly powerful email client for Android. Note: This app is not compatible with Asus Transformer devices (except the TF101). Affected customers please contact support@kaitenmail.com to receive a refund. ★★★ Features ★★★ • Supports multiple IMAP, POP3, Exchange 2003/2007 (via WebDAV) accounts • Push mail using IMAP IDLE • Rich text editing • Unified Inbox • Display contact pictures • Threaded message view • Split-screen view • Email signatures • BCC to self • Rich notifications (mark as read, reply, or delete directly from notifications) • Encrypt and sign messages using the OpenPGP standard (when APG is installed) • Settings import/export • Keyboard shortcuts • Lots of configuration options Please note that Kaiten currently does NOT support Exchange ActiveSync. ★★★ Use Kaiten for free ★★★ If you want to try Kaiten out for free (or just use it forever for free) try out the ad-supported version here: http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kaitenmail.adsupported ★★★ Support ★★★ If you're having trouble with Kaiten, drop us a line and we'll do everything we can to help you out. We'd love to hear how you'd like Kaiten to improve. Join us at http://kaitenmail.uservoice.com/ ★★★ Kaiten's origin ★★★ Kaiten is based on the popular open source app K-9 Mail and was built by K-9's lead developers Jesse and Chris. By buying Kaiten you not only get an awesome email client, you also support the open source version because almost all of the new features are contributed to K-9 Mail. The name is a play on K-9. Kaiten is a Japanese word that means rotation and sounds a lot like K10 or K-10.

Одоогийн бидний ашиглаж байгаа уламжлалт харилцаа холбооны шийдлүүд нь байгууллагын ажилтнууд хоорондоо мэдээлэл дамжуулан солилцохын тулд хэд хэдэн төхөөрөмж, дугаарлалт, и-мэйл хаягуудыг зэрэг ашигладгаас гадна олон ажилтантай томоохон байгууллагын удирдлага болон ажилтнууд хоорондоо холбогдохын тулд тэдгээр олон утасны дугаарыг заавал мэддэг байх гэх мэт хүндрэлүүд тулгардаг. Тэгвэл энэ бүгдийг хялбарчлан нэг дор цогцоор нь ашиглах боломжийг “Mobile Office” үйлчилгээ та бүхэнд олгох болно. Үйлчилгээний нэмэлт боломжууд • Mobility- Суурин утсанд ирсэн дуудлагыг гар утсандаа хүлээн авах ба гадагшаа дуудлага хийнэ. • Fax messaging - Өөрт ирсэн факсаа гар утас, компьютертаа и-мэйлээр хүлээн авна. • Voice messaging- Дуут мессежээ гар утас, компьютертаа и-мэйлээр хүлээн авч сонсоно. • Meet Me conference - Тусгайлан үүсгэсэн хурлын өрөөний дугаарт залган телефон хурал хийнэ. • Three way call- 2 хүн ярьж байх үедээ 3 дагч этгээдийг урьж зэрэг яриа хийнэ. • Group Hunting- Гаднаас ирсэн дуудлаганд хариу өгөхгүй үед байгууллагын бусад ажилтанд ээлжлэн дуудлага очно. • Call forward- Суурин утасны дугаарт ирэх дуудлагыг өөр дугаарт тохируулан хүлээн авна. • Call transfer- Яриа хийж байх үедээ дуудлагыг өөр дугаарт дамжуулан олбож өгөх боломжтой. • Call pull- Дуудлагаа таслалгүйгээр өөр төхөөрөмж рүү шижүүлэн яриагаа үргэлжлүүлэн хийх боломж. (Жишээ нь: Та ширээн дээрээ суурин утсаараа ярьж байгаад гадагш гарах бол дуудлагаа таслалгүйгээр гар утсаараа үргэлжлүүлэн яриа хийх боломжтой. • Short number dialing- Байгууллагын ажилчид хоорондоо дуудлага хийхдээ 3 оронтой дотуур дугаараар залгах боломжтой. • Call through- Wi-fi болон 3G сүлжээ муутай газраас интернэтийн сүлжээнээс үл хамааран GSM сүлжээгээрээ чанартай яриа хийх боломжтой. Энэ тохиолдолд ярианы тариф таны үүрэн холбооны дугаарын бусад сүлжээнд ярих тарифаар тооцогдох бөгөөд дуудлага авч буй хэрэглэгчид таны суурин утасны дугаар харагдах болно. • Instant messenger – Зөвхөн байгууллагын ажилтнуудад зориулсан дотуур холбооны програмаар чат хийх, файл дамжуулах боломжтой. • Web conference- Вэб хуудас ашиглан хоорондоо онлайн хурал хийх боломжтой. Одоогийнбиднийашиглажбайгаауламжлалтхарилцаахолбоонышийдлүүдньбайгууллагынажилтнуудхоорондоомэдээлэлдамжуулансолилцохынтулдхэдхэдэнтөхөөрөмж，дугаарлалт，И-мэйлхаягуудыгзэрэгашигладгаасгаднаолонажилтантайтомоохонбайгууллагынудирдлагаболонажилтнуудхоорондоохолбогдохынтулдтэдгээролонутасныдугаарыгзаавалмэддэгбайхгэхмэтхүндрэлүүдтулгардаг 。 Тэгвэлэнэбүгдийгхялбарчланнэгдорцогцоорньашиглахболомжийг“移动办公”үйлчилгээтабүхэндолгохболно。 Үйлчилгээнийнэмэлтболомжууд •移动Сууринутсандирсэндуудлагыггарутсандаахүлээнавахбагадагшаадуудлагахийнэ。 •传真消息 - Өөртирсэнфаксаагарутас，компьютертааимэйлээрхүлээнавна。 •语音消息Дуутмессежээгарутас，компьютертааимэйлээрхүлээнавчсонсоно。 •我见面发布会 - Тусгайланүүсгэсэнхурлынөрөөнийдугаартзалгантелефонхуралхийнэ。 •三方通话2хүнярьжбайхүедээ3дагчэтгээдийгурьжзэрэгяриахийнэ。 •集团狩猎Гаднаасирсэндуудлагандхариуөгөхгүйүедбайгууллагын其他应用ажилтандээлжлэндуудлагаочно。 •呼叫转移Сууринутасныдугаартирэхдуудлагыгөөрдугаарттохирууланхүлээнавна。 •呼叫转移Яриахийжбайхүедээдуудлагыгөөрдугаартдамжууланолбожөгөхболомжтой。 •呼叫拉Дуудлагаатаслалгүйгээрөөртөхөөрөмжрүүшижүүлэняриагааүргэлжлүүлэнхийхболомж。 （Жишээнь：Таширээндээрээсууринутсаарааярьжбайгаадгадагшгарахболдуудлагаатаслалгүйгээргарутсаарааүргэлжлүүлэняриахийхболомжтой。 •短号码拨号Байгууллагынажилчидхоорондоодуудлагахийхдээ3оронтойдотуурдугаараарзалгахболомжтой。 •呼叫通过无线网络连接болон3GсүлжээмуутайгазраасинтернэтийнсүлжээнээсүлхамааранGSMсүлжээгээрээчанартайяриахийхболомжтой。 Энэтохиолдолдярианытарифтаныүүрэнхолбооныдугаарынбусадсүлжээндярихтарифаартооцогдохбөгөөддуудлагаавчбуйхэрэглэгчидтанысууринутасныдугаархарагдахболно。 •即时使者 - Зөвхөнбайгууллагынажилтнуудадзориулсандотуурхолбооныпрограмаарчатхийх，файлдамжуулахболомжтой。 •Web会议Вэбхуудасашигланхоорондооонлайнхуралхийхболомжтой。

MIAR is an Augmented Reality demo application from Mobinett Interactive, Inc. To use the application go to http://www.mobinett.com/ar , scan demo targets and watch the App in action. Statistics indicate that by the year 2015, there will be almost 1.5 billion downloads of mobile Augmented Reality applications to smart phones, tablets and other mobile devices. Our AR solution can be used in several domains such as Retail, Museums, Education, Healthcare and Magazines. This technology brings real world objects to life, making them more relevant, interactive and engaging. A user walking down an aisle at the supermarket, a museum or reading a magazine, can with one tap open AR in the App, scan the object of interest with phone's camera and get a wealth of information on the products - reviews, videos, price comparison, nutritional statistics - highly targeted to the user based on their location, interests and past usage. There is also social integration allowing users to share with their friends. MIAR is available as an SDK on iOS and Android. MIAR dashboard provides a rich set of analytics on how and where users are interacting with the technology. To find out more or to request an account go to http://www.mobinett.com/ar or contact us at contact@mobinett.com Create interactive and engaging experiences with MIAR today!! MIAR是一个增强现实（Augmented Reality）的演示应用程序要使用该应用程序去到http://www.mobinett.com/ar，演示扫描目标并观看行动的App从Mobinett Interactive公司。 统计数据表明，到2015年，将有近150亿下载的移动增强现实（Augmented Reality）应用到智能手机，平板电脑和其他移动设备。 我们的AR解决方案，可用于在一些领域，如零售，博物馆，教育，医疗保健和杂志。这项技术带来的现实世界中对象的生活，使他们更具有针对性，互动性和吸引力。走在超市的过道的用户，一个博物馆或者读一本杂志，可以用1水龙头打开AR在App，扫描感兴趣的对象，用手机的摄像头，并获得丰富的产品信息 - 评论，视频，价格相比之下，营养统计 - 具有高度针对性的根据自己的定位，利益和过去使用的用户。也有社会融合，让用户与他们的朋友分享。 MIAR可作为iOS和Android上的SDK。 MIAR仪表板提供了一套丰富的用户如何以及在哪里与技术互动的分析。要了解更多信息或申请帐户http://www.mobinett.com/ar的或联系我们contact@mobinett.com 创建互动性和引人入胜的经验与今天MIAR！！

The Android SIP Client is the latest offering by AdoreSoftphone that makes entry into the android apps stores. This newly developed Android VoIP Mobile Dialer enables any Android based mobile phone to make VoIP call by using the internet connection. It is especially developed with keeping the requirements of VoIP service providers in mind that’s why Android SIP Client can easily integrate itself with any of the SIP servers. Other new and advance features are also going to make this android app likeable to mobile users as well. By integrating and registering with SIP server, Android SIP Client let user make calls without any fuzz. It is compatible with all the latest android based mobile devices. Give your android mobile the power of VoIP calling with Android SIP Client. Features:- * Customized with company name / logo * User Friendly, Advanced and Smoother GUI * Multi Language (OS Specific) * Unlimited user license * SIP protocol support * Making and receiving calls * Codecs supported:g729 g711,GSM,g722,iLBC * Advanced Phone Book (Contact manager with name number,profile pic and searching ) * Recording * call hold * call transfer * Call Log * Call Status Indicator * Save / Edit Username & Password * Work with all standard SIP SoftSwitches * Android 1.5, 1.6, 2.x, 3.x, 4.x, 5.x * Silence Suppression * Echo Cancellation * Auto Registration and Timeout * Proxy support Android的SIP客户端是AdoreSoftphone的最新产品，可进入Android应用商店。这种新开发的Andr​​oid的VoIP手机拨号器使得任何基于Android的手机使用互联网连接，使VoIP呼叫。它特别与保持VoIP服务提供商的记的要求，这就是为什么机器人的SIP客户端可以很容易地与任何的SIP服务器的本身集成开发的。其他新的和先进的功能也将会使这个Android应用程序可爱的移动用户为好。通过整合和SIP服务器上注册，Android的SIP客户端，让用户做出没有任何模糊的呼叫。它与所有最新的基于Android的移动设备兼容。给你的Andr​​oid手机网络电话的电源要求与Android的SIP客户端。 特征：- *定制公司名称/标志 *用户友好，高级和更流畅的图形用户界面 *多语言（OS专用） *无限用户许可 *支持SIP协议 *拨打和接听电话 *编解码器支持：G729 G711，GSM，G722，iLBC的 *先进的电话簿（含名称数量，轮廓PIC和搜索联系人管理器）         * 记录 *呼叫保持 *呼叫转移 * 通话记录 *呼叫状态指示灯 *保存/编辑用户名和密码 *与所有标准的SIP软交换工作 *的Andr​​oid 1.5，1.6，2.X，3.X，4.x版，5.x的 *静音抑制 *回声消除 *自动登记和超时 *代理支持

column8: 休闲-益智休闲-可爱-经营策略-僵尸-逃脱-男生最爱-外星人
column19: 嗨，伙计！准备好你的手指去抠动扳机吧！ 《牛仔与僵尸》的故事背景为狂野西部，综合了角色扮演，即时战略和动作过关游戏的要素，创造出独一无二的游戏体验。现在就开始体验，《牛仔与僵尸》，免费玩！ 帕姆敦镇的恐惧 欢迎来到北美大草原上的宁静小镇帕姆敦，这里聚集着简陋的小屋和各种悲苦境况，流浪的旅人来到这里会寻找到一点点希望，许许多多的麻烦，偶尔，会得到去见上帝的单程票。在肮脏昏暗的酒吧里，枪支商店里，或是畜栏之中… … 我们发现了赏金猎人贾科尔的身影，那些行走在帕姆敦的泥泞道路上的受雇枪手中的一位。然而今天这将是一个全然不同的故事。 老掘墓人罗梅罗这样描绘当时的场景：“埋骨地的那些死了八百年的家伙们从土里爬了出来！他们站起来然后互相啃咬，好像饿得可以吃下一个马鞍！” 死者已然复生。 绝非你司空见惯的射击游戏 在小镇中散布开来，恐怖的僵尸们追逐着他们的受害者。惊惶，恐惧和恐怖遍布在帕姆敦。动物和鸟类的腐尸也随即加入人形僵尸的队伍。各种死物行走在帕姆敦，渴望着鲜血。 与此同时，赏金猎人贾科尔正在深夜的酒吧里虚度时光，陪伴他的只有酒保简。当尖叫声骤起，俩人如风般冲出酒吧，枪已上膛。 无暇顾及生死的狂野战斗 帕姆敦马上就要被僵尸占据，但是贾科尔可以挽救一切！指挥着头牌赏金猎人和他乱糟糟的蓝莓小队去和僵尸们战斗，保卫帕姆敦。这可不是一个简单的任务，但是你可以雇佣各种各样的家伙，让乞丐、迷途旅人、冒险者和孤独的牛仔加入你的队伍！ 你将操控贾科尔，简和其他的角色扫射着视野内所有的僵尸！根据角色的不同，你可以射击、捅、砍、刺、砸、切、钻，或是把僵尸炸个稀烂。去酒吧里可以雇佣到帮手。获取经验值然后在训练师那里学习新技能。在铁匠处可以获得更好的武器和装备。把帕姆敦从这场大混乱中挽救出来，你的枪够快吗？ 游戏特点 - 狂野西部的绝妙场景 - 高质量的漫画画风 - 综合角色扮演，即时战略和经典的街机动作过关游戏，让人上瘾的玩法 - 四个队友；多种职业可供选择 - 在酒吧里可以雇佣新角色 - 花费经验值可以在训练师那些学到新技能 - 在铁匠那里可以替换和升级武器装备 - 每日“抽奖箱” 活动，可以获得各种免费服务 - 有38 个不同的关卡，你在其中或是逃脱、或是捅死、射杀僵尸 - 39 个成就等待着你去完成。 ** 注意：即便该程式为免费下载，请留意，用户依个人意愿想提高他们的游戏经验而购买的礼包是需要以真实货币付费的。您可设定密码管控本应用程式内的购买行为，密码保护功能可于 Google Play 商店的设定页面上开启。**

column8: 趣味-经典-关卡-修改版-技巧
column19: 一款充满乐趣而又与众不同的游戏，看起来，它像是一款赛车类的游戏，其实不然，这款游戏更侧重的是平衡感方面。游戏的主角是一个住在养老院的老奶奶，但是在养老院的生活实在是太枯燥了，终于，趁着医护人员的不注意，老奶奶偷偷的骑上了一辆机车，开始了自己的冒险运动。游戏看起来很简单，其实不然，老奶奶的车子稍不注意就会翻掉了，所以，你必须要小心的控制，速度不能太快。游戏的操作方式非常简单，通过触摸屏进行控制，按屏幕左边是后退，按右边是前进，上坡的时候注意控制好车速，否则你下坡的时候会翻车的。游戏总体上来说，非常好玩，而且题材新颖，给人幽默的感觉，只是看着游戏中老奶奶不停的摔跟头，真是替她担心啊！游戏解锁完整，快来体验吧。

Don't look any further! This app will automatically remember where you parked your car and help you find it. It is different from all the other car locator apps out there because if your car is equipped with a factory or aftermarket hands-free Bluetooth device, this app will automatically save your parked location whenever you leave your vehicle! Don't worry, if you don't have Bluetooth in your car, you can still manually save your currently parked location via a simple drag and drop operation. No hassle, just straight to the point. Please like us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/pinnfind Reviews: http://www.mobileappsgallery.com/free-android-apps/1908/pin-n-find-car-finder/ NOTE: Please make sure your GPS is turned on, and make sure to specify your in-vehicle Bluetooth device (if you have one) under the app’s options menu. Accuracy of your parked location may vary between devices, due to the quality of GPS signal Features: - Straightforward interface: Just drag the pin down to manually save your parked location. Cloud Computing Interview Questions provides you a wide range of questions that can be asked during a Interview. Application answers most commonly asked interview questions and has been categories for ease. This app is unique in that it helps you master the most commonly asked questions for Cloud Computing, instilling you with the confidence that you need to endure the most difficult of interviews. Application covers all Wide range of question covering different aspects of Cloud Computing. If you want to buy the source Code contact us on admin@programmerworld.net Features: 1. 125+ questions that prepare you for any type of interview. 2. The Question are ACTUAL questions asked in some of the regular interviews that the likes of Accenture, IBM and many other. 3. Provide an option for user to practice his/her own answers as your application will present your with question. User can think of his answer then compare how his answer is different from our answer. 4. Interview Questions has been categories for ease of use. Categories: Application Cover questions from Following 7 broad Categories. 1. Cloud Computing 2. Introduction to Cloud Computing 3. Cloud Computing Architecture 4. Cloud computing – Amazon 5. MapReduce 6. Ubuntu Cloud 7. Windows Azure SAMPLE QUESTIONS Q. ) What is the relationship between SOA and cloud architecture? Ans: Service oriented architecture (SOA) is an architectural style that supports service oriented methodology that is being added in the cloud architecture as a mandatory component. Cloud architecture support the use of on-demand access to resources and it provides lots of other facilities that are being found in SOA as well. SOA makes these requirements optional to use. But, to get the full functionality and more performance based efficiency there is a requirement for the mixture of SOA and cloud architecture. Q.) Can I vertically scale an Amazon instance? How? An : Yes. This is an incredible feature of AWS and cloud virtualization. Spinup a new larger instance than the one you are currently running. Pause that instance and detach the root ebs volume from this server and discard. Then stop your live instance, detach its root volume. Note the unique device ID and attach that root volume to your new server. And the start it again. Voila you have scaled vertically in-place!! 云计算的面试问题，为您提供范围广泛的问题，可以在一次采访中问。回答最常见的面试问题，并一直为便于分类。 这个应用程序是独一无二的，它可以帮助你掌握云计算的最常见的问题，灌输你的信心，你需要忍受的最艰难的采访。应用程序涵盖了所有的问题范围广，覆盖云计算的不同方面。 如果你想购买的源代码，请联系我们ad​​min@programmerworld.net 产品特点： 1。 125 +的问题，为您准备任何类型的面试。 2。问题是实际的定期会面中提出的问题，像埃森哲，IBM和许多其他。 3。为用户提供一个选项，练习他/她自己的答案，你的申请将出示您的问题。用户可以想到他的回答，然后比较如何从我们的答案，他的答案是不同的。 4。面试问题已经类别的易用性。 类别： 应用程序包括从以下7大类问题。 1。云计算 2。云计算简介 3。云计算架构 4。云计算 - 亚马逊 5。 MapReduce的 6。 Ubuntu的云 7。 Windows Azure的 样题 Q.）架构SOA和云计算之间的关系是什么？ 答：面向服务的架构（SOA）是一种架构风格，它支持面向服务的方法为强制性的成分被添加在云架构。云架构，支持按需获取资源的使用，它提供了大量，被发现在SOA和其他设施。 SOA使这些要求选择使用。但是，要获得完整的功能和更高的性能基于效率是有要求的混合物SOA和云架构。 Q.）我可以垂直缩放Amazon实例吗？怎么样？ 安：是的。这是一个令人难以置信的AWS和云计算虚拟化功能。升速一新的更大的比你当前正在运行的实例。暂停实例，并从该服务器并丢弃分离的根EBS卷的。然后停止你的生活实例，分离其根卷。请注意，唯一的设备ID，根体积和附加到新的服务器。而重新启动它。瞧你垂直缩放的地方！

A telephone, or phone, is a telecommunications device that permits two or more users to conduct a conversation when they are not in the same vicinity of each other to be heard directly. A telephone converts sound, typically and most efficiently the human voice, into electronic signals suitable for transmission via cables or other transmission media over long distances, and replays such signals simultaneously in audible form to its user. The word telephone has been adapted into the vocabulary of many languages. A ringtone or ring tone is the sound made by a telephone to indicate an incoming call or text message. Not literally a tone nor an actual (bell-like) ring anymore, the term is most often used today to refer to customizable sounds used on mobile phones. A video ringtone is a piece of video content used as a ringtone (typically on 3G phones). Any video may be used, but usually music video excerpts are used. The best examples of these use sound and video track that loops seamlessly. It is possible to use personalised video ringtones against contacts in the phone to provide video and audio Caller Identification. An alarm clock is a clock that is designed to wake a person at a specific time. The primary use of these clocks is to awaken people from their night's sleep or short naps; they are sometimes used for other reminders as well. Some use sound, some use light, and some use sensors to identify when a person is in a light stage of sleep, in order to avoid waking someone when they're deeply asleep, which causes tiredness, even if the person has gotten adequate sleep. To stop the sound or light, a button or handle on the clock is pressed; but most clocks automatically stop the alarm if left unattended long enough. The Wood Pole Guide app provides critical information needed to properly specify and use treated wood poles. Explore the preservatives used to treat wood poles available in the market today, as well as the AWPA Use Category standards that set the required retention for poles base on their use. Also featured are Technical Bulletins providing design and engineering information for wood poles, as well as case histories documenting the performance of wood poles. Users can review reports on the service life of wood poles, current lifecycle research and recommendations for protecting wildlife near wood poles. The Engineering Tools section features an ANSI Dimension Calculator that can determine the circumference 6 ft. from the butt end of the pole, based on the species, length, minimum top circumference and class. The Pole Weight Estimator provides the range of weights for each species, based on the length and class of the pole. In both utilities, users can select the criteria and search for the specific pole desired. Utilities, engineers and others can utilize the app to make informed decisions on specifying wood poles for their specific need and area. A directory provides contact information for the leading treated pole and cross arm manufacturers in the U.S. and Canada. The app is produced by the North American Wood Pole Council, representing wood pole producers in the West, the South and Canada.

Java是Java程序设计语言和Java平台的总称。用Java实现的HotJava浏览器（支持Java applet）显示了Java的魅力：跨平台、动态的Web、Internet计算。从此，Java被广泛接受并推动了Web的迅速发展，常用的浏览器现在均支持Java applet。Java平台由Java虚拟机（Java Virtual Machine）和Java 应用编程接口（Application Programming Interface、简称API）构成。Java 应用编程接口为Java应用提供了一个独立于操作系统的标准接口，可分为基本部分和扩展部分。在硬件或操作系统平台上安装一个Java平台之后，Java应用程序就可运行。现在Java平台已经嵌入了几乎所有的操作系统。这样Java程序可以只编译一次，就可以在各种系统中运行。

的声音，帮助你放松，睡得更好。不同的风的声音（天籁）帮助您和您的孩子更快入睡。我们的自然音乐应用进程后，风的声音： 风的摇篮曲 暴风雪舒缓的音乐 声雨 雷雨旋律 大雨的声音 我们的音乐应用进程： +只有自然的音乐，没有乐器，白噪声 +放松和睡眠的声音和铃声！ +高品质的声音，鸟儿的歌唱，在热带雨林 +海浪的声音自然，咆哮的海浪，海洋的声音 +天然降雨的声音，瀑布，夜丛林 +自然的水流声 +放松铃声 +自然音乐 +舒缓的音乐 - 睡眠的声音 +绝对放松 +自然的声音放松和睡眠 +白噪声宝宝的睡眠 “+”治疗音乐（音乐疗法，声音疗法，旋律疗法） +质量最好的好水声，海的声音，海浪的声音，雨的声音 - 天籁 +你会放松，像婴儿睡觉 +儿童立即入睡 +摇篮曲的性质 +深度放松 我们的环境的特点听起来Android应用进程： - 安装“天籁放松和睡眠”，以SD卡 - 性质不同声音（包括水声，雨的声音，丛林，海的声音） - 倒计时音乐放松疗法 - 美丽的壁纸中的每个声音的性质 - 冥想音乐在后台运行 - 有助于摆脱耳鸣的 - 为人类的大脑放松 - 只有良好的质量自然睡眠的声音 - 放松旋律样本 - 最好的放松的声音性质的免费应用 - 超级天然水的声音（无音乐） - 性质噪音制造者（声音效果来电铃声） - 本赛季的声音 - 城市的声音 - 游戏中的声音 - 周围的声音 风是流动的气体进行了大规模的。在地球上，风是由大量的空气流动。在太空中，太阳风是流动的气体或来自太阳的带电粒子穿过空间，而行星风系的放气，光从一颗行星的大气层进入太空的化学元素。风速：通常分为空间尺度，他们的速度，类型，这使得它们的力量，它们发生的地区，他们的影响。观察到最强的风出现在我们的太阳系的行星海王星和土星。 一个的催眠曲是一个舒缓的歌曲，唱年轻的孩子，才去睡觉，加速这一过程中的意图。因此，他们往往是简单而重复的。可以发现在每一种文化和古代时期以来摇篮曲。 许多的摇篮曲是在三米，或在复合米像6/8。音调，最摇篮曲很简单，往往只是交流的滋补和占主导地位的和声：由于预期的效果是把一个人睡觉，野生音阶的性格会有些。 被设计成催眠曲的婴儿耶稣，其中最有名的是“平安夜”圣诞颂歌。 自然，在最广泛的意义上，是等同于自然世界，物理世界，物质世界。 “自然”是指物理世界的现象，同时也为一般的生活。它的范围从亚原子到宇宙规模。 人们用自然的声音，放松的技巧，是由于以下原因，其中包括： 愤怒管理（冲浪轰鸣声，大海，水流，海浪在沙滩上的声音，海洋，雨的声音） 心脏健康（热带雨林的声音，鸟儿的歌唱） 抑郁症的治疗（鸟的声音，瑜伽音乐，白噪声的应用进程） 睡前歌曲和睡前的声音 总体幸福感（在海滩上的波浪，丛林声音） 头痛治疗（鸟叫声，海浪的声音） 血压高（冲浪，瀑布轰鸣的声音，白噪声）

DTS Software's popular z/OS Pocket Reference Guide finally makes its way to the app market. Useful information for mainframe programmers, administrators, and others is now even more easily available. New in Version 3.0.5: Fixed Jeffrey Harder's mystery crash thanks to his generous aid in the debugging process, thanks! New in Version 3.0.4: Fixed orientation change crash (click article > change orientation > hit back > crash). Still tracking down Jeffrey Harder's crash. New in Version 3.0.3: Fixed the white screen on exit, necessitating an extra back hit, still tracking down a null pointer encountered by one user New in version 3.0.2: Well that'll teach me not to put fixes in late at night, the crash on boot is fixed now. Thanks to the several of you who reported it! New in version 3.0.1: Fixed a crash occurring when switching orientations (crash reporter Steve Pryor) New in Version 3.0: Fixed a significant amount of back end code, support for tablet reading now. Default theme changed (it's easier on the eyes now). Updated to parity with the latest paper copy of the pocket reference guide, new information. Some of the formatting on the text in pages may have changed (if it doesn't look right to you, let DTS support know) New in Version 2.2: Fixed a small problem with the EBCDIC-to-Hex conversion chart. Thanks to John Clifford for the catch! New in Version 2.1: Fixed an error in the DASD Calculator's blocks per track calculation that was brought to our attention by an astute attendee at SHARE (send me your name and I will put it here). This should not have impacted users in a meaningful way, but check to be sure. The error resulted in the blocks per track being 1 off in some cases, which may have added another track to the space calculation. Again thank you for your continued support. If there's anything else you would like to see in the guide, please contact us! DTS的软件的流行z / OS的袖珍参考手册终于使得它的方式对应用程序市场。大型机的程序员，系统管理员，以及其他有用的信息，现在更容易获得。 新的版本3.0.5：修复杰弗里·哈德的奥秘崩溃感谢他的慷慨援助，在调试过程中，非常感谢！ 新的版本3.0.4：固定方向变化的崩溃（点击文章>改变方向>反击>崩溃）。仍追查杰弗里·哈德的崩溃。 新的版本3.0.3：修复了退出白屏，迫使一个额外的背打，还是跟踪一个用户遇到了一个空指针 新的3.0.2版本：嗯，这会教我不要把修复的深夜，在开机死机，现在固定。多亏了你们几个谁报告吧！ 新的版本3.0.1：修复了崩溃发生转换方向时（崩溃记者史蒂夫普赖尔） 新的版本3.0：修正了显著量的后端代码，支持平板电脑的阅读了。默认主题修改（这是对眼睛更容易了）。更新平价的袖珍参考手册，新的信息的最新文件副本。有些在页面的文本格式可能已经改变了（如果不看的权利给你，让支持DTS知道） 新的版本2.2：修正了一个小问题与EBCDIC到十六进制转换表。感谢约翰·克利福德的渔获！ 新的版本2.1：修正了，是由一个精明的与会者在分享引起了我们的注意，每磁道计算的DASD计算器的块错误（给我你的名字，我会放在这里）。这不应该以一种有意义的方式影响的用户，但检查以确保万无一失。该错误导致每个磁道被1关闭在某些情况下，这可能增加了另一个轨道的空间计算的块。再次感谢您一直以来的支持。 如果有其他任何你想看到的指南，请与我们联系！

column4: 游玩和学习。波兰语 free
column19: 此游戏是极有趣的又对个人有发展游戏，也就是学初级的外语发音及词汇量自学者的一种“电子家教”。 词汇列表专为在不同场合各种日常用语而组成。本自修教材，由使用配音和配图支持下，保证学习者掌握好外语的标准发音及外语的正字法。 便于学者方便，本教材分为个别阶段： * 训练 - 记忆锻炼：字母表、名词、形容词、动词等，附加带音标及声音的卡片。 * 使用以开心又轻松，并容易理解的游戏形式作为对于掌握词汇的参考： 1。阅读与联想：对图片选择正确答案（单词）。 2。影像：使用词汇表选择相对的移动图片（正确答案）。 3。正字法测试：写单词和正字法测试。 本软件界面的简单性，HD平板电脑支持，色彩鲜艳的专题图片，以及语言使用者高质量的配音，这都是保障与学者在学习过程中，能够提高听力并让学者专注于本教育材料，保障学者教学当中对于信息的快速性掌握。 专题列表： 蔬菜、水果、野兽、家畜、家庭、衣服、颜色、交通工具、人体、餐具、家用电器、食品、玩具、学校、大自然、昆虫、数字、几何学、乐器、工具、体育、旅游、办公室、的介词。 靠此帮助下，您或您的孩子可以以有趣的游戏形式学到外语的新词，增加词汇量，完善外语口语及书面语的水平基础。互动性（适应性）教学方法 - 是个学外语课程简单性又通畅性的方式。 对于儿童来看，本应用程序不仅学者在锻炼外语口语、书写时，是个快速及通畅方式，而且以及完全可以发展与改善自己以前于小学或幼儿园里得到的知识。孩子的父母可以在使用此应用程序时，作为孩子上学前的“各连杜曼”方法。 这包括文字超过10种语言，翻译。 实际上，这就是带图片的词典，又是个学波兰文的游戏，本游戏可以帮助学波兰文初级水平的学者或者小孩子们经过听取配音，同时参与游戏地学到很多的波兰语生词。 这个免费的应用程序工作在离线模式。付费版本没有广告，并包含详细的结果，帮助您分析语言能力的水平。

column19: 《App Config》是一款为应用设定配置的软件，系统自带的全局性设置其实并不能很好的满足我们的需求。你可能在某些应用中需要屏幕自动旋转，在某些应用中又希望屏幕方向保持锁定；在打开一些阅读类应用时，希望屏幕超时时间能自动延长一些，以避免频繁点击屏幕来保持屏幕亮起的状态。手动改来改去太麻烦，如果你也对此事感到不便，不妨让 App Config 来辅佐你吧。 App Config 提供了七个可控制项，包括屏幕亮度、屏幕旋转、屏幕超时、音量、数据、Wi-Fi、蓝牙。其内的搜索功能可以让你快速找到要设置的应用，在通知栏下点击 App Config 的通知可直接进入当前运行应用的自定义设置界面。

South Korea , officially the Republic of Korea (Korean: 대한민국; Hanja: 大韩民国; Daehan Minguk About this sound listen), is a country in East Asia, constituting the southern part of the Korean Peninsula.[1] The name Korea is derived from Goryeo, a dynasty which ruled in the Middle Ages. It shares land borders with North Korea to the north, and oversea borders with China to the west and Japan to the east. South Korea lies in the north temperate zone with a predominantly mountainous terrain. It comprises an estimated 50 million residents distributed over 99,392 km2 (38,375 sq mi).[2] The capital and largest city is Seoul, with a population of 10 million. Archaeology indicates that the Korean Peninsula was occupied by the Lower Paleolithic period (2.6 Ma–300 Ka).[3][4] Korean history begins with the founding of Gojoseon in 2333 BC by the legendary Dan-gun. Following the unification of the Three Kingdoms of Korea under Silla AD 668, Korea was ruled by the Goryeo Dynasty (918–1392) and Joseon Dynasty (1392–1910). It was annexed by the Empire of Japan in 1910. At the end of World War II, Korea was divided into Soviet and U.S. zones of occupation. An election was held in the U.S. zone in 1948 which led to the creation of the Republic of Korea. 《片轮少女 katawa shoujo》(按字面意思翻译即为“残疾少女”)是一款美少女恋爱游戏，背景架设在一所专门为残疾儿童而设的山久高校，地点位于现代日本某处。中井久夫是一个有着正常生活的普通男孩，但一次先天性心肌缺损引发的意外迫使他长期住院，之后不得不转到一所新学校。尽管困难重重，他还是交上了新的朋友——如果他能做出正确的选择，甚至还能拥有爱情。 　　故事以男主角的视角和第一人称叙述来进行。游戏由Ren'Py脚本系统制作，使用传统的文字叙事方式，单独绘制人物的视觉小说模式和ADV对话框，并辅以单独绘制人物制作成的视觉小说。游戏中有五条主线，分别对应五位女主角，每条主线都拥有为该角色设计的好/坏/中立结局。同时，每位女主角都拥有三章独立的故事情节。

This Sliding Puzzle is a 3D version of the so-called Pouss-Pouss or Taquin 's game. It's made of cubic pieces, arranged as spiral stairs, from lighter to darker color. The challenge is to reorder the pieces, after they have been mixed. You can choose for 9 or 16 pieces. 这种滑动拼图是一个3D版的所谓Pouss-Pouss或Taquin的游戏。它是由立方件，安排螺旋楼梯，从打火机到较深的颜色。面临的挑战是重新排列件，它们已被混合之后。 您可以选择9个或16个。
用手指移动控制射击方向和力度，点一下即可发射炮弹。 提示：需要击破所有地气球才能过关，炮弹打到铁链会让气球跑掉的。 这是大炮轰气球第三部，玩家仍然需要开动脑筋，利用大炮以及物理地特性消灭气球，小游戏难度逐步提升，赶快来挑战吧。

column7: 休闲时间-扑克棋牌-电子书
column19: You are a clone raised by the mysterious Silene Monks. Once the guardians of peace and justice in the galaxy, they have long since been superseded by modern technology. Now they spend most of their time hanging out and playing video games. But you are not like the rest of your clone brothers. You have been chosen for a special destiny. Make the right decisions and you'll complete your training, explore a universe full of adventure, and prove yourself a hero. Make the wrong decisions and you'll be dead. Really dead. Its hard to emphasise just how dead you will be. So here's a pro tip for you: try to make the right decisions. Written by Zach Weinersmith, creator of the hilarious award-winning comic strip 'Saturday Morning Breakfast Cereal'. You're a clone who sets out to find your place in a cold, uncaring, but also kickass and ridiculous futuristic world, solving challenging puzzles and fighting monsters along the way. It's like D&D for people who are too cool for other people! PLEASE NOTE - Due to mature content this app is for users who are 17+ only. It is not recommended for children. Exclusive new features in the app: • Wil Wheaton voice over! Listen to Wil Wheaton whisper things like "love", "plasmaster", "moral ambiguity", and "disappointment" into your ear. • All new death endings, written by Zach himself. Not available in the print book! • Achievements to find throughout the gamebook • Play the gamebook following all the rules, or cheat all you want! Trial of the clone has been brought to Android using Tin Man Games’ critically acclaimed Gamebook Adventures Engine featuring: • An automated Adventure Sheet to keep track of stats and inventory. • Artwork gallery. Find an illustration in the gamebook and be able to access it full-screen forever. • Bookmarking system which saves your position in the gamebook, much like putting your fingers between the pages to remember your previous page when reading the paperback! • Specially composed soundtrack • Landscape support for larger devices ** REVIEWS ** "A hilariously entertaining new addition to the gamebook genre, Trial of the Clone is a brilliant way to spend a rainy afternoon." - POCKET GAMER, 8 out of 10 - Silver Award! "I've finally gotten around to reading my copy and it's an absolute delight." - BOING BOING "I won’t dawdle with getting this out there: I love Trial of the Clone. It made me laugh numerous times and it made me want to replay it many, many times just so I could see how things could work out differently. It's simply brilliant." - 148APPS, 4.5 out of 5 - Editor's Choice! "If I really wanted to be lazy, I could summarize my review for Tin Man Games’ newest app Trial of the Clone like this: Buy the damn thing- NOW." - JUST PRESS START "This story touches so many GeekDad hotspots, there is a possibility that this post may self-implode in the awesomeness described here. Page after page, choice after choice, Trial of the Clone is very funny. The result is a glorious experience." - GEEKDAD “你是被神秘的僧侣蝇子草提出了一个克隆，一旦和平与正义的星系的监护人，他们早已被取代现代技术。现在，他们把大部分的时间挂出，玩视频游戏。 但你是不是喜欢你的克隆兄弟休息。你已经选择了一个特殊的命运。做出正确的决定，你会完成你的训练，探索出一条充满冒险的宇宙，并证明自己的英雄。做出错误的决定，你就死定了。真的死了。它很难强调只是怎么死的，你会。所以这里有一个PRO提示您：尽量作出正确的决定“ 撰稿扎克Weinersmith，欢闹的获奖漫画“星期六早上早餐麦片”的创造者。 你是谁列出来找到自己的位置在寒冷的，漠不关心，也kickass和可笑的未来世界，解决具有挑战性的难题，并一路上怪物战斗的克隆。这就像D＆D的人谁是太爽了别人！ 请注意 - 由于成人内容这个程序是为用户谁是17+而已。故不推荐用于儿童。 在应用程序独占新功能： •威尔惠顿配音！听威尔惠顿耳语的东西，如“爱”，“plasmaster”，“道德模糊”和“失望”到你的耳朵。 •所有新的死亡结局，是由扎克自己。不适用于印刷的书！ •成就发现整个游戏书 •玩游戏书下面所有的规则，或者欺骗所有你想要的！ 克隆的试验已经用铁皮人游戏“广受好评的游戏书冒险引擎，提供被带到Android版本： •自动化的冒险表来跟踪统计和库存。 •艺术品的画廊。发现在游戏书的说明图，并能够永远访问它全屏。 •书签系统，从而节省您的位置，在游戏书，就像把你的手指在页面读取时，平装记得你以前的页面之间！ •特别创作的配乐 •对于较大的设备支持景观 ** **点评 “一个欢快有趣的新增加的游戏书类型，克隆的审判是一个辉煌的方式来度过一个阴雨的下午。” - POCKET GAMER，8 10 - 银奖！ “我终于得到周围阅读我的副本，它是一个绝对的喜悦。” - 波音波音 “我不会让这个在那里磨蹭：我喜欢克隆的试验。它让我笑了很多次，这让我想重播了很多，很多时候只是让我能看到的东西怎么会制定出不同的这是。只是辉煌“。 - 148APPS，4.5分 - 编辑选择！ “如果我真的想偷懒，我就总结一下我的检讨这样的克隆的铁皮人游戏”最新的应用程序试用：购买这个该死的东西─NOW“。 - 只要按下START “这个故事触动这么多GeekDad热点，有这种可能后自我破灭的迷死这里描述的可能性。页页之后，选择后的选择，克隆的审判是很可笑的，其结果是光荣的经历。” - GEEKDAD

column19: 【健康有声小说】周末逛街？不去，不如窝在家里网上逛！休假旅行？不去，不如在家吃零食看电视！品尝美食？不去，不如自己在家动手做！去休闲运动？不去，不如在家打扫卫生……没错，俺是个不折不扣的宅女！ 或许是因为不爱热闹，所以喜欢待在家中；或许是因为不爱逛街，所以喜欢待在家中；或许不愿与人交谈，所以喜欢待在家中……家给我的感觉就是温暖，舒适，幸福。做个窝在家中的宅女，有何不可呢！ 其实，俺觉得宅女是最真实、单纯、可爱的女人。也许有人会反驳，宅女邋遢、颓废、寂寞、还不健康……宅在家的男女，还会宅出一身的病症。 如宅 男宅女们整天沉迷于电脑游戏、网络聊天，很少参加社会交往，大门不出，二门不迈，年轻的他们气定神闲地过着年迈的生活。时间一长，宅 男宅女们感觉人胖了，腰腿疼了，还时不时地感冒;血压高了，睡眠不好了，偶尔头晕目眩记不住事了；肛门潮湿、瘙痒、便血，痔疮也来了……另外，由于宅女们喜?长时间窝在电脑前，肌肤受到电脑辐射影响，变得暗黄，加上不怎么出门，肤色显得不自然，少了健康的色彩，给人的印象好像总是有点儿邋遢。难道宅女们真的一点前途都没有吗？

A-2481 - the horror game is one of the few games that really make you scared. Have you ever thought about possibility to control human brain at a distance? Can we do that? The same ideas occupied our hero’s mind. A journalist of a small provincial newspaper finds fragments of information about a secret military bunker of the USSR times codenamed «А-2184» where such experiments were obviously carried out in strict secrecy. Without a moment's hesitation you decide to start searching for answers for your new article! Dark and gloomy corridors of the bunker are a real thrill. And forsaken rooms where it seems people worked not so long ago, are terrifying. Every minute of stay in this evil place will make you go away as soon as possible. What is waiting for you there? Let’s find out! A-2481 - 恐怖游戏的几场比赛，真正让你害怕的。 你有没有想过可能在远处控制人脑？我们能做到吗？同样的想法占据我们的英雄的心灵。小省级报纸的记者发现了信息的碎片有关苏联时代研发代号为«А-2184»如果这种试验显然进行了严格保密的秘密军事掩体。没有片刻的犹豫，你决定开始寻找答案，为您的新文章！ 碉堡的黑暗和阴沉的走廊是一个真正的快感。而离弃室，似人的工作不那么久以前，是可怕的。留在这个邪恶的地方，每分钟都会让你走开尽快。是什么在等着你呢？让我们来一探究竟吧！

The Materials Council app presents more than 12,000 materials and finishes in the „Materials Inspiration“ section. The app is focused on materials and products intended for architectural applications. For each material / product you will find images of product variants and typical applications, as well as the possibility of sending direct enquiries about catalogues, prices and stockists. Many products are also presented within the framework of projects by international architects. The intuitive navigation by material group, manufacturer or free text search provides you with fast search results anywhere and at any time. As a result you can use the app either as a private design enthusiast, or for professional use as a planner or architect. The app also supports Materials Council's launch exhibition „Whiter than White“ during London Design Festival, allowing users to browse the exhibition samples, discover technical information about the materials and explore the exhibition literature, which is only available in digital form. An integrated QR code reader allows the exhibition audience to scan the exhibition materials with the app and be taken directly to the digital presentation, including product images, description, technical information and links to reference projects to view the materials in-situ. The app's functions at a glance: - Online research covering more than 12,000 architectural materials and finishes - Intuitive navigation and excellent image quality with zoom function - Compact texts about the products, with manufacturer's contact information - Supplementary functions enabling direct contact (prices, ordering catalogues, retailer data) - Daily automated update and expansion of the database - Integrated QR code scanner About Materials Council: The London-based Materials Council are independent exhibition curators and creative materials consultants to the architecture and creative industries. It was established in 2012 by Ian Hunter and Brad Turner, former materials researchers at Foster + Partners architects, and founding partner Architonic. You can visit us online at www.materialscouncil.com General terms and conditions and data protection guidelines: http://www.architonic.com/de/legal Architonic App Support

column19: 中财金融易考通是金融考试领域中的首创智能化学习平台。易考通由财政部中国财经出版社和国内最大职业教育机构华图教育共同开发，专注于金融考试，借助于中国财政经济出版社资源，APP以金融考试指定教材为基础，内容由金融考试教材编辑和出题专家研发,是目前金融考试考前复习最权威的一款学习软件。 金融考试的考前复习难点在于考试内容多、容易遗忘和不好理解，为了更好的帮助考生复习、提升效率，APP在功能设计上采用分级设计，将考点、试题根据必考程度和常考频率进行分级，一般分为三级，考生在复习时可根据内容的级别不同而花不同时间学习，有利于提升效果；同时为了提升考生的记忆，APP设置日记月累和错题本，日记月累根据艾宾浩斯记忆曲线进行设置，将考生学习的知识在第1天、3天和第7天进行推送，加强记忆，错题本则根据考生错误次数进行展示，便于考生复习。 为配合考生在不同场景下进行复习，本易考通系统配有电脑端学习平台，所有的帐号和积分都进行关联，内容同步更新。 每天十分钟，轻松过金考，高效、便捷和智能是金融易考通的最大特点，拥有金融易考通，金考更轻松！

***This free-download version will provide 10 trial sessions before committing to a subscription plan. You can purchase Dental RPM Pro in Google Play for an ad-free personal version*** Dental RPM Plus is a high speed acoustic rpm meter fully capable of measuring high speed air-driven handpiece free running speeds up to 550,000 rpm. Its capability in electric handpiece rpm has not been fully explored. At this time, this app is not recommended for electric handpieces. Dental RPM Plus makes very accurate measurements of high speed handpiece rotational speed with its proprietary frequency analysis algorithm that distinguishes the sound corresponding to the shaft rotation from other noises generated during handpiece operation. Even in a situation where multiple handpieces are operating simultaneously, it correctly captures the nearest handpiece’s rpm. The app also reports the peak noise level (A-weighted) of handpiece at the time of measurement. This app is compatible with all Android devices with Android OS version 2.2 or higher. A patent is pending on major features of the app including its functionality and frequency analysis algorithm. Features - Steady-state speed in revolutions per minute (rpm) between 25,000 and 550,000 with an accuracy of ±2584 rpm within 10 cm to 3 m (4 inches to 10 ft) distance from the handpiece. - A-weighted noise level with an accuracy of ± 3 dB. Recommended distance for dental handpiece noise measurement is 45 cm (18 inches) from the head. - Hold button to freeze the reading (hit again to resume). The app will display 0 rpm upon launching. Hit "Set dB" button to start (while handpiece is not operating).

十三洋行2015年初由科技行业多名实业家联合创立，秉承实业家务实坚守的工匠精神，致力于给向往品质生活的都市人群营造简单、高品质、值得信赖的跨境购物体验。 在跨境电商领域里，十三洋行首创了“简单购买”概念：以极致简洁、极其便利的购物体验，无过度修饰，无夸大其辞，竭力只为提供心仪之物和意外惊喜到顾客手中。 十三洋行所售产品全权进口，海外原产地直采，原产地原包装进口、海关全程监管，所有产品都要经过国检和商检，将商品首先存放在保税区，再通过电商平台零售交易，交易完成后直接从保税区发货，不仅可以减少消费者收到商品的等待时间，提升购物体验，更能节约贸易成本，使消费者有望获得更低的价格，商家也可以获得更大的利润。 【十三洋行,本身就是一个传奇】 在漫长的华夏史册中，十三洋行从来都只有一个。 可它用一百年（1804-1912年）的时间浓缩了长达一个世纪的中国引进海外商品的历史，是当之无愧的“跨境外贸鼻祖”。 是“十三洋行”，推开了中国走向世界的一扇门，也打开了世界透视中国的一扇窗；也是十三洋行，为中国商人搭建了走向世界的平台，实现了财富梦想。——今天，十三洋行应运而生，它承载着历史的托付，与我们不期而遇 【十三洋行的信条】 开放开放的心态 兼容 兼容并济的胸怀 创新 敢于创新的意识 务实 实业家的精神 多元 多元的文化 诚信 诚信为立世之本

column19: 喜堂之上，夫君执手她人，她"意外"香消玉殒。许是怨念太深，阎罗不收，让她重生了。只是这重生后的身份有点……据说这具身体的主人是个战功无数的女将军，阴险毒辣不说好像还十分的好色，豢养男宠换男人的速度比换衣服都快。天地可鉴，她生前可是纯的连男人的手都没有摸过的。至于上阵杀敌？不不不，她生前可是连厨房杀鸡都没做过。所以，她痛定思痛做出了个伟大的决定--逃跑！其实，她和皇子之间是清白的。大清早的衣衫不整从国师房间出来也纯属意外，更没有跟那个想要挽回她的心的前世夫君再有任何的瓜葛。她只是想要安安稳稳的过日子而已，可是这些男人穷追不舍，前仆后续。国师大人竟以色诱她，皇子还企图强行洞房……

Safely Family Utility runs on your child’s phone to power the Sprint Mobile Controls and Sprint Drive First products. FOR PARENTS Mobile Controls and Drive First are family safety products that run on the Sprint Network and let you block kids’ phone use during school hours or set a teen’s phone to automatically lock when they get behind the wheel. You only need to install Safely Family Utility on your child’s phone if you’ve already signed up for Sprint Mobile Controls or Sprint Drive First. Get Sprint Mobile Controls: http://besafe.ly/SMCandroid Get Sprint Drive First: http://www.sprint.com/drivefirst FOR KIDS ☆ Don’t believe the hype—this app does not let your parents “spy” on you or read your texts! ☆ It simply reassures them that you’re not on your phone when you should be paying attention in class or keeping your eyes on the road. ☆ A parent with peace of mind is less likely to confiscate your phone. So ask yourself: would you rather have this app on your phone or not have your phone at all? INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS You need to install Safely Family Utility on every child’s phone you add to your Sprint Mobile Controls or Sprint Drive First accounts. Install Safely Family Utility the same way you install any other app from Google Play: ☆ Tap the “Download” button and follow the instructions that appear on your screen. ☆ Once you’ve installed Safely Family Utility, you’ll get an email confirming that the phone has been successfully activated for Mobile Controls or Drive First. FROM THE SAFELY FAMILY Safely's digital parenting products enhance the personal safety and security of millions of families. In addition to Sprint Mobile Controls and Sprint Drive First, Safely also lets parents know where their kids are, right now with its Family Locator service. Get it on the Sprint network under the name Sprint Family Locator. ManageEngine EC2 Manager helps the system administrator to monitor and manage EC2 instances . It connects Amazon EC2 using access and secret key and lists the EC2 instances in dashboard view. It displays the graphical view of performance metrics like CPU, Network, Disk usage of EC2 instances. Also user can view the alarms generated by each instances. Using the App you can monitor the running status of EC2 instances in each region on the move. Key Features:Monitor EC2 instances (Zone wise)Displays Performance Metrics & Alarms graphicallyMonitor EBS volume detailsStart and Stop EC2 instancesProvides dashboard viewEnables reporting and sharingNo Agent required

column19: 古人曰："熟读三字经，便可知天下事，通圣人礼。"《三字经》自南宋以来，已有七百多年历史，共一千多字，可谓家喻户晓，脍炙人口。三字一句的韵文极易成诵，内容包括了中国传统的教育、历史、天文、地理、伦理和道德以及一些民间传说，广泛生动而又言简意赅。《三字经》早就不仅仅属于汉民族了，它有满文、蒙文译本。《三字经》也不再仅仅属于中国，它的英文、法文译本也已经问世。1990年新加坡出版的英文新译本更是被联合国教科文组织选入“儿童道德丛书”，加以世界范围的推广，也是儿童的必背读物。

Looking for the best night-clubs in town? Where are the good sports bar or pub to enjoy the game? Need to impress a date or a business partner in a great cocktail lounge? In the mood for a hookah but can’t find the perfect hookah lounge? You prefer an outdoor terrace, or maybe a rooftop bar? Or you love live music, live jazz perhaps? What about discos? A great nightspot, from a karaoke bars to a speakeasy lounge or a cabaret, an upscale nightclub or just cheap bars: everything will be a tap away with Nybber! HOW IT WORKS What’s the best party near me? Using my current location, Nybber shows me the best night-clubs and bars near me. What if I want to browse around a specific location and not what’s near me? No problem, Nybber can work anywhere in the world: just type-in a city name or a full address in the search field. WHAT IT SHOWS What are the events tonight? We have the events flyer and description. What’s the vibe really like? We have the photo albums from the previous party. What do people say about it? We give you direct access to the nightclub / bar review and ratings from Yelp, TripAdvisor, Foursquare and Google Place. And of course, we have all the important information for you: • Opening times • Address – both in English and local format • Phone number • Website And much more, all in a single free App! - Bar pictures, night-clubs pictures and events flyer come from Facebook - WHAT IT DOES The concept is to use as many sources as we can, in order to deliver you up-to-date and accurate information, on as many bars and night-clubs as possible, everywhere in the world. Whatever you may be interested in, may it be a speakeasy lounge in Chicago, an upscale nightclub in Sydney, a hookah lounge in London, a gay bar in New-York or information on Las Vegas stripclubs, you name it, we’ll have it! Nybber nightclub and bar guide targets travelers, newcomers, and locals alike: everyone will benefits from using Nybber to plan a night out! REMARKS FROM THE DEV TEAM The service has been launched at the end of the summer 2015, so we plan to quickly improve, both in number of sources –may it be local bars and local night-clubs nightlife guide, or a more global digest– and in number of nightspot we will be able to find for you. We are a social nightlife guide in a sense: the more party people use Nybber, the more cool bars and cool nightclub you’ll find with each request! Any comment on Nybber? How could we improve to better serve you? We’ll love to hear from you so we can make Nybber the best party advisor out there! Get the free app as a part of your Writer subscription to manage your writing and research anywhere you go. (Subscribe at http://writer.pearsonhighered.com) Manage all of your writing projects from your iPhone or iPod—get answers to your questions about research and grammar, instantly cite (search or scan) and organize your sources, keep notes, and view full-text sources while you research. Writer gives reliable answers to all of your questions about research, documentation, grammar and other writing topics. No need to carry around a handbook or weed through search engine results. Just use the Writing Guide search engine to see relevant and clear explanations, videos, podcasts, and examples. Manage your essays and research projects. You can keep track of your due dates, keep notes, and manage all of your sources for each project. Your “Bibliography Score” will flag any potential issues for you. And a “Progress Checklist” will help you stay on schedule from beginning to end. You can even search and view full-text journals and books so you can do your research when you’re on the go. FEATURES: • Writer’s Guide: Search a comprehensive library of content on research, grammar, and writing topics. Get answers to your questions with text, video, audio, and examples. • My Projects: Manage writing and research projects. Track due date and progress. Cite and organize sources. Check your “Bibliography Score.” Add and view notes. • Cite a Source: Cite sources in various documentation styles, including MLA and APA. Word game to practise reading and writing (spelling) of German words. German is spoken in Germany, Switzerland and Austria. 1) Learn how to spell German words: for each word a picture is shown with the letters of the word in a random order. Guess the word and place the letters below the image in the correct order, 2) Reading German words, 4 pictures and 1 word are displayed. Select the right image for the word, like in a quiz. 3) Vocabulary: learn German words, all words are displayed one by one. For each word an image is shown, like flashcards ✔ Vocabulary of 250+ words and pictures, more will be added ✔ Helps develop literacy skills ✔ Maximum word length can be set: from 4 up to 12 letters. Change the difficulty by setting this word length. ✔ Words from different categories like: vehicles and animal names, tools and types of furniture, fruits and vegetables.The latest version also has shapes, colours and numbers. ✔ A fun way to learn words and the alphabet / ABC of a foreign language. ✔ Kids at elementary school can learn to read and write (spell) their first words ✔ The app menus and texts have been translated to: English, Spanish, German, Dutch and Hungarian The app can be used by young and old to learn to read and write German words. For example for kids at primary school to learn to read and write (spell) their first words in their native language. And it can be used by older children and adults to learn German words if they are learning the German language. The free version has ads, the paid version does not. Besides the ads the versions are equal. The ads make the free version less suitable for young kids like toddlers. If you find errors then please let us know by sending an email. If you like the game then please rate it. Always try the free version before buying the full version. The description of Adblock Fast You can now block ads without rooting your device or switching to another browser ! Adblock Fast runs an optimized filtering ruleset to accelerate webpages more but consume less disk space, CPU cycles, and memory than other ad blockers do. Also unlike other ad blockers, Adblock Fast doesn’t allow “acceptable ads” and never will. The app requires and blocks ads in Samsung Internet 4.0 and up (not in other apps). After installing, follow the in-app instructions to turn ad blocking on. Adblock Fast is free to use and the source code, free to modify: https://github.com/rocketshipapps/adblockfast We use a public content-blocking API provided by Samsung Internet: http://developer.samsung.com/technical-doc/view.do?v=T000000278L If you have any questions or comments, follow and message us: • https://www.facebook.com/adblockfast • https://twitter.com/adblockfast ••• Adblock Fast was created and is maintained by Rocketship, an award-winning app studio based in Palo Alto and San Francisco whose mission is to design and develop the finest mobile and web experiences in the world: http://rocketshipapps.com/ Adblock Fast for Android official Trailer

咔咔点击精灵是一款在android手机上不仅可以模拟手机点击、按键操作的软件,还可以获取被控软件的界面信息，如按钮文字、控件位置、控件父子结构等。 通过制作简单的lua脚本,就可以自动执行一系列点击、触摸、按键操作并实时获取被控软件的界面信息，可以省力高效的在手机上完全模拟人的操作。 咔咔点击精灵采用Lua简单易学的语言作为脚本语言,在其基础上实现了点击、找图、触摸、滚屏、获取UI界面信息等功能。 咔咔点击精灵需要手持设备root后才可以使用，所以使用前请提前对设备进行root。

广电财富（www.guangdiancaifu.com）网络金融信息服务平台隶属于陕西广电融汇信息科技有限公司，是由陕西广电网络传媒（集团）股份有限公司全资设立，成立于2015年8月，注册资本壹仟万。 广电融汇公司依托陕西广电传媒集团的良好企业背景、完善的风控体系及集团多年运营的成熟经验和管理模式，并吸收了来自各行业的精英团队，对于资本运作、品牌包装、网络运营具有丰富经验，以普惠金融发展为使命，搭建互联网金融业务的创新运营平台——广电财富平台。 广电财富平台是一个公正、透明、公开的信用网络借贷平台，由从业于金融、互联网行业多年的精英团队倾力打造，以发展即时投资融资渠道，完善安全放款投资理财服务为理念，提供发布借款供求信息、项目投融资信息等服务，建立诚信、安全、快捷的服务体系，为业内人士提供一个高效、快捷的网上资金供求、交流平台，为社会闲散资金和个人创业者以及中小企业搭建一个合法、规范、诚信、透明、快捷、安全的借贷网络信息平台。

金属装饰材料分为黑色金属和有色金属两大类。 黑色金属包括铸；铸铁、钢材，其中的钢材主要是作房屋、桥梁等的结构材料，只有钢材的不锈钢用作装饰使用。有色金属包括有铝及其合金、铜及铜合金：金、银等，它们广泛地用于建筑装饰装修中。 现代金属装饰材料用于建筑物中更是多种多样，丰富多彩。这是因为金属装饰材料具有独特的光泽和颜色作为建筑装饰材料，金属庄重华贵，经久耐用，均优于其他各类建筑装饰材料。 现代常用的金属装饰材料包括有铝及铝合金、不锈钢、铜及铜合金。

column19: IF—中国第一款男生使用的经期记录软件。 有85%的男生都面临过这样的困境：不知女生什么时候来大姨妈，就是不知道暴风雨什么时候会来；不知道女生何时是危险期，就是不知道自己何时就会当上爸爸。虽然市面上有众多的经期记录软件，但由于界面复杂、功能繁琐等设计，并不符合男生的使用习惯。 然而IF，就做了一次历史性的颠覆！ 【男生专属】根据男生的使用习惯为男生量身设计 【简单易懂】男生无须任务基础也能看得懂的数据 【精准专业】基于大数据分析的全国女生的平均经期情况 【今日现象】显示她今日可能会出现的各种情况 【未来预测】预测她未来七天各项指标的发展趋势 【贴心助手】每天提供不同的建议帮助男生照顾女生 IF以最简单、最有效的方式，只为帮助你更好地照顾处于经期的女生。

SCUT gPen（简称gPen）输入法以提升用户输入体验为宗旨，界面设计简洁美观，功能设计高效简约易用！采用了极其先进的机器学习及人工智能技术，很可能是目前中文手写识别率最高的输入法！ 1. 采用全新的中文识别引擎，无约束书写识别率高达97%以上，规范书写识别率99%以上； 2. 支持简繁体汉字、香港字、标点、符号及常用手势等上万字符。 3. 支持绝大多数常用的数学符号、扩展符号手写输入 （例如√ Σα β γ ψ ╳∵ ≈ ≥ → ↗ ① ②③ 等100余种常见符号可轻松手写识别输入） 。 4. 自由输入，包括重叠手写、文本行连写、多行文本行重叠书写，随心所欲，手写体验更自然！ 5. 书法美化，集成鹅毛笔和毛笔效果，让你的字与众不同。 6. 键盘输入功能齐全，支持语音输入、九宫格、全键盘、表情符号键盘和数字记号键盘，随心切换。 7. 兼容当下热门应用和所有主流平台设备。

Features: * 1568 terms and definitions. * Vocabulary Player: pause, resume and forward terms like using a media player. * Text to Speech: hear and learn the correct pronunciation of every word in the vocabulary. * Text to Speech: read word definitions together with the app and improve your reading skills. * Two-way quiz: Study and test your Esperanto to English and English to Esperanto vocabulary. * Swipe enabled: simply swipe the bottom of the screen to fast forward terms. * Automatic loading of terms after a defined space of time (6 seconds by default, changeable in Settings). * Completely offline (use it on the road), lightweight, runs in all screen resolutions and uses no extra storage. Text to Speech: Prior to use the Speak Words and Speak Descriptions features builtin in this software, you will need a Text to Speech engine, such as SVOX or IVONA, with a Polish voice installed and active in your device (voices can be installed directly from inside the app). The Polish voice will then be adapted to speak Esperanto. An Android application written using Java. It can merge an number of SQLite database files into a single SQLite Database files.The definitions of the Views and Indexes and Triggers are then copied to a plain text file located beside the new database file where the output of merging happened.You will have to review the plain text file to fix the references to the table names in the new merging database file.This free version allows you to merge only TWO databases.

A checklist application that tries to stay out of your way wherever possible. Designed with speed, simplicity and readability in mind - just like you would use a simple checklist in real life. FEATURES: - Unlimited lists and entries - Sortable by date, label or checked state - Colors and icons for your lists - Password protection - Backup to and restore from SD card - Send your lists by E-Mail, Facebook, SMS, and many more using Android's sharing API - Remembers when an item has been checked and asks for confirmation (if enabled) when you uncheck it. - Nifty autocomplete hinting to minimize typing - Clean and readable interface - Selectable font size for lists and items - Customizable check method - choose between single tap, double tap or fling (swipe) gesture - Single or multiline entries - Available in English and German so far COMMENTS FROM USERS: Sean writes: "Five stars, supports app2sd, developer works hard to update an already very useful app they care about making the best on the market!" REQUIRED PERMISSIONS: - Backup feature requires access to your SD card NOTE: You can long-press on a list or entry to get to the context menu of that item. If you want Check and Done in your language, simply drop me a mail and i'll send you a translation template. 一个清单的应用程序，试图留出自己的方式尽可能。设计速度，简单性和可读性 - 就像在现实生活中，你可以使用一个简单的清单。 特点： - 无限的名单和条目 - 可排序的日期，标签或选中状态 - 颜色和图标为您的名单 - 密码保护 - 备份和恢复从SD卡 - 发送的电子邮件，脸谱，短信，和许多使用Android的共享API列表 - 记得当一个项目已经检查，并要求确认（如果启用）当你取消它。 - 俏皮自动完成提示，以尽量减少打字 - 清洁​​和可读性接口 - 可选择字体大小列表和项目 - 可定制的检查方法 - 选择单一的水龙头，双击或一扔（刷卡）手势 - 单或多行的条目 - 可在英语和德语到目前为止 从用户的评论： 肖恩写道：“五颗星，支持App2SD功能，开发人员努力工作，以更新已经非常有用的应用程序，他们所关心的市场上最好的！” 所需的权限： - 备份功能需要访问到你的SD卡 注：您可以长按列表或进入到该项目的上下文菜单中。 如果你想在你的语言的检查和完成，只需给我发邮件，我给你翻译模板。

Application Schema Therapy Diary helps you in your Schema Therapy every day, day by day. With this application you can record your emotions, analyze them in charts and send a report to your therapist. Because the Schema Therapy Diary app is on your mobile, you have your emotions diary always with you. You can take notes anywhere, anytime. With this app you can: - Note your thoughts and emotions you have during this thoughts - Note events which happens and emotions you have during this events - Note your emotions you have during day, you can do this periodically for example 4 times a day - Track your emotions on charts - List, edit, delete notes you have wrote - Generate reports about your emotions and send them via e-mail, for example to your therapist - Export data from one device and import on another - Protect application with password For an amount of time all features of the applications are available and no ads appears. After this time ads will appear and some features will be disabled. 「Remote control camera by the sound 」 This application lets you can remote control the camera inside Smart Phone. In other words, responding to sounds, the camera inside Smart Phone work automatically and you can take a photo hands free. For example, this application saves you from clicking the shutter button when you want to take a photo at the sightseeing spot, or marrying ceremony. Direction for use First, you touch “Shutter Keyword” in order to register a keyword to make your phone work. Second, you touch “Voice to shoot”. Finally, you say a keyword, and the photography will start automatically. Function You can… take a photo automatically by sounds take a photo also by the clapping or tapping, beside your voice put the taken photos in order. use silent mode. use autofocus. some kinds of flashes for the photography. specify the folder preserving photos. Caution! ･When you use this application, you must let your phone can access the internet, because your phone will operate an analysis of sounds through it. ･Your phone needs installed the application of Google sounds searching.(almost all the Smart Phone have installed this application already. If your phone don’t have it, you can download by GooglePlay.) ･If you distant from microphone, and make sounds, it will be hard for phone to catch the sounds. Equipping a better microphone on the phone, it can receive the sounds more distant. This application was developed to help improve access of the population in Lebanon to effective ambulance services. The application enables any person with an internet connection in Lebanon to register their physical addresses and to transmit that address rapidly to the Lebanese Red Cross operators of the national "140" medical emergency hotline. This will help ambulances reach the patients speedily. The application also provides a platform for people to know more about, and interact with the Lebanese Red Cross in order to constantly improve this vital healthcare service. It is the fruit of a close collaboration between the Lebanese Red Cross, Alfa - the Lebanese telecom operator managed by Orascom Telecom -, the Ministry of Telecommunications and the Waked family. We hope that this application will be useful to you, your loved ones and your colleagues. Keywords: First Aid, Help, Emergency, Red Cross, Lebanese, Danger, learning, EMS, ambulance,140

Easy to use outdoor navigation app with the best topographic maps of Canada. This app gives you similar mapping options as you might know from Garmin or Magellan GPS handhelds. *** Attention: Please use Toporama or Canada Base Map layer if you need most recent topo maps ! *** Main features for outdoor-navigation: • Bulk-download of map tiles for OFFLINE USAGE (NOT in this FREE version) • Create and edit Waypoints • GoTo-Waypoint-Navigation • Create and edit Routes • Route-Navigation (NOT in this FREE version) • Track Recording (with speed, elevation and accuracy profile) • Tripmaster with fields for odometer, average speed, bearing, elevation, etc. • GPX-Import / Export, KML-Export • Search (placenames, POIs, streets) • Customizable datafields in Map View and Tripmaster (e.g. Speed, Distance, Compass, ...) • Share Waypoints, Tracks or Routes (via eMail, Facebook, ..) • Use Coordinates in UTM, WGS84 or MGRS • and many more ... Available map layers: • Topomaps Canada (CanMatrix, seamless coverage at scales 1:50.000 and 1:250.000) • Toporama Maps Canada in EN&FR (CanVec, NTDB, Atlas of Canada) • Canada Basemap (CanVec, NTDB, Atlas of Canada) • CanTopo (new Canada topos at 1:50.000, partial coverage of Can) • Google Maps (Satellite images, Road- and Terrain-Map) • Bing Maps (Satellite images, Road-Map) • Open Street Maps (OSM Mapnik and Cloudemade Cyclemap) • Hillshading overlay layer (NOT in this FREE version) Toporama Maps Canada: These are the most recent topographic maps of Canada. Topomaps Canada: These maps contain many small pathes and 4WD tracks that are missing in Toporama, Google, Bing and OSM maps. This layer is essential for real outdoor and offroad trips in Canada. Seamless mosaic of more than 13.000 collar clipped 1:50.000 maps. LIMITATIONS OF THE FREE VERSION: • Ads • No Bulkdownload • No Hillshading overlay • Max. 3 Waypoints • Max. 3 Tracks • No Routes • No import of waypoints and tracks • No Local City DB (Offline Search) Use this navigation app for outdoor activities like hiking, biking, camping, climbing, riding, skiing, canoeing or offroad 4WD tours. Unlike other dictionaries you might have on your device, TapTap Word lets you look up the definition of words in the application you are running, without leaving the application! No ads. Be it a web browser or a document viewer - if you can copy a word in it, you can then tap-tap (or pull-tap) our notification icon, and our software will show the definition of the word on top of the application you are running. You can let the definition disappear automatically, or you can tap-tap (or pull-tap) to dismiss it sooner, or use our fun "flip-to-dismiss" feature! It's very convenient when you just want to quickly look up a word (in the application you are running). Currently TapTap Word looks up English words and shows their definition in English only.TapTap Word looks up words in an online database, located in US. Thus, network connection is required. However, it does not consume processing power or network connection while it is idle.Required user permissions: (1) Network communication - full internet access: to access the online dictionary. (2) Network communication - view network state: to test whether your device currently can access the internet (and thus the online dictionary). (3) Phone calls - read phone state and identity: to promptly dismiss the definition box when the phone is ringing.Note that if the online dictionary used by TapTap Word changes their data format, TapTap Word will have to be revised to work properly. Hopefully, this won't happen often, but please do check back for revisions. If you enjoy this software, please consider leaving a review here! Any problem, question, or suggestion? Email us. Thanks!

Advanced open-source SNES emulator based on Snes9x 1.53 with near complete game compatibility. A 1GHz+ device is recommended for best results. For older devices, a faster version based on 1.43 is available for download on my site. This app is 100% free with no ads. The public-domain game Bio Worm is included. Other ROMs must be supplied by the user. A number of public domain games/demos are available at www.pdroms.de. Transfer games anywhere to your internal storage/SD card and browse to them from within the app (default SD card directory on most devices is /mnt/sdcard). ROMs may be in .smc and .sfc formats, optionally in ZIP, RAR, or 7Z files. Follow me on Twitter for updates about my apps: https://twitter.com/rakashazi Visit the homepage at explusalpha.com for more info & apps, ports for other platforms, and source code. 基于Snes9x 1.53近乎完整的游戏兼容性先进的开源模拟器SNES。一颗1GHz +设备推荐最好的结果。对于较旧的设备，基于1.43更快的版本可供下载我的网站上。这个程序是免费的，没有广告100％。 在公共领域的游戏生物蠕虫是包括在内。其他的ROM必须由用户提供。许多公共领域的游戏/演示可在www.pdroms.de。转场的任何位置到内部存储/ SD卡，并浏览到他们的应用程序中（默认SD卡目录上大多数设备是/ mnt / SD卡）。 ROM的可能是.smc和.sfc格式，可选的ZIP，RAR，7Z或文件。 跟随我的Twitter有关我的应用程序的更新： https://twitter.com/rakashazi 请访问explusalpha.com主页以获得更多的信息和应用程序，其他平台的端口和源代码。

随着时代的变化，人们不能满足现有的生活圈子，希望有更大的自由空间来充实自己的生活。通过一个群体的共同特点建立其特有的社交网站成为大量中小网站的发展模式。但是传统的旅游网站，只适合于记录旅游结束后的感想，并不能很好的将旅游途中的点点滴滴保存下来。 而手机的移动属性，天生适于碎片化记录——随时随地拍下见闻，三言两语简要描述，即可生成足迹的碎片。当这些碎片被以各种维度被组织，串联起来就构成了完整的旅途记录。且信息的碎片化使得信息组织非常自由，可以更灵活快速地被传播，实现其SNS的价值。看国外Tripl与Facebook的合作，正是旅游与社交属性强强结合的    现在，每个人出行之前关注旅游网站更多是为了获得吃、住、行、游、购当中的一部分实用信息。可是当下旅游网站的内容，动辄就是数千字的长篇大论，除了少量的实用信息之外，更多的可能是作者自己的感慨，而我们的软件，就是记录用户的脚步，形成一个自我展示，且供他人参考的平台。 所以，我们的目标就是让用户在旅途中简单轻松地生成足迹碎片，并自动把这些碎片串联起来，形成声色并茂的旅行地图，满足记录与分享的需求。Iu(矮油)，Iu是我和你的英文缩写，又是爱游的谐音，他是一款基于xmpp的旅游地图地理类社交应用Iu是将社交与旅游地图相结合，并记录你你路游玩的历程，以地图的形式保存下来，*终传递给你的好友圈，而且其他陌生人还可以通过查看你的旅游地图记录，对你进行评价或赞，并可以与你交朋友。 以上描述中存在违反广告法的内容，自动用*代替

Learn Idioms helps to learn Generally Used English Idioms over a period of time. The application provides new Idioms to learn everyday. Think, if you learn 5 Idioms a day and start using them in your communication (both verbal & written) - the impact it will generate on your communication, personality and earnings - this app helps to do that! It provides a program to learn new Idioms every day and you can learn 1000 Idioms in 200 days (considering you learn 5 Idioms a day) Additionally, you can Test your learning using Quiz and check your ranking worldwide. See progress of your learning using Charts & Tables. * * * This application does not have Any AD Strip Or In-App Purchase ADs. column19: 通过检测使用者做题的准确率、做题速度、看懂率、看懂速度，智能提供学习帮助。学习帮助文档是我们软件的理论核心，帮助文档从思维、心态、学习方法、导引、学习方案等方面为学生提供指引。 学生还可以分章节、知识点进行专项学习和练习，也可以将多个知识点进行组合学习，还可以分年级进行检测、练习，无论选择任何内容，软件都可为学生出题检测，制定对应学习方案。 准确率——即做题准确率，分为极高、很高、比较高、一般、比较低、很低、极低等标准。 做题速度——指的是做对题目所花费时间的多少，分为极快、很快、比较快、一般、比较慢、很慢、极慢等标准。 看懂率——能理解题意，并有大概解题思路的题目即为看懂的题目，看懂率分为极高、很高、比较高、一般、比较低、很低、极低等标准。 看懂速度——能理解题意，并有大概解题思路的题目即为看懂的题目，看懂速度就是在这一过程中花费时间的多少，看懂速度分为极快、很快、比较快、一般、比较慢、很慢、极慢等标准。 每一个软件都包含对应科目对应学段的所有知识点，知识点可以选择单个进行检测，也可以组合检测。

column4: 宝宝成长记录+(Baby Care)-新手爸妈的贴心帮手！
column19: 记录宝宝成长的点点滴滴，新手爸妈的贴心帮手！ ★★★★☆ 作为刚刚成为父母的家长来说，照顾新生宝宝可是个需要随时待命的大任务。何时喂奶、何时换尿布、睡多久了?这些事情需要时时留心，让人紧张不安而又疲惫不堪。这款直观简洁的小工具可以帮助新手爸妈们从这些琐事中解脱出来，随时跟踪这些必要的信息，给宝宝提供更好的呵护。 本软件是由一个新爸爸和他的团队倾心打造，您可以通过它来记录宝宝成长的点点滴滴，通过提醒功能提前为宝宝需要的照顾做好准备，通过日记、图像和声音来记录他的每一个变化，记录他的成长感受为人父母的骄傲…… ☆☆☆☆功能列表 .记录宝宝发育情况（身高、体重、头围），以成长图（成长图数据基于（CDC）标准数据）显示 .记录宝宝情绪变化、母乳、奶粉、辅食、睡觉、换尿片（便便/臭臭）、健康状态、吃药、防疫、保健、其他（洗澡/玩耍/抬头锻炼等），并可通过短信、Twitter、Facebook分享，我们内置的丰富趋势图进行分析 .支持桌面放置可定制的应用程序小工具（Widget） .添加和分享宝宝照片（可拍照或从照片中选择） .录下和分享宝宝声音 .记录和分享宝宝日记 .提醒功能 .历史记录，查看任一天的宝宝情况 .备份数据到SD卡 .从备份还原数据 ☆☆☆☆☆特色功能 .为妈妈提供手工吸奶记录和图表功能 .支持照片Widget，将宝宝照片放于桌面 .为母乳喂养的宝宝提供专属计算器功能，可以结合吸奶功能使用（背奶族首选功能！） .支持主页面事件定制 .支持默认事件类型选择 .对比当天和前七天的平均数据，及时发现问题 .丰富的统计图表 母乳/奶粉/辅食/换尿片/睡眠(可设置夜间睡眠区间)/吸奶量/体温变化 一览表视图 .日历视图 .支持多个宝宝 .内置多款皮肤，可针对不同的宝宝进行设置 .导出事件、日记、成长记录到CSV文件(注意，如在导出后用Excel打开发现有乱码，不必着急，可以用记事本将此文件打开并保存为ANSI编码即可)。 Keywords: 宝宝成长记录 Baby Care 发育 成长 母乳 奶粉 喂养 家长 爸爸 妈妈 日记 成长图 吃药 防疫 拍照 录音 图表 吸奶 背奶 小便 大便 日历 体温

We want to create a better, more efficient everyday life for the many people in the trucking industry.Melody Truckload is a new mobile app that helps you fill those empty miles in considerably less time and effort. It uses automated software to recommend the most relevant and reliable loads for you, based on your preferences and location.Using our app, you can easily set personalized filters, book matching loads, and generate e-invoices at the tap of a button. Whether you are looking for a long haul or a quick LTL job nearby, Melody Truckload is your guide to finding just the load for your trucking business.(*) Discover high-paying loads fast and effortlessly.(*) Search for available loads nearby (great for return trips!).(*) Receive custom filtered results by pick-up or drop-off locations, trailer type, remaining LTL length, and trip mileage.(*) Generate e-invoices at the tap of a button and send fuel receipts or other documents electronically.MATCH EFFORTLESSLYStop staring at loads irrelevant to you, and let the perfect loads always find you. Our app lets you set up personalized filters and only shows you matching loads that are most likely to become yours. Let our technology do the busy work for you, so you can focus on getting more done.WORKS LIKE AN INBOXOur goal was to take the familiar further. So we redesigned the loadboard to make load matching light, fast, and mobile-friendly. Quickly fly through your matched list and claim your favorite load at the tap of a button. It’s a whole new loadboard that looks and works just like your email inbox you are so accustomed to.MORE TRUCKLOAD, LESS WORKLOADBesides filling your empty miles, use our app to automatically generate time-stamped invoices with geolocation coordinates, send fuel receipts or other documents electronically -- keeping things organized and simple. All you need is your smartphone and our Melody Truckload app.

column19: The Cambridge Academic Content Dictionary defines the vocabulary students need to succeed in high school and beyond. Its entries include more than 2,000 key vocabulary items from the content areas of math, the arts, chemistry, earth science, physics, American and world history, social studies, language arts, and other disciplines, as well as the more general vocabulary used in academic writing and speech, such as "analyze," "derive," and "subsequent." The dictionary also provides full coverage of the everyday words and phrases students need to know. It is based on extensive Corpus research and developed with the needs of English learners in mind. ***This is a fully functional trial!*** Features:  • Easy-to-understand definitions make the meanings clear.  • Full-sentence examples show how English is really used.  • Usage notes help students avoid common mistakes.  • Word Family and Word Choices boxes help students expand their vocabulary and choose the right word.  • Reference Pages provide useful information about geography, science, math, literature, and more. A SEARCH TOOL featuring search autocomplete to help you find words quickly by displaying predictions similar to the terms you're typing. You also get enhanced search extras including:  • A quick search of words while you type.  • A 'fuzzy filter' for when you are not sure of the correct spelling of a word.  • A 'keyword' search for finding key words within compound words.  • A wild card search function ('*' or '?') which can replace a letter or entire parts of a word.  • Download dictionary definitions locally for offline word lookup. A LEARNING TOOL including a number of features that help you further enhance your vocabulary:  • A 'Favorites' feature to create custom folders with lists of words from the extensive library, including cross-curriculum words.  • History list to help you easily review looked-up words.  • Discover more using the included special language notes.  • See words in context with example sentences.  • 'Word-of-the-day' feature with dedicated homescreen widget. 剑桥学术内容字典定义的词汇学生需要在高中及以后取得成功。 其作品包括数学，艺术，化学，地球科学，物理学，美国和世界历史，社会科学，语言艺术的内容领域中使用的2000多名关键的词汇，和其他学科，以及更普遍的词汇学术写作和演讲，诸如“分析”，“导出”和“后续”。该词典还提供了日常单词和短语的学生需要知道的全覆盖。它是基于大量的语料库研究，并与英语学习者心目中的需求而开发的。 ***这是一个全功能的试用！*** 产品特点： ＆＃8195;＆＃8226;易于理解的定义做出明确的含义。 ＆＃8195;＆＃8226;全句的例子说明如何英语真正使用。 ＆＃8195;＆＃8226;使用注意事项，帮助学生避免常见错误。 ＆＃8195;＆＃8226;字族和Word选项框帮助学生扩大他们的词汇量，并选择正确的字。 ＆＃8195;＆＃8226;参考页提供有关地理，科学，数学，文学，更有用的信息。 搜索工具 具有自动完成搜索可帮助您快速通过显示的预测相似，你输入的条件查找单词。您还可以得到增强的搜索演员包括： ＆＃8195;＆＃8226;快速搜索的话，而你输入。 ＆＃8195;＆＃8226; A'的模糊滤镜“当你不能确定一个单词的正确拼写。 ＆＃8195;＆＃8226; A'关键词'搜索复合词中找关键词。 ＆＃8195;＆＃8226;通配符搜索功能（“*”或“？”），它可以取代一个字母一个字或整个地区。 ＆＃8195;＆＃8226;在本地进行离线单词查询下载词典定义。 一个学习工具 其中包括了许多功能，帮助您进一步提高你的词汇量： ＆＃8195;＆＃8226; A'收藏'功能来创建字从粗放库列表，包括跨课程的话自定义文件夹。 ＆＃8195;＆＃8226;历史记录列表，以帮助您轻松地查看看着向上的话。 ＆＃8195;＆＃8226;使用附带的特殊语言笔记发现更多。 ＆＃8195;＆＃8226;看到上下文例句的话。 ＆＃8195;＆＃8226; “口碑的天”功能与专用的主屏幕小部件。

在香港有很多人还惯用旧的度衡量单位, 新一代已转用公制,这个方便的程序为大家转换单位,只要输入数字在一方的格内, 另一方的值便会即时转换,一目了然。 Many people in Hong Kong are still used to old units of measurement and the new generation has switched to the metric system. This app brings convenience to everyone when it comes to unit conversion. Just enter a value in a cell, the conversion will take place instantly. 在香港有很多人还惯用旧的度衡量单位，新一代已转用公制,这个方便的程序为大家转换单位,只要输入数字在一方的格内,另一方的值便会即时转换，一目了然。 不少人在香港仍用于测量的老单位， 新的一代已经切换到公制。这个应用进程带来了 方便大家，当涉及到单位转换。只需输入 在一个单元格的值，转换将发生瞬间。

column4: 다리 교정 운동 - 휜다리 클리닉 체형, 하체 다이어트
column19: 8월 18일 이후로 날씬이 운영하는 모든 앱들의 회원가입/다운로드 서버가 종료됩니다. 구버전 사용자들은 미리 새로운 앱(2.0버전)으로 이동하세요.^^ 2014년 여름!! 다리교정 2.0 출시!! [휜다리 클리닉]이 [다리교정]으로 새롭게 개편되었습니다. 그동안 수많은 회원분들이 지적하셨던 문제들을 모두 수용해서 이번엔 회원가입 기능을 모두 제거했고 보다 직관적이고 트랜디하게 디자인했습니다. 주의: 운동카테고리 3개중 2개(이완운동,마무리운동)는 유튜브로 연결됩니다. 데이터 통신이 발생하니 주의 깊게 이용하세요. 대신 가장 중요한 교정운동은 앱에 내장되어 있어서 언제 어디서든 이용할 수 있습니다. 아이폰 앱스토어 건강 1위, 전체 6위에 빛나는  'Self 휜다리 클리닉'[무료] 앱이 안드로이드 마켓에 런칭됐습니다.^^  "당신의 다리는 곧은가요?"  -늘씬한 연예인 같이 쭈욱 빠진 다리!  -치마와 청바지, 어떤 옷을 입어도 옷태가 나는 각선미!  -나이가 들어도 튼튼한 무릎 관절!  이는 곧은 다리일 때 누릴 수 있는 것들입니다. 당신의 다리는 곧은가요?  이 앱은 개발자의 다리도 O다리에 가까와 개선을 위해 특별하게 개발한 예방/치료 프로그램입니다.  재활 필라테스 전문 강사님과 휜다리클리닉 전문가가 협력하여 개발한 컨텐츠를 담고 있습니다.  실제 커뮤니티에 배포 후 많은 분들이 효과가 있다며 호응을 해준 프로그램이죠!  "잘 빠진 다리의 기준은 뭘까요?"  다리가 가는지, 통통한지 이전에 얼마나 골격이 곧은가가 더 중요합니다.  다리가 곧지 않으면 미용적으로 다리가 예뻐보이지 않으며, 심리적으로도 컴플렉스를 유발합니다.  장기간 휜다리를 방치할 경우 인체의 골격이 무너져 바른 자세가 흐트러져 근육통을 유발하고 피로를 가중합니다.  다리가 휘는 원인은 단지 다리 관절에만 문제가 있는 것이 아니라 골반, 무릎관절, 발(평발), 척추의 자세게 문제가 있기 때문입니다.  이 어플은 필라테스와 요가 자세를 중심으로 하체, 즉 골반, 하체근육, 무릎과 발목관절을 밸런스 있게 자극하고 이완해 바르고 자신감 있는 몸매로 만드는데 도움을 주는 동영상으로 구성되어있습니다.  장기간 운동을 따라하시면 교정효과와 휜다리 예방효과를 얻을 수 있습니다.  매일 저녁 TV를 보면서 딱 10분만 투자해보세요!  다리의 휘어짐이 큰 분들은 전문 병원을 찾아가셔서 치료를 받으시는 것이 꼭 필요합니다. 방치하면 점점 더 심해지는 것이 휜다리 질환입니다. 셀러오 올림. # 오류 발생시, 정보를 저희에게 보내주십시오. 어떤 기기로 어떻게 사용할 때 오류가 발생하는지 상세하게 적어서 이메일을 보내주시면 보다 빠르고 정확하게 오류 수정을 할 수 있습니다. ---- 개발자 연락처 : 경기도 성남시 분당구 서현동 풍림아이원 A동 808호 关机寄存器/自8月18日下载服务器的所有应用程序运行更瘦了。老用户要移动到一个新的应用程序（2.0版本）提前。^ 2014年的夏天！标定桥2.0发布！ 新改组[大桥修正[hwindari诊所]是。与此同时，一些成员谁必须接受所有的智力hasyeotdeon问题的这个时候，除去所有的成员函数有一个时髦的设计更加直观。 运动与YouTube的3类产品共2相关的（放松练习，练习结束）注：。进行数据通信发生，请小心使用。代替内置的应用程序，你随时使用的最重要的校准工作，任何地方。 ＃1 iPhone应用程序商店泛着健康在整个06 自我hwindari诊所[免费]在Android Market的应用程序启动。^ “你的腿是直的？” - Jjuuk失踪苗条名人的脚！ - 穿着牛仔裤，裙子和适应任何衣服我州的两条腿！ - 听到老崎岖的膝盖！ 这是你可以享受直腿的时候。做你的腿伸直？ 这个程序是用腿特别是O桥的方法来改善预防/治疗程序的开发人员开发的。 它包含了与专业导师和hwindari普拉提康复治疗诊所的专家合作开发的内容。 这是一个很多人谁促成了上诉，说效果是真实的，然后分配给社区项目！ “一个很好的标准的任何想法缺少的桥梁？”这座桥去，以前丰满知道如何goteunga骨架更重要。 如果桥没有好看的腿gotji美容，还导致心理情结。 如果你想离开人体的长期框架摇摇欲坠hwindari扰乱了正确的态度会导致肌肉疲劳和体重。 这是因为有一个问题导致腿膝盖弯曲的姿势，以脚（扁平足），骨盆，脊椎不只是一个只腿关节问题。 它包括视频的刺激可使下半身的平衡，即骨盆，下半身的肌肉，膝关节和踝关节周围的普拉提和瑜伽姿势和放松揉搓，以帮助信心应用程序中创建一个机构。 你hwindari根据长期锻炼的预防作用和校准，你可以得到的效果。 每天晚上看电视只是尝试投资10分钟！ 你只需要去找到你收到的腿弯曲是伟大的人民专科医院治疗。 这是越来越严重，如果不hwindari疾病。 哦，卖家随身携带。 ＃错误时，请给我们的信息。 当您详细介绍如何使用的任何设备错误写下来，请快速准确地比对纠错可以发送电子邮件。

Amharic is an official language of Ethiopia. It is widely spoken language.This Dictionary gives Amharic definitions for about 40,000 English words. The correct pronunciation is also given in English/Amharic letter. It is designed for use in schools and colleges where the Amharic equivalent of an English word is often sought to make a meaning clearer. Business-men and professional people will also find it helpful. Students of Amharic as well as visitors to Ethiopia and foreign workers will benefit from this concise dictionary with phonetic transcriptions that allow for its use by those unfamiliar with Amharic script. This app contains advertising. 阿姆哈拉语是埃塞俄比亚的官方语言。它是广泛使用language.This字典给出的定义阿姆哈拉语为约40,000英文单词。正确的发音是英文/阿姆哈拉语信中还给出。它是专为在学校和学院所在的阿姆哈拉语相当于一个英文单词经常被要求作出一个意义更清晰的使用。商务男人和专业人士也会发现它有用。阿姆哈拉语的学生和游客到埃塞俄比亚和外国工人会从这个简洁的字典受益与音标，允许对那些不熟悉阿姆哈拉语脚本的使用。 这个程序包含广告。

Madame Bovary by Gustave Flaubert Series: The 10 Greatest Books of All Time http://www.time.com/time/arts/article/0,8599,1578073,00.html#ixzz2DitztA29 Virtual Entertainment, 2013 The story focuses on a doctor's wife, Emma Bovary, who has adulterous affairs and lives beyond her means in order to escape the banalities and emptiness of provincial life. Though the basic plot is rather simple, even archetypal, the novel's true art lies in its details and hidden patterns. Flaubert was a notorious perfectionist and claimed always to be searching for le mot juste ("the right word"). — Excerpted from Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia. Cover and App icon is a frame with Isabelle Huppert of movie "Madame Bovary" 1991, Director: Claude Chabrol. This app turns your smart phone into a Ghost detector. Unlike the most apps on the market that use Electromagnetic fields for searching for ghosts (which is very inaccurate and will give you random results), Ghost sensor searches for so called "Cold Spots". Cold spot describes an area of localized coldness or a sudden decrease in ambient temperature that is allegedly connected to paranormal activity. As soon as Ghost Sensor adapts to the room temperature you can start your hunt. Please note that the accuracy of this app depends on the accuracy of your devices sensors! 这个应用程序将你的智能手机变成一个幽灵探测器。不同于市场上用于搜索鬼电磁场（这是非常不准确的，会给你随机的结果），鬼传感器搜索所谓的“冷点”的大多数应用程序。 冷点描述局部发凉或突然降低环境温度涉嫌被连接到超自然活动的区域。只要鬼传感器适应室温就可以开始你的追捕。 请注意，这个应用程序的精确度取决于你的设备的传感器的准确度！

This is a fun and educational free math game for preschool and schooling children. With its friendly interface and easy rules “Kids Math: Add” helps children to learn adding and trains their brain constantly. Parents also can enjoy it and keep their math skills in shape. This game is based on two components. Sheep representing digits that can be added and a cloud containing a number i.e. a sum. The kid's goal is to select those sheep who's total of digits will equal the number in the cloud. If an answer is correct the game continues automatically. And if the sum of digits on the selected sheep exceeds the number in the cloud the game ends. “Kids Math” add has tree levels: Easy – calculations go up to 10; Normal - calculations go up to 25; Hard - calculations go up to 100. Have fun! Developed using libgdx game framework: http://libgdx.badlogicgames.com/ 这是一个有趣的和教育的免费数学游戏为幼儿园和子女上学。凭借其友好的界面和简单的规则“儿童数学：添加”帮助孩子学习增加和不断训练他们的大脑。家长也可以享受它的形状，并保持他们的数学技能。 此游戏是基于两个部分组成。羊，代表数字，可以添加和包含数字的总和即云。孩子的目标是选择那些羊谁是总的数字，将在云中的数目相等。 如果答案是正确的，比赛继续进行自动。并且如果在选定的羊数字的总和超过在云中的数量，游戏结束。 “儿童数学”添加树级别： 易 - 计算多达10个; 正常 - 计算高达25; - 计算硬多达100个。 玩得开心！ 开发的使用libgdx游戏框架： http://libgdx.badlogicgames.com/

Synchronizes Android with Microsoft Outlook 2007 or greater via WiFi (protected by SSL), USB cable - (tasks - including recurrent tasks and categories; notes - including categories; contacts - 50 data items; calendar - including recurrent appointments, timezones and categories; categories). There are provided applications for Notes and Tasks (categories manager is reachable from these apps). Synchronizes directories/files with PC. Application web page: http://www.psencik.cz/local-sync It is possible to use Local Sync without Outlook to synchronize files/directories between Android and computer or use Local Sync only in Android for its Tasks and Notes apps without any synchronization. Localization: English, Czech, German, French, Japanese, Polish PC server application download is available on product homepage. Support, documentation and educational videos are available on product homepage. It is possible to synchronize one Android device with many PCs and one PC with many Android devices (e.g. synchronize Android with notebook and PC at home and with PC at work) - Local Sync is primarily designed to support such a scenario. If manufacturer replaced Android 4 contacts application with own (naive) version it may not be possible to add/edit Local Sync contacts - ask manufacturer for stock contacts apk. Used icons author: RRZE, http://rrze-pp.github.io/rrze-icon-set/licence.html, License: CC BY-SA 3.0 Android的同步与Microsoft Outlook 2007或更高版本通过WiFi（SSL保护），USB连接线 - （任务 - 包括经常性的任务和类别;笔记 - 包括两类;联系人 - 50个数据项;日历 - 包括经常约会，时区和类别;类别）。有提供应用笔记和任务（类别管理器是从这些应用程序可到达）。 同步目录/文件与电脑。 申请网页：http://www.psencik.cz/local-sync 它可以使用本地不同步Outlook同步Android和电脑之间的文件/目录，或仅在Android中使用本地同步进行的任务和便笺的应用程序没有任何同步。 本地化：英语，捷克语，德语，法语，日语，波兰语 PC服务器应用程序下载可在产品网页。 支持，文档，教育视频都可以在产品网页。 它可以同步一个Android设备与多台PC和一台PC与许多Android设备（如笔记本电脑和在家使用电脑在工作中的Andr​​oid同步） - 本地同步主要是为了支持这样的情景。 如果制造商的Andr​​oid更换4个触点与自己的（天真的）版本的应用程序也可能无法添加/编辑本地同步联系人 - 要求制造商股票的联系人APK。 使用的图标作者：RRZE，http://rrze-pp.github.io/rrze-icon-set/licence.html，许可：CC BY-SA 3.0

This app initializes Abbott Freestyle Libre new sensors without the need of Abbott reader. Move back of your device near the new sensor and wait until you feel two short vibrations. Please be careful: -To access sensor, NFC must be enabled on Android device -If you initialize a sensor with Glimp S you will be unable to read it with Abbott Freestyle reader -For reading sensors initialized by Glimp S you need to use Glimp app -Glimp app can read sensors initialized by Glimp S and by Abbott Freestyle reader -This app is not an official Abbott app and it will access sensor memory writing data, so you use it at your own risk.

column19: ★☆Achieved 4 million downloads! Thank you☆★ ChickPusher is a game like the Coin Pusher! Many chicks are in a cape. They are trying to ride on the nest at a tip. However, chicks do not have the courage which has crossed the cape. Then,Please lend your power. 【How to Play】 If a screen is touched, a chick will fly. Please push out chickens to a cape front. "Piyo Coin" can be got if it can fly from a tip. It is a source of the power of chickens. Moreover, a friend will be called if it goes into a nest. If much "Piyo Coin" is collected, a new friend will come. There is also a rare chicken in a friend. If the chick is put into a nest, it will become a bonus time full of chick. Let's put many chickens into a nest. column4: Yahoo!知恵袋　悩み相谈できる质问・回答掲示板アプリ
column19: ★日本最大级のQ&AサービスYahoo!知恵袋アプリ！おかげさまで累计300万ダウンロード突破！★ ・今话题のQ&Aがすぐにわかる！「総合ランキング」 ・悩める子羊の甘酸っぱい恋の悩みがたくさん「キラキラ知恵袋」 ・人気のQ&AはPUSH通知で配信！ ・疑问や悩みは手軽に质问投稿！　PUSHで回答・返信をすぐに确认。 ・人に知られたくない秘密の质问は匿名でこっそり质问。 ・あなたの兴味に合わせてホーム画面をカスタマイズ ★こんな疑问や悩み、质问を投稿してみよう 知恵袋アプリなら匿名での质问投稿や画像添付もできるのでどんな疑问や悩みも质问できます。 回答や返信はPUSH通知ですぐに确认できます。 ・身近な人には闻けない恋爱相谈や人间関系の悩み ・ハマっているゲームの攻略方法 ・病気や怪我の不安 ・ダイエットの悩みやコツ ・お気に入りのアーティストや芸能人の疑问 ・学校の宿题の质问 ・子育ての不安や悩み ・明日着ていく洋服のコーディネート ・旅先の隠れた穴场スポット ★こんなキーワードをホームに登录してみよう 知恵袋アプリでは兴味のあるキーワードやカテゴリをホームに登录してカスタマイズする事ができます。 最新のQ&Aをいつでもすぐにチェックできます。 ・ハマっているゲームのタイトル ・好きなスポーツ ・お気に入りのアーティストや芸能人の名前 ・気になるドラマや映画のタイトル ★ホーム画面について お客様の端末にインストールされているアプリ情报を取得し、お客様に最适なQ&Aがトップ画面に表示することができます。 现时点では、お客様の端末にインストールされているゲームアプリのイベント情报や攻略情报などゲームに関するＱ＆Ａがトップ画面に表示することができます。この机能は、アプリの设置から>OFFにできます。 ※投票机能について ver2.0.0以降のAndroid版知恵袋アプリでは投票机能を廃止しております。 引き続き投票机能をご利用の方はPC版知恵袋からご利用ください。 ★日本最大的问答服务雅虎答案的应用进程！由于人数300万下载突破！ ★ - 现在的Q＆A的话题很快就可见一斑！ “综合排名” - 甜和麻烦酸酸的爱情是很多陷入困境的羔羊“金葱答案” - 流行的Q＆A在PUSH通知交付！ - 疑虑是很容易的贡献！立即确认PUSH答案回复。 ·你不想知道的秘密男人的问题是偷偷的问题匿名。 - 自定义主屏幕，以满足您的利益 ★这样的疑惑和担心，让我们张贴问题 任何问题或疑虑，也可因此质疑答案也可以贡献和图像伴随应用进程，如果匿名。 答案及回复可以立即在PUSH通知加以确认。 •不要听爱情辅导和人际关系的人熟悉的忧虑 - 沉迷于游戏的捕获方法 ·生病和意外伤害的焦虑 饮食忧虑和技巧 问喜爱的艺术家和演艺人员 校外家庭作业的问题 ，育儿焦虑和担忧 的 - 穿衣服，明天协调 的最隐蔽的道路关闭因循守旧点 ★让我们注册这个关键字到户 在回答应用进程可以被定制来注册你有兴趣在家里关键字或类别。 你可以很快查询最新的Q＆A. - 沉迷于这个称号的游戏 - 最喜欢的运动 最喜爱的艺术家和演艺人员 - 的名字 - 焦急的戏剧和电影标题 对于★主屏幕 获取已安装在终端上的应用进程的信息，客户最佳的Q＆A将能够显示顶部屏幕上。 目前，我们可以Q＆A关于游戏，如事件信息，并抓住显示在顶层屏幕上已安装在终端上的游戏应用进程的信息。此功能，从应用进程的设置>你可以为关闭。 ※关于投票功能 在ver2.0.0后来针对Android应用的答案我们已经废除了投​​票功能。 请从PC版本中使用Chiebukuro继续？请使用投票功能。

column4: OpenTable Japan - レストラン予约 - 日本
column19: 『いつでも・どこでも・简単に』オンライン予约ができる、世界有数のレストラン予约サイト OpenTable（オープンテーブル）の日本版公式アプリです。 日本、アメリカ、イギリス、カナダ、ドイツ、およびメキシコで、7亿人のお客様が32,000店以上のレストランに OpenTable を使って予约を入れています！ オープンテーブルAndroidアプリを使って、ぜひ行ってみたかったお店にご予约を！アプリでのご予约は惊くほど简単。その场で确定するので、电话で确认する必要もありません。 【注意】日本にあるレストランのご予约にお使いになれます。アメリカやイギリスのレストラン検索やご予约には、それぞれの国で提供しているアプリを别途ダウンロードしていただく必要があります。 【使い方】 ①予约の希望日时と人数を选んで検索 ②空席のあるレストランから行きたいお店を决定！ （※レストラン名を指定して空席検索することもできます。） ③予约可能な时间帯から、お好きな时间をタップ ④アプリ上で予约が完了 本アプリからのご予约でお食事されると、ポイントもたまりさらにお得です。（※要ユーザー登录） 【便利な机能】 ・エリア内の复数のレストランを検索 ・店名を指定して検索 ・予算、评価、距离、料理のジャンルなどでの绞込み ・评価・口コミやお料理の写真 ・一绪にお食事される方への招待メール ・予约情报をカレンダーに追加 【さらに】 ・自分だけのお気に入りリスト ・レストランへのリクエストや连络事项もアプリ内から送信 ・贮めたポイントはギフトカードに ★ OpenTable Is Secretly the Best Thing on the Internet (Gizmodo) ★ World's Greatest Apps (Business Insider) ★ Best Restaurant Dining Apps (People Magazine) ★ Top Android Developer (Google Play) OpenTable サイトはこちらから >> http://www.opentable.jp/ OpenTable サポートはこちらから >> http://support.opentable.jp/ “随时，随地，方便”，可以网上订票，这是日本版的世界领先的餐厅预订网站OpenTable的（开放式表）的官方应用进程的。 日本，美国，英国，加拿大，德国和墨西哥，7亿的客人有使用OpenTable的32000多的商店餐馆预订！ 使用开放式表Android应用进程，您的预订到店，我们想要去通过各种手段！预订是在应用进程非常简单。自成立以来在其位，你不需要通过电话进行确认。 [注]，你会发现在你的餐厅在日本图书。在美国和餐馆搜索英国和预约，有一个应用进程，提供在每个国家的需要为你单独下载。 [如何使用] 搜索和选择所需的日期和时间以及①保留的数 ②确定你想从一个空缺的餐厅去的店！ （您也可以通过指定※餐馆名称空置搜索。） 从预订窗口③，挖掘你最喜欢的时间 ④保留在应用进程完成 一旦从该应用进程的订餐，也点积累是比较大。 （需要※用户注册） [实用功能] 搜索区域内的多个餐厅 通过指定商店名称搜索 和预算，评估，距离和缩小的菜肴流派 评估和审查和菜肴照片 - 邀请那些谁在一起吃饭 - 添加预约信息到日历 [更多] ·您自己的收藏列表 请求或接触此事向餐厅还从应用进程内发送 •合并的一点是要礼品卡 ★ OpenTable的暗中在互联网上最好的东西（Gizmodo的） ★世界上最伟大的应用进程（商业内幕） ★最佳餐厅用餐应用进程（人物杂志） ★顶级Android开发者（谷歌播放） OpenTable的网站从这里>> http://www.opentable.jp/ OpenTable的支持，从这里>> http://support.opentable.jp/
