The Sesame Street: Incarceration app provides parents and caregivers with tools to help children ages 3-8 cope with the many transitions related to a parent’s incarceration. Features include: • Tip Books providing parents and caregivers with age-appropriate language to talk honestly with children (3–8) as well as strategies to help children cope with a parent’s incarceration • Videos featuring real families and Sesame Street Muppets • An interactive storybook and photo activity for caregivers to use with children • Suggestions for additional support and educational resources We recommend you use the tools and watch the videos before sharing them with your children so that you can choose what is most relevant and helpful for your family. Resources in this app are part of Sesame Street’s Little Children, Big Challenges: Incarceration initiative. You can access additional project materials online, at sesamestreet.org/incarceration. 芝麻街：监禁的应用程序提供了父母和看护者提供工具，帮助孩子3-8岁应付有关父母的监禁许多过渡。 其特点包括： •提示书提供父母和看护人与年龄相适应的语言与孩子（3-8），以及战略老老实实说话，帮助孩子应付父母的监禁 •影片具有真正的家庭和芝麻街布偶 •交互式故事书和照片活动护理人员与儿童使用 •建议更多的支持和教育资源 我们建议您使用的工具，并与孩子分享，从而使您可以选择的是最相关和最有用的为您的家庭之前观看的视频。 在此应用程序的资源是芝麻街的小儿童，大挑战的一部分：监禁举措。您可以在线访问其他项目的材料，在sesamestreet.org/incarceration。

Swipe left for a new song. Swipe up for search. Swipe down to access genres and favorites. There's unlimited skips so you can always find something great to listen to! OnRad.io works with 100,000 online radio stations from all over the world. The stations are monitored every 3 seconds to identify the currently playing artist and song. This information is used to allow the user to find the song or artist they desire. To play, users connect to the station's free audio stream using the OnRad.io app. OnRad.io compatible messaging apps: Twitter Snapchat Messenger (Facebook) What'sApp WeChat Hangouts (Google) Yahoo IM Examples of OnRad.io URLs: onrad.io/Hello.Adele - Plays Hello by Adele onrad.io/Metallica - Plays the most popular song by Metallica played on radio onrad.io/Walk.The.Moon Plays the most popular by Walk The Moon played on radio onrad.io/1 - Plays #1 song on radio (works 1-100) onrad.io/country - Plays a popular country song onrad.io/country1 - Plays most popular country song 查找和播放任何歌曲或艺术家在世界上播放电台的任何地方。分享歌曲和艺术家对流行的通讯服务，包括微博，Snapchat，微信，WhatsApp的和Facebook Messenger的使用OnRadio网址。 OnRad.io网址将自动启动应用程序，找到歌曲播放。没有申购费，无需注册或登记要求使得它很容易与任何人分享。一次点击和播放音乐。只需添加任何艺术家，歌曲或艺术家的歌曲组合到OnRad.io URL的末尾请参见下面的例子。如果歌曲不提供任何地方无线世界中，应用程序将提供它正在播放下一个时间通知你，你能听我的话。 该应用程序有一个易于使用的刷卡驱动界面。刷卡离开了新歌。向上滑动进行搜索。向下滑动访问类型和收藏夹。有无限的跳跃，所以你总能找到一些伟大的事情来听！ OnRad.io适用于来自世界各地的10万在线广播电台。该站监控每3秒，以确定当前正在播放的歌手和歌曲。这个信息被用来允许用户找到他们想要的歌曲或艺术家。要播放，用户连接到使用OnRad.io应用该站的免费音频流。 OnRad.io兼容的通讯应用： 推特 Snapchat 使者（脸谱） What'sApp 微信 视频群聊（谷歌） 雅虎IM OnRad.io URL示例： onrad.io/Hello.Adele - 戏剧你好由阿黛尔 onrad.io/Metallica - 播放由Metallica的最流行的歌曲播放的电台 onrad.io/Walk.The.Moon播放最流行的步行月球上播放收音机 onrad.io/1 - 播放1首歌曲在电台（作品1-100） onrad.io/country - 播放的热门乡村歌曲 onrad.io/country1 - 播放最流行的乡村歌曲

column19: Epic hunting adventure finally on Android! If you are playing on a tablet, get HD version! Carnivores: Dinosaur Hunter is a console-quality lifelike hunting game where the players track down a variety of dinosaurs while exploring huge non-linear locations. The dinos boast with some of the most advanced AI on the platform, evolving from “pea-brained” dummies to dangerous creatures that are able to see, hear and sense the adrenaline in hunter’s blood. Distinct 3D environments including pine forests, muddy marshes and rolling hills give room for different hunting tactics, which are important because the hunter may easily end up becoming a prey. Wind direction, scent and the use of a special dinosaur call are all key elements in tracking the dinosaur and not being caught. Game Features: * Huge 3D world, open to explore! * Console quality HD graphics * 3D dinosaurs, from the Herbivorous (plant eating) for novice hunters to the Carnivorous (meat-eating) for experts. * Two exciting game modes: – Hunting: a non-linear close to reality hunting experience where players roam through vast landscapes, tracking and hunting a variety of dinosaurs. – Survival: a timed, frenzied affair where dinosaurs run onto the player in waves with a clear intention to fress him. * Choose from among six different weapon types – from a sniper rifle to an X-bow. * Map and radar to locate and track dinosaurs. * Hunting accessories for smart hunting * Online leaderboards and social networking integration. * Interactive Dino Trophy Room. Supported on devices with OS 4.0 and up Become a fan of Carnivores on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/carnivores Thank you for playing our games! This app continuously captures camera images in the background for timelapse videos (see video link for a sample). Delay between images is adjustable down to 1 second. Normal phone operation can continue with minimal CPU load. Note: images are saved on SD card in an intermediate format to minimize CPU load. Use "Convert All" to convert them to PNG (warning: may take some time). This app is open-source under GPL. The source code is available at https://github.com/floe/Background-Timelapse I have a couple of additional features planned - please stay tuned :-) 这个程序连续捕获摄像机图像在后台慢速拍摄的视频（见视频链接样本）。 图像之间的延迟是可调整的下降到1秒。 普通的手机操作上可以继续用最少的CPU负载。 注意：图像被保存在SD卡中的中间格式，以减少CPU的负载。使用“转换全部”将它们转换为PNG（警告：可能需要一些时间）。 这个程序是GPL下开源。源代码可在https://github.com/floe/Background-Timelapse 我有一对夫妇的计划的附加功能 - 敬请期待：-）

[국내유일] 사법시험 기출문제 앱, 즐겨찾기, 오답노트, 진행률 계층적 관리 사법시험 기출문제를 정리하였습니다. = 정리된 내용 = 헌법, 민법, 형법 : 2007~2014년 국제법, 형사정책, 법철학, 국제거래법 : 2008~2014년 노동법, 조세법, 지적재산권법, 경제법 : 2008~2014년 = 프로그램 특징 = 1. 진행률 지원 – 어디까지 문제를 풀었는지 과목별, 폴더별로 볼 수 있어 학습상황을 직관적으로 알 수 있습니다. 2. 즐겨찾기, 오답노트 지원 – 즐겨찾기와 오답노트를 분리 지원합니다. 헛갈리는 문제나 중요한 문제는 즐겨찾기에 추가해서 관리하고, 틀린 문제는 오답노트에 추가한 후 반복학습 하면서 맞은 것은 지우는 방식으로 학습할 수 있습니다. 3. 자동 채점 지원 – 필터의 도입으로 맞은 문제 틀린 문제만 살펴볼 수 있으며 메뉴에서 ‘결과보기’로 언제든지 점수를 볼 수 있고 원하는 문제로 빠른 접근이 가능합니다. 4. 다양한 옵션 지원 – 여러가지 옵션으로 정돈된 화면을 만들 수도 있고 상세한 화면을 만들 수도 있습니다. 다양한 옵션 기능을 활용해 보세요. 5. 선택과목 지원 – 자신의 선택과목을 옵션을 이용해서 하단 메뉴에 배치함으로서 자신만의 탭메뉴를 만들 수 있습니다. (선택과목을 지원하는 앱에 한함) = 프로그램 설명 = 화면 하단의 탭 메뉴에서 학습하고자 하는 아이콘을 선택합니다. 화면 중앙에서 폴더 또는 과목을 선택합니다. 과목을 선택하면 문제 풀이가 진행됩니다. 문제를 풀면서 정답을 볼 수 있습니다. 또한 '+' 버튼을 사용하여 즐겨찾기에 추가가 가능합니다. 옵션에서 자동 진행을 선택하면 문제를 풀 때마다 다음문제로 자동 진행됩니다. 문제를 다 풀면 채점이 되며 채점화면에서 틀린문제, 맞은 문제를 볼 수 있으며 틀린 문제는 오답노트에 추가가 가능합니다. 즐겨찾기와 오답노트에서는 간략하게 문제 정보를 보여주면 필요없는 경우 옵션을 통해서 보지 않을 수 있습니다. ---- 개발자 연락처 : 주소지 : 서울시 관악구 호암로 546번지 (대학동 1557-1) 교내기업실 연락처 : 010-8519-4125 사업자등록번호 : 209-81-51463 国内仅有】司法考试的试题和内容以前出现的应用程序，书签，笔记不正确，进展分级管理 已经当他们成为问题组织了司法考试项目。 =组织内容= 宪法，民法，刑法：2007-2014 法律，犯罪学，哲学，国际贸易法：2008-2014年 劳动法，税法，知识产权法，经济法：2008-2014年 =该方案的特点= 1.进展支持 - 在哪里主题是否解决问题，我可以通过文件夹看看，你可以看到学习状况直观。 2.我的最爱，不正确说明支持 - 支持删除不正确的笔记和书签。小屋分歧问题和关键问题，除了收藏管理，这是学习的重复正确和错误的答案加上不正确的音符后，你可以学习开道。 3.支持自动评分 - 只要看看对面的一个问题错在引进过滤器，你可以看到你的得分在任何时间从菜单和快速访问可能期望的问题，“查看结果”。 4.支持多种选项 - 可以创建一个整洁的屏幕与各种选项，或者你可以创建一个详细的屏幕。请采取多种可选功能。 5，选修的支持 - 通过把他们选修的选择在菜单的底部使用创建自己的选项卡菜单。 （应用程序只支持选修课） =程序说明= 选择您想要从选项卡菜单，以了解在屏幕底部的图标。 在屏幕的中心，选择文件夹或主题。 如果你选择一个主题将进行池。 正如你所看到的答案来解决问题。它也可以通过使用“+”按钮被添加到收藏夹。如果选择自动，选项将自动进行每次解决问题的时间进入下一个问题。 解决这个问题是一个错误的分数，你可以看到的问题，正确的和错误的答案是在计分屏问题可以被添加到不正确的音符。 在收藏夹和不正确的笔记，你无法通过选择看，如果你显示，不需要一个简短的信息的问题。

应用搬家sd是一个帮助您将应用程序到SD卡上的简单工具。将原本安装在手机存储的应用程序移动到SD卡存储，此操作可以节省你的手机内部存储空间。软件功能：★列出所有可以移动到SD卡的应用程序★显示通知，当新安装的应用程序可以移动到SD卡★告诉用户哪些应用程序不应该被移动到SD卡，并告诉用户详细原因★统计面板，显示应用程序数量，总大小，可用内存和已使用的内存★按照应用程序的名称，大小或安装日期排序。★快速菜单（长按应用程序列表项）：打开应用程序/显示详细信息/显示应用程序的Google Play页面/卸载应用程序软件还集成了其他功能，如缓存清理，优化内存等，快来下载试试吧。

“动画与动物之声”是为儿童开发的特别申请。它是一个有趣的应用程序，它是使用简单。同时该应用程序的目的招待孩子是教不同的动物的叫声。孩子玩耍和有一个良好的时间与动画的动物以及学习不同动物的叫声。 应用程序是与几乎所有的Android设备兼容，但如果不支持的设备，让我尽量给你快速的支持。 您要申请的权限： “ Android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE ”和 “ Android.permission.INTERNET ” 上网给予所需的程序的错误和崩溃报告发送权。 注意：此应用程序是用于动画，图形和声音文件在互联网上的“自由发布”从标记各种来源获得的。因此，你认为是一个文件的版权持有人可能立刻注意到我的电子邮件，如果你有这些文件将被删除。

This is self described as “a simple, practical, biblical, helpful, and personal tool for disciples of Jesus who want to make disciples of Jesus.” Multiply is written by Francis Chan and endorsed by David Platt. The Multiply Material is a 24-session discipleship experience where one person helps another understand what it means to follow Jesus, study scripture, and be the church. Features - displays all the content for each session in a friendly format for mobile devices - for each session there are links to the pdf content, audio content and coaching videos to assist you as you study through the course - provides links to other short multiply clips as well as the multiply gathering videos - weekly Bible reading plan - swipe from the left of screen to open up the menu; or press the button on the top left - can move app to SD Card - basic pinch to zoom ---- Official Multiply Movement site can be found here: http://www.multiplymovement.com Before the official site updated to be mobile friendly I had made this site: http://multiply.ampers.x10.mx I am in no way associated to Multiply Movement, I am grateful they have given their content out for free. ---- 这被描述为自我“谁想要使耶稣的门徒耶稣的门徒简单，实用，圣经，乐于助人，和个人的工具。”乘由李国庆书面和大卫·普拉特认可。乘法材料是24届门徒体验，一个人帮助另一个明白它的意思跟随耶稣，学习经文，并教会。 特征 - 显示所有每个会话的用于移动设备的友好格式的内容 - 为每个会话有链接到PDF内容，音频内容和指导视频，帮助你，你通过课程的学习 - 提供到其他短乘法剪辑链接以及乘法采集视频 - 每周读经计划 - 从屏幕打开菜单的左侧刷卡;或按左上角的按钮 - 可以移动应用程序到SD卡 - 基本捏放大 ---- 乘官方网站的运动可以在这里找到：http://www.multiplymovement.com 官方网站更新之前移动友好的我做了这个网站：http://multiply.ampers.x10.mx 我在没有相关乘运动方式，我很感谢他们给他们的内容要求自由。 ----

Network printer driver for Android. Directly print your photos from your Android device over your WIFI network. No need to install anything on your PC! Lets you print from all printing enabled Android applications (e.g. browser, image gallery, office applications). After first install, you have to enable the zenofx.com PrintBot service. In the PrintBot GUI, use Menu -> Service settings. If you have any problems setting up, please use the integrated setup help (Menu -> Help). - Supports more than 4.700 printer models from all leading manufacturers (e.g. HP, Canon, Epson, Lexmark, Brother, Samsung). Works with most Airprint™ enabled printers. - Supports printing over JetDirect, LPR and IPP protocol. - Auto scan for printers - Free version allows printing of 3 images or PDF documents per month (after that, a watermark is added on each page). PDFs are restricted to 3 pages. - Pro version allows unlimited printing and printer profiles Android的网络打印机驱动程序。直接从您的Andr​​oid设备在你的WIFI网络打印照片。无需在PC上安装任何东西！ 让您从所有打印启用的Andr​​oid应用程序（例如浏览器，图片库，办公应用程序）进行打印。 在首先安装，您必须启用zenofx.com PrintBot服务。在PrintBot GUI，使用菜单 - >服务设置。如果您有任何问题设置，请使用集成安装帮助（菜单 - >帮助）。 - 支持来自所有主要制造商（如惠普，佳能，爱普生，利盟，兄弟，三星）超过4.700打印机型号。与大多数通过Airprint™启用打印机。 - 支持过的JetDirect，LPR和IPP协议打印。 - 对于打印机自动扫描 - 免费版本允许每月3的图像或PDF文档（在那之后，一个水印每一页上添加）打印。 PDF文件限制为3页。 - 专业版允许无限打印和打印机配置文件

column4: 专业修眉画眉彩妆技巧
column19: 如何让你的眉更加的迷人？修眉后整个人都会有不一样的运气哦！其实修眉是很重要的，它能提升一个人的精神和气质修养，因为眉毛对面部能起到很大的决定性的作用。即便你没有化妆，只要你修眉，整个面部看上去也会很有型。精致的眉形，会让你的整体面容更具立体感。 特别是女孩子走的是眉运，主财和心情，眉开眼笑，眉清目秀。所以，更应该修眉，眉修整齐了，脸看着也感觉干净许多。

column19: 邦讯物联用于控制和管理上海海纳通物联网公司的wifi智能家居系列以及兼容的第三方智能家居设备（包括但不限于智能插座、智能路由器、智能音响、智能摄像头、净水器、酒精测试仪等）。 1. 只要您的手机连上网，就可以在全球任何地方控制您的家电； 2. 通过扫描二维码或者蓝牙，非常轻松方便的添加智能设备，并且管理。您可以给设备分组、查看设备的信息状态、修改设备头像、昵称等。随时可以远程操控升级； 3. 可以给智能插座和插排支持定制多个定时任务，根据您的生活习惯来设置家电的开关时间，还可以清楚的了解其用电量、电费、功率电压等信息，并对您的历史数据进行分析。您甚至还可以用插座直接连接音响来播放音乐； 4. 智能音响让你摆脱线的束缚，通过无线网络和零客轻松播放您手机里音乐； 5. 智能摄像头就像把家带在身边，随时随地，远程查看； 6. 您的所有数据保存在云服务，方便快捷； 7. 根据用户的喜好可以选择不同个性的UI界面； 8. 安全保障，手机验证码和密码双重保险。 邦讯物联致力于给人们的生活带来更多的便利，您就像多了一个家居管家，给您最个性化的智能家居控制解决方案。

Solution of logical puzzles with matches is a great way to spend your free time, training logic and wit. Puzzles with matches known for a long time, the first of which appeared about three thousand years ago in China long before the matches themselves and are one of the most common categories of puzzles with small objects. Puzzles from famous compilers - Sophus Tromgolt, Y.I. Perelman and B.A. Kordemskiy. 拼图比赛 - 球迷的智能娱乐。优越的发展逻辑，适用于儿童和成人。 解决方案是一个伟大的方式来度过你的空闲时间，训练逻辑和机智的逻辑拼图比赛。拼图比赛很长一段时间，其中第一个出现在约三千年前在中国的比赛前自己和小物件的难题之一，最常见的类别。 从著名的编译器 - 拼图，易Sophus Tromgolt佩雷尔曼和学士学位Kordemskiy。

MATLAB is a numerical computing environment and programming language. Maintained by The MathWorks, MATLAB allows easy matrix manipulation, plotting of functions and data, implementation of algorithms, creation of user interfaces, and interfacing with programs in other languages. Although it is numeric only, an optional toolbox uses the MuPAD symbolic engine, allowing access to computer algebra capabilities. An additional package, Simulink, adds graphical multidomain simulation and Model-Based Design for dynamic and embedded systems.

Easy to learn, hard to master! Burn the Rope is a challenging game where you try to burn as much rope as you can in each level. There’s a catch! The fire only burns upwards, leaving you to tilt and turn your phone to keep your flame alive! As you progress through the levels, you’ll encounter bugs crawling along the rope. Different bugs have different reactions to the flame. For example, the ant changes the color of the flame so you can burn different colored ropes, and the spider shoots out a web bridge so you can access parts of the level that you could not before. Burn the Rope is incredibly fun and addictive. You will actually feel like you’re burning a rope, yet there’s no need for a fire extinguisher! Features: • 232 exciting levels with more coming soon! • Incredibly fun and addictive! • Unique controls ! • Beautiful graphics and cool fire effects! • Easy to learn, hard to master! • Fun for the whole family!

column19: Games that are based on stories often manage to gather interest of the players. You really want to see the end of the game when you have a mission which is not possible in the popular endless running games. One such game is Datswer which is an action and puzzle game where you will not only have to use your fingers but also your brain. Datswer is a statue which came to life as some drops of magical liquid fell on it. it is a statue in the dark cave and now he has to exit the cave in order to save his life. You are going to help it find its way out. Datswer, is an adventure game and people have already loved its previous versions. It is a paid game on iTunes with a lot to explore and with several bug fixes in the recent version the game is almost perfect. There are 40 scenes in the game. There are acrobatics involved in the game and lots of puzzles to overcome. There are inventories to collect in the game. The joystick is the control of the game and you have to use it to perfection in order to save yourself. 是基于故事游戏常常管理收集的玩家的兴趣。你真的想，当你有一个使命，这是不可能的流行无尽的运行游戏，看比赛的结束。一个这样的游戏是Datswer这是一个动作和益智游戏，你将不仅要使用你的手指也是你的大脑。 Datswer是一个雕像来的生活，神奇的液体几滴落在它。它是在黑暗的洞穴的雕像，现在他已经离开了山洞，以挽救他的生命。你要帮助它找到它的出路。 Datswer，是一个冒险游戏，人们已经爱过了以前的版本。它是在iTunes上付费的游戏有很多的探索和几个bug修复在最新版本的游戏几乎是完美的。有在游戏40的场景。有参与游戏杂技和大量难题要克服。有库存以在游戏中收集。操纵杆是游戏的控制，你必须用它来完善，以保存自己。

One of the key challenges when requesting emergency assistance is communication. When out in the street, sometimes you are unsure of the exact location that you are in, which is then difficult for the rescue team to find you quickly. When in a scenario such as kidnap, where you could not speak or communicate your movement, therefore you could not alert the rescue team of your movement for rescue operation. When in distress, you could be too traumatized to speak or for individuals with hearing or speech impaired, it is a challenge to communicate calmly to the rescue team. Hence, with MyDistress, you could alert the police department, Polis Diraja Malaysia(PDRM) of your emergency situation with just a click. Important: - This application is linked directly to Polis Diraja Malaysia(PDRM) Selangor Contingent. - Coverage Area – Selangor only. - MyDistress is a platform where rakyat could notify the Selangor police when assistance is required. - “Personal Alert” is for outdoor use and it tracks your movement. - “Preset Location Alert” is for indoor use especially in multi storey buildings. - By hitting the “ON HELP” button within “Personal Alert” and “Preset Location Alert”, your request for assistance will alert the Selangor Police and police personnel will be sent to your location. - ONLY use MyDistress for emergencies that require police assistance. - MyDistress DOES NOT track your movement or location if NOT activated. Brought to you by NKRA Selangor Police.

In this simulation game, you are an air traffic controller at the approach radar of a busy airport. The goal is to guide the planes safely to the ILS (Instrument Landing System) of the runways to get a high score. If you make no errors, the number of planes you have to control gets larger and larger. How many flights at a time can you handle? The game shows you a radar screen with planes and runways. Planes are generated randomly. To keep it fun and playable, this ATC sim is a bit simplified compared to real life, yet it's all on scale and the planes behave quite realistically. A warning for users who are unfamiliar with aviation: due to high realism, this game may bore or frustrate you, so please read the instructions below first. :) Instructions Select a plane, give it a descend instruction (to about 2000 feet), guide it to the thin blue line at a large distance from the runway (somewhere between the blue circles), and clear it for approach by enabling ILS mode, which means it will follow the line to the runway (given that the plane captures the line at a shallow angle). It's also handy to check out the screenshots and the video. Then just try it! More detailed instructions: • sequence the traffic to the ILS path in front of a landing runway. The runway is depicted as a small, thick blue line in the middle of the screen; the ILS path is the thin line extending from the runway. In order to capture this ILS beam, a plane must comply to three conditions: (1) the ILS mode of the plane is activated, (2) the plane has to be descended low enough to intercept the glideslope from below; the blue circles mark the altitudes of 2000, 3000 and 4000 feet, (3) the plane must intercept the ILS at a heading of 50 degrees or less with respect to the runway (aim for about 30 degrees). If captured correctly, it will follow the line and land automatically on the runway. Note that it takes some time for a plane to descend to the selected altitude. When a plane is fully established, it will be handed over the the tower and then you score skill points. For parallel approaches, maintain 1000 feet vertical separation until both planes are localizer established. • Departing aircraft determine their heading and speed themselves (by default); they only require an instruction (when it's safe, of course) to climb to a higher altitude: flight level 130. • You can also lose skill points when planes: (1) fly too close to eachother (generally: overlapping circles and altitude difference <1000 feet), (2) leave the airspace (outer grey circle), also if they are departures but leave the airspace at or below FL100, (3) missed approaches/go arounds. • The amount of planes that you have to control is about the same as the amount of skill points you have: the higher the skill value, the more planes you have to deal with. You can also achieve 'goals' by landing a certain amount of planes in the correct way. • Some planes have an additional 'RD' tag; only these planes need to land on the secondary 'RD' airport. In the menu there are options like a speed multiplier, and a 'skill cap' for a more relaxed gameplay: this 'cap' limits the skill value so the rate of inbound traffic will also be limited. Other parameters are randomly chosen. Double tap on the radar screen to zoom in/out. For more detailed instructions go to http://startgrid.blogspot.nl/2013/11/endless-atc-instructions.html Features • endless amount of planes, multiple runways, • give radar vectors like a real air traffic controller, • amount of traffic adapts to your skill level, • pause and high simulation speed modes, • automatically saving game; resume where you left off, • no internet connection required, • no ads, • it's free. The game plays best on big screens. If you have feedback, please send me an email. 在这个模拟游戏，你是在一个繁忙的机场进近雷达空中交通管制。我们的目标是安全引导飞机到 ILS 的跑道（仪表着陆系统），以获得高分。如果您没有错误，你要控制飞机的数量变得越来越大。你有多少航班在同一时间可以处理？ 这场比赛显示了你的飞机和跑道雷达屏幕。平面是随机生成的。为了保持它的趣味性和可玩性，这ATC SIM卡是有点简化比起现实生活中，然而这一切都在规模和飞机表现得很逼真。 A 警告内，谁不熟悉航空用户：由于高真实感，这个游戏可能孔或阻挠你，所以请阅读下面首先说明。 :) 说明 选择一个平面，给它一个降序指令（约2000英尺），引导其以蓝色细线在距离跑道（蓝圈之间的某处）一个大的距离，并清除它的方法通过启用 ILS模式的，这意味着它会按照行跑道（鉴于飞机捕获在小角度行）。这也是方便检查出的截图和视频。那么就试试吧！更详细的说明： ＆公牛;测序流量在着陆跑道前的ILS路径。跑道被描绘为在屏幕中间的小，粗蓝线;的ILS路径是从跑道延伸的细线。为了捕捉这ILS光束，一个平面必须符合三个条件： （1）平面的ILS模式被激活， （2）在飞机必须下降足够低，以从下方拦截下滑道;蓝色圆圈标出的2000，3000和4000英尺的高度， （3）的平面必须截取在50度以下，相对于跑道一个标题中的ILS（目标约30度）。 如果正确地捕捉，它会自动跟随跑道上的线条和土地。请注意，需要一定的时间为一个平面下降到选定的高度。当飞机完全建立，这将在塔交给然后你的分数技能点。对于并行的办法，保持千英尺垂直间隔，直到两个平面定位确立。 ＆公牛;离场飞机确定其航向和速度本身（默认）;他们只需要一个指令（当它是安全的，当然）爬升到更高的高度：飞行高度层130。 ＆公牛;您也可以失去技能点，当飞机： （1）飞太接近海誓山盟（一般为：重叠的圆圈和高度差<1000英尺）， （2）离开空域（外灰色圆圈），同时如果他们离职，但等于或低于FL100离开领空， （3）复飞/去变通。 ＆公牛;你必须控制飞机的数量大约是一样的，你拥有的技能点数量：高技能的价值，你必须处理更多的飞机。您也可以实现“目标”由正确的方式登陆一定量的飞机。 ＆公牛;有些飞机有一个额外的“RD”标签;只有这些飞机需要降落在次要“RD”机场。 在菜单中有喜欢的速度倍增的选项，而“技能上限”一个更轻松的游戏：这个“上限”限制技能值，使入站流量的速度也将被限制。其它参数是随机选择的。在雷达屏幕上双击放大/缩小。 有关详细说明去http://startgrid.blogspot.nl/2013/11/endless-atc-instructions.html 功能 ＆公牛;飞机的无尽的金额，多跑道， ＆公牛;给雷达引导像一个真正的空中交通管制员， ＆公牛;业务量，适应你的技能水平， ＆公牛;暂停和高仿真速度模式， ＆公牛;自动保存游戏;恢复你离开的地方， ＆公牛;不需要互联网连接， ＆公牛;没有广告， ＆公牛;它是免费的。 本场比赛发挥最好的大屏幕。如果你有反馈，请给我一个电子邮件。

column19: 这是最好的纸牌游戏为Android。如果你喜欢你的电脑上的纸牌，然后你会喜欢这种休闲卡Android游戏的免费版本。图形是非常beautifull和游戏是简单明了。你可以cusomise游戏卡和游戏背景。你甚至可以通过OpenFeint的竞争与朋友。我们也有几个我们挑战你解开的成就！ 免费纸牌的特点： - 最佳solitare游戏 - 选择处理1卡或3卡 - 克朗代克与经典solitair规则 - Beautifull扑克牌 - Preety背景 - 惊人的特殊效果 - 免费游戏 - 与OpenFeint的全球高分 - 真棒成就 你可以玩这个游戏单独或您可以与朋友一起玩。克朗代克solitare是一个伟大的益智游戏，这是最好看的Andr​​oid市场上最好的工作之一。这个免费的纸牌游戏，是您对您的电脑有solitare类似，但是好了很多前瞻性的伟大工程。 其他类似的游戏就像纸牌突击或纸牌包豪华有很多变化，包括接龙，蜘蛛，纸牌或piramid的游戏，但因为这些版本有很多的模式，他们没有在其中任何伟大的。我们正在上的空当接龙和蜘蛛版本太多，但我们打算花费了大量的时间和细节，对待每一个版本作为一个独立的单机游戏。所以留下的空当接龙纸牌，蜘蛛纸牌，纸牌接龙和甚至piramid纸牌tooned。 许多人指克朗代克作为耐心，或solitaire.If你要播放的标准接龙这是只有真正好的版本为Android，毫不妥协。如果你喜欢蜘蛛纸牌，空当接龙纸牌，我们将这些版本也很快。我们希望做出最好的纸牌游戏，它需要时间。克朗代克Solitare自由是来自我们的纸牌免费包许多纸牌游戏之一。 经典的纸牌是最好的，我们喜欢玩的经典游戏。这个版本的经典接龙保持经典的感觉，但增加了beautifull卡和背景。这个经典的纸牌是通过一段时间的最佳选择。 Other similar games like solitaire blitz or solitaire pack deluxe have lots of variations of the game including freecell, spider, tripeaks or piramid, but because these versions have lots of modes they aren't great in any of them. We are working on a freecell and spider version too, but we intend to spend a lot of time on details and treat every version as a stand alone game. So stay tooned for the freecell solitaire, the spider solitaire, the tripeaks solitaire and even the piramid solitaire.

column19: We all love soccer – but how badly do you want to win? FootLOL lets you use mines, shields, aliens, cows, guns and many more cheats to decimate the opposing team and protect your players. Play against your friend or a AI opponent. As a manager, you’ll take your team through a few training matches, before being unleashed on new planets. As you go, you’ll unlock new gadgets, improve your players’ performance, and unlock new kits and hats for them to wear. Opponents often have the same tricks you do so it’s not as simple as knocking the ball in the back of the net. You’ll need to fulfill the conditions for each level – which might mean losing, or fighting your way back from defeat! Thankfully, the addictive action, cute characters and the best arsenal seen in a soccer game since, well, Arsenal make every match too close to call. Once you’ve finished FootLOL’s tournament mode, you can play against the computer or go online for gripping multiplayer. With the player who’s best at cheating winning, FootLOL is a funny old game! • Four planets, each with several types of field • Multiplayer • Hilarious soccer chaos • Highly customizable characters and teams • Sixty levels • Crazy abilities and tools FootLOL community on Facebook https://www.facebook.com/footlol.epic.fail _____________________________________ FOLLOW US: @Herocraft WATCH US: youtube.com/herocraft LIKE US: facebook.com/herocraft.games

ipadio is the easiest and fastest way to create and share audio. Use this free app to record, edit, and upload audio to the web. The ipadio app lets you record up to 60 minutes of high quality audio and then add titles, descriptions, images, and geo-locate your recording before it is instantly uploaded to your ipadio.com account or cross-posted to your Twitter, Facebook, Wordpress, Posterous, Blogger, Live Spaces, or LiveJournal accounts. You can also edit out sections of your recording using our in-app editing suite. Each audio clip also comes with its own selection of embed codes, which you can grab off your online ipadio account, meaning you can also put your recording on your website. The ipadio app is designed to seek out the best connectivity possible and to upload your data bit by bit, depending on your bandwidth. So, if you’ve got weak signal, you can just hit upload and close the app, and ipadio will keep working away until the file is uploaded. Our app offers the option to either record and upload, or live stream your audio straight to the web, direct from your phone. ipadio is used by podcasters, educators, radio DJs, travel bloggers, charities, and individuals around the world to create and upload high quality audio with minimal fuss. By downloading the app, an online account at ipadio.com will also be created for you. From there, you can access additional features such as embed codes, RSS feeds, download options, listener stats, and the chance to adjust your privacy settings. ipadio is also a great way to record phone calls. Call one of our local ipadio numbers and enter your unique PIN. You can then add a call and merge the two, meaning both sides of the conversation will be recorded and the audio automatically appears in your online account. But don’t forget to tell people first if you’re recording them! ipadio also now offers a video recording option in our app. This feature was developed for the London 2012 Paralympic Games and allows you to record and instantly broadcast up to three minutes of high quality video. If you would like this feature enabled on your app please email app@ipadio.com. Please note that we are currently limiting this feature to charities, educators, and journalists, but are working on making this available to all consumers as soon as we can. For any more information or support in using ipadio, please email help@ipadio.com. ipadio是创造和共享音频的最简单和最快的方式。 使用这个免费的应用程序来录制，编辑，并上传音频到网上。 该ipadio应用程序可以让您录制长达60分钟的高品质的音频，然后添加标题，描述，图像和地理定位拍摄之前它会立即上传到您的ipadio.com帐户或交叉张贴到您的Twitter，Facebook， WordPress的，Posterous，博客，Live Spaces的，或LiveJournal的帐号。您也可以使用我们在应用程序的编辑套件编辑您的录音部分。每个音频剪辑还带有自己的选择的嵌入代码，你可以抢了你的网上ipadio账户，这意味着你也可以把你的记录在您的网站。 该ipadio应用程序的设计寻求可能的最佳连接，并通过位来上传您的数据位，这取决于你的带宽。所以，如果你已经有了微弱的信号，你可以打上传并关闭应用程序，并ipadio将继续在外打工，直到该文件被上传。 我们的应用程序提供了两种选项，记录并上传，或实时流音频直接到网上，直接从您的手机。 ipadio是使用播客，教育，广播的DJ，旅游博客，慈善机构和世界各地的个人创建和上传高品质的音频最小做文章。 通过下载应用程序，在ipadio.com在线帐户也将被用于创建。从那里，你可以访问附加功能，如嵌入代码，RSS订阅，下载选项，监听状态，并有机会调整您的隐私设置。 ipadio也是一个伟大的方式来记录电话。请致电我们的当地ipadio号码中的一个，并输入您唯一的PIN。然后，您可以添加一个呼叫并合并这两个，这意味着通话双方将被记录和音频自动出现在您的网上帐户。但是，不要忘记告诉人们首先如果你正在录制他们！ ipadio现在还提供在我们的应用程序的视频录制选项。此功能是为2012年伦敦残奥会的开发，并允许您记录和实时广播长达三分钟的高质量视频。如果你想这个功能对您的应用程序启用请电邮app@ipadio.com。请注意，我们目前限制这个功能给慈善机构，教育工作者和记者，但正在努力使这个提供给所有消费者只要我们能做到。 如需使用ipadio任何更多的信息或支持，请发送电子邮件至help@ipadio.com。

column19: 什么是一元猎宝？ 选择喜欢的商品，选择要参与的人次并支付，直接充值并获得对应人次猎宝号码。 怎么计算中奖？ 1.商品的最后一个猎宝号码分配完毕后，将公示最后分配时间点前本站全部商品的最后50个参与时间； 2.将这50个时间的数值进行求和（得出数值A）（每个时间按时、分、秒、毫秒的顺序组合，如19:25:15.283则为192515283）； 3.为保证公平公正公开，系统还会取最近下一期中国福利彩票“老时时彩”的揭晓结果（一个五位数值B）； 4.（数值A+数值B）除以该商品总需人次得到的余数 + 原始数 10000001，得到最终中奖猎宝号码，拥有该猎宝号码者，直接获得该商品。 【安全保障】金山毒霸，安全保障。 【接近梦想】一元钱=大大的梦想。零钱换梦想，要啥有啥。 【趣味体验】一元钱=欢快的购物+刺激的开奖。 【中奖晒单】晒出你的运气，做个人人都羡慕的红人。 【奖品丰富】手机平板、电脑办公、数码影音等等等等应有尽有。

America's National Parks (previously National Park Tours) provides information on each of the 58 national parks. The entire application has been rewritten and updated. It tells you how to get there, when to go and how to visit. It provides park maps, a topographic map for hiking, and information on park activities. It is a platform for sharing your experience of the park visit. You can create your own park tour with your points of interest (POI) on the maps. The POI contains comments, photos, and trails. You can share your tours with others or store them locally for future use. With your customized tour, you can create your own tour guide, or photo journey of your park visit. It is integrated with Flickr and Google. The park information is packaged in a tour for each park. Once loaded, the tours can be used without network connectivity. 美国的国家公园（以前国家公园之旅）提供​​的58个国家公园中的每个信息。已被重写整个应用程序和更新。它会告诉你到那里怎么走，什么时候去，以及如何访问。它提供远足，公园地图，地形图和游园活动的信息。它是一个平台，分享你的经验公园参观。与您在地图上的兴趣点（POI），您可以创建自己的公园游览。 POI包含评论，照片，和小径。您可以与他人分享您的旅游行程或本地存储它们，以备将来使用。您定制的巡演，你可以创建自己的导游，或者您的游园之旅照片。它集成了Flickr和谷歌。公园信息被打包在游览各公园。一旦加载，没有网络连接，可用于旅游。

column19: Paris - 1940 You are Artemis, a spy on the trail of a notorious traitor in this 1940s, film noir style, point and click adventure game. Life in the French capital has settled down to an almost indifferent acceptance of the occupation. The Germans, enjoying ‘La Bonne Vie’, are taking full advantage of what Paris has to offer. You, a British spy, have been dropped into Northern France with instructions to infiltrate your way into the capital to liaise with the much hidden and secretive French Resistance. Relive history by playing as the famed British Agent, Artemis. Find yourself following the trail of a known member of the French Resistance in this 1940 film noir style point and click adventure game. As Artemis, you will need to solve challenging puzzles; search rooms; find hidden objects; use a real life enigma machine and spot the clues that are hidden throughout the streets of Paris as you find yourself playing a dangerous game of cat and mouse with a notorious British Agent working for the Nazis. Can you track down your missing contact and uncover the mystery surrounding a notorious spy loose on the streets of Paris? GAME FEATURES Relive history in this riveting storyline steeped in mystery based on a notorious British spy A unique take on the well known and popular point and click style adventure games Stunning high resolution, film noir style graphics with atmospheric music that transports you back through history to 1940s Paris Hours of fun, innovative and intriguing point and click puzzles to work your way through Access to hints and answers page to help with the most challenging of puzzles Use an enigma machine, spot hidden objects and escape from the nazis in a unique WW2 setting The Paris Dossier brings together history, film noir, mystery and adventure, and puts these elements into a fun point and click style adventure game set in 1940 Paris. Solve puzzles, spot clues, use an enigma machine and catch a spy. Escape the nazis and spot ways to complete your mission. 1940, WW2 Paris will literally come alive in this new mystery game. If you like any of these things, you will enjoy the Paris Dossier: adventure, mystery, film noir, puzzles, spot hidden objects, point and click games, history, spies, agents, and daring escapes! 巴黎 - 1940 您是阿蒂米斯，在20世纪40年代这个，黑色电影的风格，点一个臭名昭著的叛徒的线索是间谍，并单击冒险游戏。 生活在法国首都已经安顿下来，以一种近乎冷漠的接受职业。德国人，享受着“香格里拉Bonne Vie宾馆”，被充分利用的东西巴黎所提供的。你，一个英国间谍，已经下降到法国北部与指示渗透的方式进入资本，并与很多隐藏的秘密的法国抵抗。 通过发挥作为著名的英国代理，阿蒂米斯重温历史。发现自己下面的法国抵抗在这1940黑色电影风格的角度已知成员的踪迹，并单击冒险游戏。由于阿蒂米斯，你将需要解决具有挑战性的难题;搜索房间;找到隐藏的物体;用现实生活中的谜机和发现那些隐藏在整个巴黎街头的线索，你会发现自己在玩一场危险的游戏猫捉老鼠的一个臭名昭著的英国代理工作的纳粹。你可以跟踪你丢失的接触，揭开神秘面纱周围的一个臭名昭著的间谍宽松的巴黎街头？ 游戏特色 重温历史的基础上臭名昭著的英国间谍这种铆接的故事情节沉浸在神秘面纱 一本独特的著名和流行点和点击式的冒险游戏 令人惊叹的高分辨率，黑色电影风格的图形与大气中的音乐传送回你穿越历史，以20世纪40年代巴黎 乐趣，创新，有趣点时间，点击拼图，通过合作的方式 使用提示和解答页面，以帮助最具挑战性的难题 使用一个谜机器，发现隐藏的对象，并从一个独特的设置二战纳粹逃脱 巴黎档案汇集历史，黑色电影，神秘和冒险，并把这些元素融入到一个有趣的指向和点击式的冒险游戏在1940年巴黎成立。解决难题，发现线索，用一个谜机，赶上一个间谍。逃脱纳粹和现货的方式来完成你的使命。 1940年，二战巴黎将字面上来活着在这个新的谜游戏。 如果你喜欢这些事情，你将享受巴黎档案： 冒险，神秘，黑色电影，拼图，现货隐藏的对象，指向和点击游戏，历史，间谍，代理和大胆的越狱！

column11: 深圳市宏智力科技有限公司
column19: 内容提要 【应用特色】 零基础科学减压，情绪调节 真人语音引导，自定义训练时长 实时α、β脑电波走势图及减压数据报告； 放松数值达标，自动进阶下一训练章节 【应用介绍】 「开心禅」是由开发商Macrotellect专为都市高压人群量身定制的专业大脑减压APP应用。 「开心禅」依据美国威斯康辛大学理查‧大卫森、安东尼‧露兹等科学家进行的【禅修对精研禅修者脑部影响】即【头脑成像和行为】的科学实验，结合“世界上最快乐的人”——咏给·明就仁波切体悟实证的经验基础，藉由各种易于理解与简单易行的禅修方法，整合理论和禅修方法，辅以尖端EEG脑电波探测技术，实时了解禅修练习中的大脑变化，达到较高层次的大脑专注及潜能唤醒，实现大脑本质的洞察力及深度放松体验。 《开心禅》分为多个章节，展示日常生活中简单实用的禅修方法。 根据不同章节的训练数据，开出不同数量的荷花。荷花数量越多，身心越放松。 【禅修好处】 注意力更易集中 减少焦虑和压力 改善睡眠降低血压 防止抑郁及增强免疫力 减轻急性和习惯性疼痛 提高呼吸效率和肺活量 增强强迫性行为和识别能力

新锐主流杂志《看世界》于1995年创刊，是一本以华人利益关联与国际化视角，反映在全球化浪潮席卷下的政治、经济、文化生活的综合性的新中产者个性读物。 《看世界》是广州日报报业集团主力期刊，坚持“中国立场，国际视野”的报刊理念，是一本充满活力的全方位反映当今世界政治、经济、文化、科技、军事的综合性的中国名刊，具有高度社会影响力的新锐媒体，当今有志青年必备的生活手册，思想读本；是一本连续数年获得中国“百种重点期刊奖”的精品期刊。

Now you will have access to information about your Cochlear Baha system wherever you are and whenever you need it! 「英雄围城：口袋版 Hero Siege: Pocket Edition」是一款像素化的生存类围城游戏。游戏初始的时候，玩家会在火炉旁选取英雄，这个场景不禁让人想起了暗黑破坏神中也有类似的场景。 总体上来说，本作属于一款动作类型的生存游戏，玩家只能呆在一小块封闭的区域中，等待一波又一波敌人的来袭。玩家需要操控自己召唤的角色，在这片牢笼中生存下来。 地图中随机散落了瓦罐，宝箱等物品，玩家需要搜集金币来购买一些道具，寻找钥匙来开启宝箱获得稀有的武器和能力，更要通过击杀怪物获取经验值来提升自己的特有技能。 这款游戏设置了不同的难度和区域，当玩家击杀了区域 BOSS 之后，便会开启下一个区域的传送门。在地图结构上游戏采用了随机地牢的形式，你的每一次启动游戏，都会产生一个不一样的区域地图，这也大大加强了游戏的难度和可玩性。 虽说是像素风格，但是画面的表现力一点也不差，游戏采用了 3D 建模的像素风，通过 45 度的俯视角将整个区域展现在玩家面前。火把燃烧时光线的明暗变化，树枝和草垛的摆动，还有泛着微光的湖水，即便是在这样一个看似粗糙的画质下也能体验到真实的动态视觉。 喜欢怀旧的暗黑老玩家们，还不赶紧来体验一把当年的感觉啊。

《逃亡酷跑》是为手机用户量身打造的一款精品手机游戏。在传承跑酷游戏诸多经典玩法的基础上， 是继《天天酷跑》之后推出的又一部经典酷跑系列游戏，《逃亡酷跑》在沿袭传统玩法的基础上，为玩家带来了更为得心应手的跑酷体验。 【巧妙关卡，“酷跑达人”获挑战】 游戏上手容易，但是如果真的想要成为“酷跑达人”却不是那么轻而易举的事情哦！《逃亡酷跑》的关卡设计非常巧妙，在不同的关卡中还会碰到不同的地形以及各种不同的障碍，使自我不断获得挑战及快乐体验。 【新增“下滑”操作+僵尸木箱】 继承经典酷跑游戏的基础玩法，新增“下滑”操作，乐趣翻番。区别于市面上常见的酷跑游戏，《逃亡酷跑》的操作只需两根手指就可以完全搞定。按“跳跃”键向上跳跃，按“下滑”键俯身下滑——掌握了这两个动作你就已经可以完全无顾虑的在游戏中勇往直前了。另外，游戏还增添了僵尸木箱，一定要小心前面的僵尸木箱哦~非常刺激！

Put your swordsman skills to the test as you use your fingers to slice and dice veggies of all shapes and sizes in Veggie Samurai. *************************** Veggie Samurai is an addictive, pickup-and-play action game that puts you in the heart of all-out veggie carnage. ****** 7 DISTINCT GAME MODES ****** --- Samurai Mode - 3 Lives. No time limit. Avoid dropping veggies. Avoid poison vials. --- Hardcore Mode - Only 1 life. No mistakes. --- Harmony Mode - Time based. No poison. No lives. More action. More combos. --- Chaos Mode - All Out veggie smack-down. 3x the pace. --- Sort Mode - Selective slicing. Only the chosen veggie shall pass. --- Match Mode - Frenzied action. Spot the matches. Slice combos. Use the "Wild Pepper". HUGE combo sizes. --- Training Mode - Free play. No time limit. No hazards. ****** FEATURES ****** --- Slicing AND Dicing allows you to cut up veggies multiple times (some veggies can be diced a surprising number of times...) --- Watch your score skyrocket as you perform Slice Combos, Multi-Dice Combos, Dice Chains, Pea Killers, Onion Blossoms, and more! --- Score big bonus points with Rare MEGA VEGGIES that can be triggered by figuring out the secret, in-game prerequisites --- Keep your eyes peeled and score big points with the rare bonus veggies! --- Fight for global bragging rights atop the Open Feint Leaderboards --- 32 Achievements and counting… (as if dicing veggies to bits wasn’t enough) Now go out and prove your worth as a VEGGIE SAMURAI… Veggie Samurai HD is in no way associated with Halfbrick Studios and/or the game Fruit Ninja.

column19: Redneck Hunter The most exciting animal hunter available! Amazing HD graphics, optimized performance, advanced animations and addictive gameplay. Drive a car to smash animals and hunt them with awesome weapons like: - Tomahawk - Bazooka - Molotov Cocktail - Desert Eagle - Shotgun Avoid the strong bears, kill the weak animals to gain points! Collect gasoline and find optimal routes. Let's see how long you can survive. GAME You have to kill as many animals as possible. The bears will get stronger and faster with the time so you have to avoid them or kill them quickly. You have to collect the gasoline on the map to keep the car going. QUALITY SETTINGS The game will automatically detect which quality settings to apply for your device, but you can change them in the settings menu. SIMPLE CONTROLS To use a weapon - tap on the screen. By default, you will use gyroscope to steer a car, but you can change it to buttons in settings menu. Use gas and brake pedal to control the speed. Good Luck! 乡下人猎人 最令人兴奋的动物的猎人可用！ 令人惊叹的高清显卡，性能优化，先进的动画和令人上瘾的游戏。 开车粉碎动物，猎杀它们与真棒武器，如： - 战斧 - 火箭筒 - 莫洛托夫鸡尾酒 - 沙漠之鹰 - 散弹枪 避免强熊，杀弱的动物获得积分！收集汽油，并找到最佳路由。让我们来看看你能存活多久。 游戏 你必须杀死尽可能多的动物越好。空头将获得更强和更快的时间，所以你必须避免他们还是很快杀死他们。你要收集地图上的汽油，以保持车内去。 画质设置 游戏会自动检测哪些质量设置以应用为您的设备，但你可以在设置菜单中更改它们。 简单的控制 使用武器 - 轻点屏幕上。默认情况下，您将使用陀螺仪来引导一辆车，但你可以在设置菜单将其更改为按钮。使用油门和制动踏板控制车速。 祝你好运！

column19: 迷尚钢琴是一个音乐游戏，也是钢琴演奏最简单的方法，只需轻点上的任意位置的钢琴演奏下一个音符或你所选取的歌曲。所有的节奏都可以由你双手的来控制，可快可慢，在这个版本中，有两种模式可以玩：一种是有很多免费的歌曲可以选来弹奏，著名古典音乐作者作曲以及不同的艺术家演奏的歌曲 ，如：云雀，糟糕的罗曼史，哈利路亚，只要给我一个理由，麻木了，让她去，尝试等等！闭上眼睛都可以玩！另一种模式是自由弹奏，随意弹出你喜欢的歌曲，和许多其他流行的旋律！这很有趣吧！

************************************************** 키즈영어 Pro 에서는 부분유료구매가 가능합니다. 한번 결재후 프로그램 삭제전 까지 무제한 사용 가능합니다. ************************************************** 세계 영어 명작동화,동요,파닉스,어휘, Chant 등 종합 영어교육 프로그램 전세계 영어교육 최고 전문가들의 250 여개의 동영상 어린이 뿐 아니라 조기영어 학습 기회를 갖지 못한 언니, 오빠, 엄마, 아빠, 할머니, 할아버지 까지 온 가족이 재미있게 영어를 배울 수 있는 종합 영어 교육 프로그램입니다. 메인화면의 아이콘을 누르시면 티스토어에서 단말기 사이즈별로 최적화된 프로그램을 다운 받을 수 있습니다. (무료) 어린이의 애창곡 곰세마리를 영어로는 어떻게 부를까? 이솝우화뿐 아니라 세계명작 동화를 움직이는 동영상과 함께 영어로 배우면 얼마나 좋을까? 영어는 기초부터 발음을 제대로 배워야 한다는데 이 파닉스라는 어려운 학문을 전공자의 강의 없이도 쉽게 반복해서 배울 수는 없을까? 단어를 무조건 암기만 시키지 말고 연상 작용으로 쉽고 재미있으면서도 많이 암기할 수 있는 방법은 없을 까? 고민 하셨죠? 이제 이 유튜브 키즈영어가 모두 해결했습니다. 지루한 이동 시간 중에도 단 몇분의 짜투리 시간을 이용하여 아이들에게 보여 준다면 그것으로 재미와 학습의 효과를 볼 수 있도록 구성하였습니다. 어릴 때 부터 영어는 영어로 배워야 한다는 철칙이 이제는 상식이 되었습니다. 그러나 그것을 실천하기에는 너무나 큰 시간과 노력과 비용이 든다는 사실 또한 우리를 슬프게 했습니다. 비싼 돈 들여 싫다는 아이를 원어민 학원의 종일반에 보내지 않아도 그런 여유가 없다해도 위험을 무릎쓰고 조기 유학 보내지 않아도 엄마 아빠의 영어가 유창하지 못해도 이제는 영어를 영어답게 가르칠수 있는 아니 재미있게 놀면서 배울 수 있는 프로그램을 체험해 보십시요. 전세계 영어 학습프로그램의 권위자들이 만들어 놓은 유튜브 동영상을 스마트폰으로 직접 감상하며 쉽게 배울 수 있도록 영어교육 전문가가 직접 컨텐츠를 정리하고 개발하였습니다. column19: Do you dream of riding a Harley Davidson Fat Bob motorcycle? Now, with our "Harley Davidson Fat Bob HD LWP" your dream can become a reality ! We would like to present a combination of beauty and power of technology based on your favorite motorbike model and really helpful widget with digital clock, digital compass, infromation from battery temperature sensor and battery level.Also, In this application we have implemented a smooth parallax effect with wonderful hd background. Our live wallpaper optimized for phones and tablets modes, contains hd graphic and great atmosphere for all motorcycles lovers from true moto maniacs.The 2013 Harley-Davidson Dyna Fat Bob FXDF model is a Dark Custom cruiser with a big motorcycle feel. The Harley Fat Bob model features a powerful air-cooled Twin Cam 103 Harley engine with 6 speed cruise drive transmission, providing more performance power for passing, hill-climbing, and riding with passenger and cargo. For the custom style you want, the Fat Bob model motorcycle's beefy handlebar is truly reminiscent of an aggressive quarter mile monster. And with the wires routed through the steel, you get a clean, minimal look with nothing standing in your way of the open road. Add to that the wide stance and 16 inch front wheel, and you have a cool fat custom look with a powerful big twin engine.Also, In this application we have implemented a smooth parallax effect with wonderful hd background. Game Lokal Indonesia 简介: 王子蒂博尼哥罗，来自印度尼西亚的民族英雄，是日惹苏丹，苏丹Hamengkubuwono |||的长子王子。他反对荷兰殖民统治，并在Java战争（1825年至1830年）重要组成部分。阅读此https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diponegoro =================================== =============================这个游戏不告诉你蒂博尼哥罗王子真正的历史。这个游戏只是想提高蒂博尼哥罗字符作为民族英雄殖民保卫中Java的领土。游戏特点： - 6楼：尖竹，泥仓，火焰箭，巨箭，电动自行车和狙击手 - 16的敌人类型 - 26级，并会增加 - 在游戏中蒂博尼哥罗的英雄人物 - 许多技能和项目，这将有助于你完成任务 - 塔可以升级到5级 - 印度尼西亚和英语本地化 - 爪哇岛地图游戏是挤满了游戏塔国防部预计将能够恢复印尼国家英雄的玩家内存。至少通过玩这个游戏中，玩家将开始寻找蒂博尼哥罗，到底是谁。

Vaper's Toolbox was designed specifically for those vaper's who are wanting to build their own coils. It helps newcomers and experts alike with the complex calculations required to build the perfect coil. It currently consists of four tools: 1. Wire Cutter helps you calculate how long each piece of coil wire needs to be to achieve the proper resistance. Supports single, dual, triple, and quad coil design. Wire types supported are Kanthal (A-1, A, and D), Nichrome (60 and 80), SS (304, 316, 316L), NI200, and T1 as well as Kanthal A-1 Ribbon wire. It can also display calculated lengths in inches, cm, mm, and even fractional inches (4 3/16). 2. Coil Builder helps determine how many wraps the coil needs to be using the correct length of wire. Using the wire length from Wire Cutter along with the coil diameter and estimated length of the leads, it will calculate the exact number of wraps you should use. Diameter size can be input as inches, cm, or mm, and can be set independently of the length settings. 3. Power Tool calculates either voltage or wattage at which you are vaping based on your inputs and setting. Basically a simple Ohm's Law calculator designed to help determine the power or voltage you should use. 4. Converter is a new conversion tool that can convert inches to mm and back as well as convert fractions to decimals. Try it out. We think you will agree that Vaper's Toolbox is a must have for any e-cigarette enthusiast that is planning on building their own coils. This app should work with any android version 2.2 or later. NOTE: The latest update changed the way the Power Tool works. I would like to hear from you what you think of the new design on the Power Tool page. Just shoot me an email. Also if you have any issues or would like to see additional wire types and/or gauges or features added, send me an email. Vaper的工具箱专为谁是想建立自己的线圈的vaper的设计。它可以帮助新人和专家的一致好评与建立完善的线圈所需的复杂计算。目前，它由四个工具： 1.线切割机帮助你计算出多久，每片线圈导线的需要是实现适当性。支持单，双，三和四线圈设计。支持线类型有康泰尔（A-1，A和D），镍铬合金（60和80），SS（304，316，316L），NI200，和T1以及康泰尔A-1带状线。它也可以在显示英寸计算的长度，厘米，毫米，甚至分数英寸（4 3/16）。 2.线圈生成器有助于确定多少涡卷线圈需要使用电线的正确长度。 使用从线切割机的线长度沿与线圈直径及引线的估计长度，将计算出应该使用包裹物的具体数量。直径大小可以是输入作为英寸，厘米，或毫米，并且可以独立的长度设置来设置。 3.电动工具计算电压或功率，你是根据你的投入和设置vaping处。 基本上是一个简单的欧姆定律计算器旨在帮助确定功率或电压你应该使用。 4.转换器是一个新的转换工具，可以转换英寸到毫米，背部以及分数转换为小数。 试试看。我们认为你会同意，Vaper的工具箱是一个必须有任何电子香烟爱好者正在筹划建设自己的线圈。 这个程序应该与任何Android版本2.2或更高版本。 注：最新的更新改变了电动工具的工作方式。我想从你听到你的想法的电动工具，页面上的新设计。只是拍我的电子邮件。此外，如果您有任何问题或想看到更多的导线类型和/或量规或添加的功能，给我发电子邮件。

column4: 小小农场。动物、拖拉机和大冒险！
column8: 经典-模拟-模拟经营-创意-恶搞-农场-田园-全民农场
column19: 你置身农场中：这里有动物、拖拉机，还有众多神秘冒险。 在我们的隐藏物品游戏中探索乡间生活，畅享90多个互动故事、有趣的声音和无限乐趣！ ++ Toddlers Seek & Find，我们开发的一款超赞的应用程序已经获得超过400万次的下载次数。 ++ 让2-6岁的儿童快乐感受生机勃勃的田园农场生活，体验真正的互动冒险！  ++ 四个场景中90多个隐藏的动画和故事等待你去发现，儿童和家长可以体验农场生活，同时发现众多情节丰富的故事： 场景1——游戏亮点（农场中） ------------------------------ 帮助农夫种甜菜。 喂驴。 给小猪洗澡！ 骄傲的公鸡巡视每个人。 场景2——游戏亮点（乡间） ------------------------------ 用联合收割机在农田收割庄稼并播种。 让树屋中的男孩滑下钢索。 弄明白绵羊为什么这么有趣。 骑小马：漫步、小跑或慢跑！ 场景3——游戏亮点（谷仓中） ------------------------------ 给绵羊剃最有趣的发型！ 用你喜欢的颜色绘彩蛋。 给动物喂食。 帮助农场修拖拉机。 场景4——游戏亮点（夜晚的农场） ------------------------------ 现在月亮出来了。 动物都睡觉了。 但老屋门窗后面还有什么动静？去一探究竟！ 更多亮点 ------------------------------ + 大量农场和乡村生活主题的可爱故事。 + 为什么老奶奶对踏板车唠叨个不停？ + 山羊为什么抓所有苹果？ + 母牛喜欢吃什么？ + 和孩子们在湖边玩！ + 渔夫为什么只钓到一只鞋？ + 机器人在谷仓中做什么？  ……还有很多事等你来做： 完成每个场景中的任务，弄明白为什么绵羊和猪是亲密好友，融入我们可爱的农场世界！ 我们的承诺 ------------------------------ + 您的孩子会发现许多相互关联的小故事。 + 父母们也会不停地寻找新的隐藏细节。 + 不仅仅您的孩子会爱上这款应用程序。 支持的语言 ------------------------------ + 阿拉伯语 + 中文（繁体和简体） + 荷兰语 + 英语 + 法语 + 德语 + 意大利语 + 日语 + 韩语 + 挪威语 + 葡萄牙语（巴西） + 俄 + 西班牙语 + 瑞典语 + 土耳其语 技术支持说明 ------------------------------ 我们已经在所有设备上彻底测试了这款应用程序。然而，如果您遇到问题，我们无法根据评论部分中的评语提供技术支持，请谅解。请给我们发送电子邮件，这样我们可以即时回复并提供帮助。非常感谢。

Prepare to wake up softly assisted by an animated sunrise alarm. Each alarm can have a sunrise pre-alarm configured that will launch a nice sun animation: dawn, sunrise, morning, noon. You can configure the duration of each of the four phases (you can preview it on youtube: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iTmdwpG59t8).The sunrise alarm can be associated with a sound or just let the light wake you up. It begins before the alarm time (10 minutes by default) and it will allow you to wake up gently under the effect of light, especially if you are during a light sleep stage. Of course the classical sound alarm can kick in if you’re not up when the time elapsed.Features:• Classical and/or sunrise alarm• Repeating or one-shot alarm• Increasing volume, volume level and vibration options• Color code to see if it’s a disabled (gray) , classical (purple) or sunrise alarm (orange)• Choose Android theme• Choose the ringtone : any music on your phone or just record a new sound• Configure the global duration or each stage of the sunrise animation• Night clock mode : current time and next alarm• Light therapy : play the animation in infinite loop to help you light up your cold winter morningsThe ad-free version is here :https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=fr.d1si.sunriseNote : Please, do not hesitate to send us your feedback at contact[at]d1si.fr. Whether it’s a bug, wishing for a new feature or just having a hard time with how the app works, we’ll do our best to provide the necessary help.

骷髅小王子 Dokuro 又名多克罗、骷髅王子救公主是一款由智龙迷城开发商GungHo制作的动作游戏。玩家要扮演可爱的小骷髅，带领着公主逃出这个布满怪物与陷阱的城堡。主角骷髅小王子多克罗要带着公主从邪恶的魔王手掌中逃脱出来。 虽然骷髅小王子多克罗平时是一个小骷髅的模样，但满足一定条件之后他就可以变身成为帅气的王子，变身之后不但可以抱起公主，还可以对敌人进行攻击。游戏的主要目的就是解开重重谜题并救出公主，玩家可以在小骷髅和王子之间进行变换，利用两者不同的能力来解开谜题。

Lightweight CSV Viewer apps. The developer of this app is authenticated to the official developer of andro Idah as a developer of a safe and secure application. https://androider.jp/developer/0942e3401a0d980f5d0f0278547838a1/ Feature 1.CSV file viewing. - Supports multiple data delimiter. (Comma, Semicolon, Space, Tab) - Display function of the line number. - The default setting screen.(You can be set from the Options menu of the file selection screen.) - Viewing the files in the ZIP file. - Sort of data display function. 　　 Operation : Tap on the header to toggle (Disabled, Enable) 　　 Supplement : By turning on the check batch setting, the same settings are applied to all columns. - Ability to select the format in the per-column sort. 倚天屠龙记为香港作家金庸所着武侠小说射雕三部曲之三 时代背景为中国元朝末年，神雕侠侣结尾的近百年后故事围绕两样兵器屠龙刀和倚天剑出场的真实历史人物包括张三丰、朱元璋、陈友谅、常遇春、徐达、汝阳王察罕帖木儿、韩林儿等等设置中的当时社会之焦点主要是以明教为首的邪派和以少林、武当为首的正派之争，以及起义军和朝廷的对抗涉及的武林秘笈包括九阳真经、九阴真经、七伤拳谱等等 小说前两章延续神雕侠侣的结尾，描述南宋末年郭襄、张君宝的经历以及武当派的起源故事正式情节从第三章开始，时为元顺帝至元二年三月廿四日（1336年5月5日） 其时江湖流传一句话武林至尊，宝刀屠龙号令天下，莫敢不从倚天不出，谁与争锋武林中人便因此而展开对倚天剑与屠龙刀两把兵器的激烈争逐

SPECIAL PRICE 50% OFF(USD 9.99 -> USD 4.99)!!! A brand new entry in the Alphadia series! Full-fledged fantasy RPG experience with stunning 3D battles! *Important Notice* Cloud Save will stop functioning starting from September 30, 2015. If you need to migrate your save data to other devices, please do it beforehand. Other functions will continue to be accessible without change. Featured on TegraZone. Now with controller support for NVIDIA SHIELD and Android TV (A game controller is necessary to play on NVIDIA SHIELD devices, including NVIDIA SHIELD tablet). Alphadia Genesis boasts a rich multifaceted story that revolves around Fray, an Archleign's guild member and Corone, a knight in the Ghalzabine Army. As their journey progresses and conflicting national interests come to the forefront, it becomes apparent that it will take more than a little work on both their parts if their relationship is to weather the boding storm on the horizon. Having been at peace for only 15 years since the end of the Energi War, the kingdoms of Archleign and Ghalzabine are once again thrust onto center stage after a murder perpetrated by a clone, whose rights and freedoms they both lobbied for, comes to light. Hoping the treaty signed to end the use of clones for conventional warfare has not been violated, a joint-investigative team is put together to find out the cause and bring those responsible to justice. However, things then appear to be far more volatile than anyone could have first imagined... Dramatic Event Scenes With a voice cast of many notable Japanese actors and actresses lending their talents to the story, significant events take on more meaning as each has life breathed into them, allowing players to become more deeply immersed in the world. *Character voices are only available in the original Japanese language. Intense 3D Battles Shifting camera angles and voiced characters are just a few of the new features that make battles more engaging than ever before! And with beautifully rendered graphics and vibrant Energi and Break Skills, players will never tire of being bloated with such a visual feast! Furthermore, with the inclusion of a highly efficient auto-battle function, portable gaming has never been this convenient! Not to be forgotten, however, roaming the land are monsters so powerful that if come upon unprepared, players will face certain doom! Energi In the world of Lagoon, there are three elementals from which all Energi flows- fire, water, and light. Learning to harness these forces will allow the player to become more adept in skills related to them, which include attack, recovery, and support. Therefore, it would be wise to become acquainted with their use as early on in the game as possible. Submembers Characters outside the battle party can cooperate in various ways through the use of Assists. Depending on the combination of submembers, attack, defense and other parameters like the critical rate can be increased. Moreover, when the Assist Gauge has been maxed out, powerful combo attacks can be unleashed with their help. *While in-app-purchase content requires additional fees, by no means it is necessary for finishing the game. *The actual price might differ depending on the region. Club Matas App giver dig en let og personlig adgang til Club Matas, ClubM og alle Matas’ produkter. Du har altid dit medlemskort ved hånden, du får besked, hvis dine yndlingsprodukter kommer på tilbud, du kan altid finde den nærmeste Matas eller ClubM Partner, og du kan let bruge dine Club Matas point på dejlige præmier. Vi har allesammen favoritprodukter, som vi bruger dagligt. Og hvad er bedre end når disse produkter er på tilbud? I Mit Skab kan du gemme alle dine yndlingsprodukter og få besked, når de er på tilbud i Matas. Hvis du står og er løbet tør for din yndlingscreme kan du nemt finde ud af hvilken Matas, der forhandler netop din creme. Foretrækker du at shoppe online, kan du med få clicks købedine produkter på matas.dk. Du har måske allerede nu prøvet at stå i et supermarked eller et stormagasin og overveje, hvad et produkt koster i Matas, hvor du jo får point for alle dine køb. Med Club Matas app’en kan du med det samme tjekke prisen og se, hvor mange point du får for dit køb. Og trænger du til endnu flere point, kan du med app’en altid finde den nærmeste ClubM partner – og altså se, hvilke andre steder ud over Matas, du OGSÅ får point for alt, hvad du køber. Desuden har du adgang til Pointshoppen, så du altid kan se hvor mange point du har og hvad du kan købe for dem. Og står du en den situation, at nogle af dine point er ved at udløbe, vil du med app’en få besked… så vi hjælper dig FØR du mister dine point. Vi håber du bliver rigtigt glad for Club Matas app’en og de mange muligheder og fordele, som den giver dig. 俱乐部麦塔斯应用程序给你一个简单和个性化使用俱乐部麦塔斯，ClubM和所有麦塔斯的产品。你总是有你的会员卡在手，您将会收到通知，如果您喜欢的产品都在报价，你总能找到最近的药店或ClubM合作伙伴，您可以轻松地在保费用你的俱乐部麦塔斯点。   我们都有我们日常使用的最喜爱的产品。这有什么好于如果产品上提供？在我的盒可以存储所有您最喜爱的产品，当他们在麦塔斯报价得到通知。   如果你站在和已用完了你最喜欢的冰淇淋，你可以很容易地找出哪些麦塔斯，谈判特定霜。如果你喜欢在网上购物，你可以用点击几下购买你的产品在matas.dk。   你可能已经尝试站在超市或百货公司，并考虑什么麦塔斯一个产品的成本，你当然得点，所有的购买。随着俱乐部麦塔斯应用程序可以即时检查的价格，看看你多少分能为您的购买。   要是你需要更多的点，可以使用应用程序总能找到最近的ClubM合作伙伴 - 从而了解哪些其他地方麦塔斯之外，你也可以得到你买到一切百分点。   此外，您还可以访问点Hoppen，所以你总能看到你多少分，你可以买到他们。和你站的情况下您的一些点是即将到期，你的应用程序得到的消息......所以我们帮你之前，你失去了你的观点。   我们希望你会真的很高兴俱乐部麦塔斯App和众多的机会和好处，它给你。

Join the millions of Moment.me users who create amazing moments every day! Turn your camera roll into multi point-of-view moments. Pick the best photos from friends and strangers nearby and create breath taking moments. Moment.me is the easiest way to capture real-life experiences. column18: 居然有怪兽闯入萌猫七仔的甜点屋，它可是出了名的神枪手，且看七仔如何一枪弄死怪兽！
column19: 神马？居然有怪兽胆敢闯入萌猫七仔的甜点屋，妄想偷吃掉七仔的美味甜点？！它们可来错地方了！我们七仔可是个威风凛凛的斗士，枪技一流的神枪手，且看七仔如何一枪弄死怪兽，保卫甜点！ 《一枪弄死它》是一款精品休闲益智游戏，玩法简单，操作轻松，游戏画面温馨可爱，每一关都有各种各样的美味甜点，非常适合女性和小朋友。您只需手指轻点，调整七仔的枪口发射子弹，射死所有怪兽就能过关！注意哦，子弹遇到障碍物会反弹，反弹九次后就会消失。你所花费的子弹数影响星星评级，花费子弹越少得到星星越多。如能一枪搞定（one shot）是最完美不过的了！相信不甘于平凡的你，会在one shot的追求道路上坚持不懈地挑战下去，获得不断冲击神技的快感！ 本游戏关卡丰富多样，各种各样缤纷多彩的甜点屋在等着你，不同阶段将给予你不同风格的挑战！随着闯关的深入，更有冰块、炸弹、滚轮、链条等等有趣的元素不断地加入进来，让游戏世界更精彩，让你的体验随时保持新鲜！

column18: 一个新的电子邮件应用程序，自动设置常用的电子邮件服务。
column19: AquaMail is an email app for Internet and Exchange mail, for Android 4.0.3 and higher. Easy automatic setup for popular email providers: Gmail, Yahoo, Hotmail, FastMail, Apple mail services (@me.com / @icloud.com), GMX, AOL, and more. Recognizes mail accounts hosted at Google Apps, Yahoo BizMail, and others. Works with many other email services via standard Internet email protocols (IMAP, POP3, SMTP). IMAP push mail (instant incoming email delivery) for those servers that support the IDLE extension (Gmail, GMX, AOL… not supported by Yahoo, for Hotmail please see the FAQ the app's web site). Microsoft Exchange is supported via IMAP or EWS: Exchange (EWS) accounts provide access to server side contacts (personal and global, with search), and Calendar sync. Recognizes mail accounts hosted at Office 365 and Exchange Online. Plays well with other email apps that you may be using to access your IMAP or EWS mailbox. Uses existing folder structure, can synchronize drafts, sent, and deleted messages. Improved security (OAUTH2) for Gmail and Hotmail. ***** Widgets (message counts, message list). Swiping in message list (actions) and between messages. Can save attachments as files. Message auto-fit (like in Gmail). Rich text formatting when writing messages (including embedding images, in the signature too). Android Wear (4.3+). OAUTH2 for Gmail (Google's preferred, "more secure" authentication method). Integration with Tasker (change settings, trigger mail check, message based events). Integration with Light Flow, Enhanced SMS & Caller ID, Cloud Print, Apex Launcher Pro, Nova Launcher / Tesla Unread, Executive Assistant, DashClock Widget. Lots of settings to configure the application just the way *you* would like. Separate settings for WiFi and mobile connections. Backup and restore of app and account settings via Dropbox, OneDrive, Box.com, Google Drive. This is the Lite version, which is limited to two accounts, no identities, and adds a promo signature to all outgoing messages with a link to the program's web site. You can add more than two accounts, use identites, and remove the promo signature by purchasing the Pro Unlocker app here on Play. The app is available in (translated into) more than a dozen languages. Please see the web site for the list, a Google Play policy won't let me include it here. ***** You can contact me at: kmansoft@gmail.com. ***** AquaMail是Internet和Exchange邮件的电子邮件应用程序，为Android 4.0.3及更高版本。 流行的电子邮件服务提供商易自动设置： 的Gmail，雅虎，Hotmail，FastMail，苹果公司的邮件服务（@ me.com / @ icloud.com），GMX，AOL等。认识到在谷歌企业应用套件，雅虎BizMail，和其他人托管的邮件帐户。 作品通过标准的互联网电子邮件协议（IMAP，POP3，SMTP）许多其他电子邮件服务。 对于那些支持空闲分机服务器IMAP邮件推送（即时传入电子邮件传送）（Gmail中，GMX，AOL ...不支持雅虎，Hotmail的请参阅常见问题的应用程序的网站）。 微软Exchange正在通过IMAP或EWS支持： 交易所（EWS）帐户可以访问服务器端的联系人（个人和全球性的，搜索），和日历同步。在认识到Office 365和Exchange Online的托管电子邮件帐户。 与您可能使用访问您的IMAP或EWS的邮箱的其他电子邮件应用打得很好。使用现有的文件夹结构，可以同步草稿箱，已发送和删除的邮件。 提高了安全性（的oauth2）针对Gmail和Hotmail。 ***** 窗口小部件（邮件数，邮件列表）。 在刷卡邮件列表（行动）和消息之间。 可以将附件保存为文件。 信息自动调整（如在Gmail中）。 编写信息时（含中嵌入图像，在签名太）富文本格式。 Android Wear（4.3+）。 OAuth2以Gmail的（谷歌的首选，“更安全”的认证方法）。 集成塔斯克（更改设置，触发邮件检查，基于消息的事件）。 集成光流动，增强型短信和来电显示，云打印，顶点启动临，新启动/特斯拉未读，行政助理，DashClock的Widget。 设置很多配置应用程序只是*你*会喜欢的方式。支持WiFi和移动连接单独的设置。 备份和透过Dropbox，OneDrive，Box.com，谷歌云端硬盘应用程序和帐户设置恢复。 这是精简版的版本，这是仅限于两个账户，没有身份，并增加了一个促销签名所有待发邮件的链接到程序的网站。 您可以添加两个以上的账户，使用identites，并在这里购买Pro解锁应用在游戏中移除促销签名。 该应用程序是（翻译成）十几个语言的详细资料。请参阅网站的列表，谷歌Play政策不会让我包括在这里。 ***** kmansoft@gmail.com：您可以与我联系。 *****

column19: 逻辑中有三种逻辑推理的方式：演绎、归纳和溯因。给定前提、结论和规则，而前提导致结论，则可分别解释如下：演绎用来决定'结论'。它使用规则和前提来推导出结论。数学家通常使用这种推理。归纳用来决定规则。它借由大量的 前提 和 结论 所组成的例子来学习 规则。科学家通常使用这种推理。溯因用来决定前提。它借由结论和规则来支援前提并解释结论。诊断和侦探通常使用这种推理。

This app has been incorporated into the Android Tipitaka app - please download that app for updates: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.yuttadhammo.tipitaka ======================== Simple app for looking up Pali words in four different Pali<>English dictionaries. Available dictionaries include: CPED - Concise Pali-English Dictionary CEPD - Concise English-Pali Dictionary DPPN - Dictionary of Pali Proper Names PED - Pali-English Dictionary The app uses Velthuis input scheme (aa = ā, .t = ṭ, "n = ṅ, etc.). Pali is the language of the historic Buddha: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pali and is the language of the Theravada Buddhist Tipitaka. 这已被纳入“大藏经”的应用程序的Andr​​oid应用程序 - 请下载该应用程序的更新： https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.yuttadhammo.tipitaka ======================== 寻找巴利文的话，在四个不同的巴利语<>英语词典的简单的应用程序。 可用的字典包括： CPED - 简明巴利文英词典 经建会 - 简明英语巴利语词典 DPPN - 巴利专有名词词典 PED - 巴利文英词典 应用程序使用Velthuis输入方案（AA = A，T = T，“N = N等）。 巴利文是历史悠久的佛的语言： http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pali 是上座部佛教“大藏经”的语言。

In this tutorial series in which you will learn Flash right from the beginning..Improve and master your flash skill with this playlist of flash tutorial..Learn :+ Basic Motion Tween+ Generating Random Numbers+ Variables+ How to make sprites transparent+ Hot to add movie clips to stage using code+ While and For loops+ Tic Tac Toe Game+ Functions+ Play sound and Change mouse cursor+ Clicking through movie clips & Classic motion tween+ Module Operator+ Basic Calculator+ Set Focus to Textfield and Press Enter+ Array 3D & 2D+ Document class / Using code in External FilesAdobe Flash (formerly called "Macromedia Flash") is a multimedia and software platform used for authoring of vector graphics, animation, games and rich Internet applications (RIAs) that can be viewed, played and executed in Adobe Flash Player. Flash is frequently used to add streamed video or audio players, advertisement and interactive multimedia content to web pages, although usage of Flash on websites is declining.Flash manipulates vector and raster graphics to provide animation of text, drawings, and still images. It allows bidirectional streaming of audio and video, and it can capture user input via mouse, keyboard, microphone and camera. Flash applications and animations can be programmed using the object-oriented language called ActionScript. Adobe Flash Professional is the most popular and user-friendly authoring tool for creating the Flash content, which also allows automation via the JavaScript Flash language (JSFL).Adobe Flash Player makes the Flash content accessible on various computer systems and devices and is available free of charge for common web browsers (as a plug-in) under a few of the major operating systems, some smartphones and tablets, and a few other electronic devices using Flash Lite.Virtually all browser plugins for video are free of charge and cross-platform, including Adobe's offering of Flash Video, which was first introduced with Flash version 6. Flash Video has been a popular choice for websites due to the large installed user base and programmability of Flash. In 2010, Apple publicly criticized Adobe Flash, including its implementation of video playback for not taking advantage of hardware acceleration, one reason Flash is not to be found on Apple's mobile devices. Soon after Apple's criticism, Adobe demoed and released a beta version of Flash 10.1, which takes advantage of GPU hardware acceleration even on a Mac. Flash 10.2 beta, released December 2010, adds hardware acceleration for the whole video rendering pipeline.Flash Audio is most commonly encoded in MP3 or AAC (Advanced Audio Coding) however it can also use ADPCM, Nellymoser (Nellymoser Asao Codec) and Speex audio codecs. Flash allows sample rates of 11, 22 and 44.1 kHz. It cannot have 48 kHz audio sample rate, which is the standard TV and DVD sample rate.The Adobe Flash Professional multimedia authoring program is used to create content for the Adobe Engagement Platform, such as web applications, games and movies, and content for mobile phones and other embedded devices.swfc is an open-source ActionScript 3.0 compiler which generates SWF files from script files, which includes SVG tags. It is currently the most complete alternative for building Flash content in Linux, despite being entirely script-based and not having a GUI.DISCLAIMER : The content of this app is powered by YouTube. We do not upload any of the videos to YouTube. column19: 传统武术是我国的国宝。它是一种力与美的高尚运动，而且是一门内含哲理与文化精神的艺术。传统武术，从体育的角度来讲，它是以功法为基础，以套路为载体，以技击为核心的民族传统体育项目。从肢体运动的角度来说，它是一门由力至劲，由肢体到精神的运动学问。用文化的眼光看，它是集思想性、哲理性、技击性、健身性、艺术性于一体的中华民族的非物质文化遗产。从艺术性来看，…... 展开

■About game Aliens are coming to earth. Protect your castle with your thunder machine. For activate machine, answer questions correctly. Some aliens are wearing costumes to hide from you. Be careful! If you can catch special aliens, you will get extra points. You can improve your geography skills while learning national flags of the world and you will have a lot of fun! The geography level is about middle school and junior high school. Kindergarten / preschool children at all ages, primary school and elementary school students can play 1st levels. Helps to improve memory and brain skills. Recommended by teachers, best for boys, girls and kids. ■45 levels with 5 stages ■How to play 1. Country name will display on thunder machine. 2. Please select correct national flag of the country from 3 buttons. 3. If your answer is correct, you can attack aliens and protect your castle. 4. If you mistake the answer, you lost a star. game will finish after lost all stars. 5. A special alien will appear in each level. If you attack these aliens, you can get extra points. ■Unlock all levels First 5 levels are free to play, unlock other levels for more fun. ■关于游戏 外星人来到地球。保护你的城堡与你的风头机。 对于激活的机器，正确地回答问题。 有些外国人都穿着戏服，从你隐藏。当心！ 如果你能赶上特殊的外星人，你会得到加分。 你可以改善你的地理技能的同时学习世界上的国旗，你将有很多的乐趣！ 地理水平约为初中和初中。幼儿园/学前班的孩子在所有年龄段，小学，小学生能玩1日的水平。有助于提高记忆力和大脑技能。 由教师推荐，最好的男孩，女孩和孩子们。 ■45个级别，5级 ■如何玩 1.国家名称将显示雷鸣机上。 2.请从3个按钮中选择国家正确的国旗。 3.如果你的答案是正确的，你可以攻击外国人和保护你的城堡。 4.如果你错了答案，你失去了一个明星。赛后将完成 失去了所有的星星。 5.特殊的外国人将出现在每个级别。如果攻击这些外星人，你 可以得到加分。 ■解锁所有级别 首先5个级别可以自由发挥，解锁其他级别更多的乐趣。

Sudoku is a puzzle, a small box containing 9x9 3x3 divided into large squares called blocks (see next diagram). The objective of Sudoku is to fill in separately for each row, column and block with the numbers 1 to 9, with each row, column and block must not have a repeat of the same number. Puzzle Sudoku begins with some small boxes filled with random numbers.Sudoku is a Japanese word which means "the numbers must be single" or "the numbers must occur only once". However, Sudoku is actually not from Japan, he became a very popular puzzle games in Japan when first introduced in 1984 in the country.Sudoku is the founder Howard Garns, a retired architect Americans who came from Indiana, created when he was 74 years old. Original name Sudoku is the Number Place, and first published by Dell Megazine in 1979. Howard Garns died in 1989, before he could see his creation become the playground of the most popular puzzle all over the world.How to play Sudoku Solver Free?To play Sudoku, you do not need to be an expert mathematics or calculations. It only requires logic, strategy and full concentration while playing.Sudoku puzzle there are several steps that gentle, moderate, challenging, complex and x-pert. New to be familiarized herself, to begin with gentle stage. Do not underestimate the ability of Sudoku, you might have a very tough time to solve it. One expert even Sudoku, sometimes takes hours to solve a Sudoku puzzle levels and x-pert complex.Sudoku rules are easy and quick. Each number can appear only once in each row, column and block. The composition of each of the numbers 1 through 9 in each row, column and block must not be in the correct sequence.Tip to play Sudoku- The accuracy of the numbers correct fill in the empty box is very important. If not, you will perform a series of mistakes that quest when filling other numbers in the empty boxes so on.- Do not try to fill the empty boxes guest manner. You need to think and make strategic decisions.- Make a Sudoku puzzle resolve this challenge as a fun session. If you get stuck, do not panic, tension and despair. Relax yourself, drink a cup of coffee, go take a shower, go out to the home page or walk to get a breath of fresh air. Then back to the game, this time Sharpen your focus and strategy.- Play Sudoku sometimes require the power of imagination, but you still need to adhere to the principles of the rule of this game.- To the beginner, try solve Sudoku puzzles on the first few gentle stage, until you can adjust to this game. Then, only then you should try and move to the next stage.

atisfied with the results of the free version, and you also need to know that the app helps you find out who is viewing your profile and photos among your friend's list and NOT others outside your friends list, and also please note that we will do our best to keep this service running but we hold no responsibility if the app was taken down by Facebook.*** In case you had any issues with the app please feel free to contact us through the support email where we will be more than happy to help you or refund you if applicable.

Want an easy way to help organise your life and make the best use of your valuable time! WotsNext is here to help you do just that. An easy to use app that allows you to quickly add a task but has flexible and powerful features to keep you on top of your life. FEATURES IN FREE VERSON: * Ad free * Quick and easy to create, edit and mark tasks off * Assign user-defined categories to tasks * Assign priorities to tasks * Repeat tasks when completed - daily, weekly or monthly * Set alarms to notify you when tasks are due, including the ability to set two alarms for a given task * Re-occurring alarm notifications until cleared * Daily notifications of your day’s tasks * Search for tasks and calendar events * Link a contact to a task that can be opened from the list * Entered locations can be displayed in Google Maps * Quick filters to allow you to quickly filter the task list to easy see what’s coming up * Swipe task to set it complete * Auto-deletion of completed tasks * Snooze or set a task to complete from Alarm Notification (Android 4.1+) * Daily backup of all your data to SD Card or even your Cloud storage with WotsNext Plus * Support for tablets with landscape views * 6 Color themes to choose from * Home Screen widgets to suit all versions of Android. A new version takes advantage of features in new Android versions. For Android 4.2+ users, the widget can be placed on the Lock Screen FEATURES IN PLUS (PAID) VERSION: * View tasks by day, week or month with the Calendar Views * Ability to view two days in Day Calendar View in landscape mode on 10" tablets and most 7" newer tabets * Ability to view two weeks in Week Calendar View in landscape mode on 10" tablets and most 7" newer tabets * Display calendar events stored on your device’s Google Calendar * Export tasks in CSV or HTML formats for viewing and printing * Synchronize your tasks and categories with all your devices running WotsNext Plus * Access your Cloud storage to export files, sync devices and backup your data to. IVONA - The leader in realistic, natural-sounding & accurate TTS voices for your Android device. No more robotic, sythesized voices. IVONA for Android replaces the synthesized text-to-speech (TTS) voices currently available on your Android device with more natural sounding, accurate & easy-to-understand voices. Select from 13 different languages to find the one best suited for you. Easy to install one or several different voices! IVONA is compatible with many of your favorite Android applications. With IVONA, enjoy: ☆ Turn-by-turn voice navigation so you can keep your eyes on the road (e.g. Google Maps) ☆ Have your ebooks naturally read aloud to you (e.g. Moon+ Reader Pro) ☆ Listen to online content, articles, PDF documents & RSS feeds (e.g. Pocket, ezPDF Reader, gReader) ☆ Change the voice on your virtual assistant (e.g. Jeannie, iris, Skyvi) Plus: ☆ Enjoy improved accessibility (e.g. TalkBack built-into Android) ☆ Increase your productivity (e.g. Driving Mode built-into Android) Key features include: • BrightVoice technology provides lifelike, expressive reading of all your text • Clear & easy-to-understand sound – even in noisy environments • A rapidly expanding portfolio of award-winning voices available in multiple languages, accents & genders • Easy-to-install & use with automatic, free updates Get started in 4 easy steps: 1. Install IVONA Text-to-Speech HQ to your Android device from the Google Play store 2. Select & install your preferred language and voice(s) from the Google Play store 3. Once downloaded, launch the IVONA app to complete your installation 4. Finally, Select IVONA TTS Engine as your default engine by navigating to Android Settings Now you’re ready to experience world-class IVONA Text-to-Speech & IVONA voices on your favorite text-to-speech enabled Android apps. column19: 猜字谜是汉民族特有的一种语言文化现象，它主要根据方块汉字笔画繁复、偏旁相对独立、结构组合多变的特点，运用离合、增损、象形、会意等多种方式来进行，显得既有趣味，又有知识内涵。 把玩疯狂猜字游戏的8大好处： 1、开发智商(聪明也要靠训练哦) 2、激活脑细胞，开发右脑(汉字得天独厚的优势、其他语言文字无法比拟) 3、丰富想象力 4、防止老年性痴呆 5、祖国传统文化精髓潜移默化的熏陶 6、拓展知识面(天南海北、传奇典故都有涉及) 7、培养幽默感(也许你也能成为开心果的~~) 8、提高个人文学素养 学渣学霸均可一试，来体验一下这种高层次的文学娱乐活动吧~~~~

All graphics in this game are generated by programs and this is why the size of the installation package is less than 1M. In this game, you are to compose several words using given RANDOM letters. Try to minimize the number of unused letters which costs life points. To compose words is easy while to achieve the minimization is much harder. Think carefully and try different plans. Varieties of special cards can be discovered and obtained. The longer words are composed, the better cards are obtained. To be a skillful player, a good understanding of the usage of special cards is required. To get further instructions, see cards wiki in app. 由程序生成在这场比赛中所有的图形，这就是为什么在安装包的大小小于1M。 在这个游戏中，你是用给定的随机字母组成几个单词。尽量减少花费的生活点的未使用的字母数。撰写话很容易，同时实现最小化是更难。仔细一想，并尝试不同的计划。 特殊卡种可以被发现和得到。较长的单词组成，更好的卡获得。要成为一个熟练的玩家，特殊卡的使用有很好的了解是必需的。 为了获得进一步的说明，请参阅应用程序卡的wiki。

Boys and girls, welcome to Libii Hospital, the funnest medical treatment game ever!!! Here you can turn yourself into a professional doctor, operate your own clinic and cure different kinds of patients with various diseases! Libii Hospital occupies a complete building, but each floor has the totally different department and function. Meanwhile, there are plenty of medical instruments, as well as the ambulance, medical helicopter, and a pretty nurse, the only character we need now is an amazing doctor, that’s you! Don’t hesitate any more, dear friends, the patients need you urgently, come to join us, and help all of them! We promise, you’ll absolutely have a brand-new experience, for this is an excellent and unique medical treatment game! How To Play: Open the game, click Play to start , in this game you should slide up and down to arrive different floor. After you enter the game, patients have already been sitting in the lobby and waiting for you, here you can choose their favorite candies to them. Then you can choose to come different floor to cure different patients, they may have various diseases throughout the body, some are internal while some are external, some are heavy while some are tiny. You may need to check the patients’ blood, or use X-Ray machine to scan and examine their bodies, you need check the healthy status of the patients’ organs by yourself, then you can start to cure the patient according to the nurse’s voice prompts or with her help. Besides treating the patients’ multiple diseases, you can also manage and arrange the medical instruments in your treatment rooms, make them neat and in order. Therefore, when you feel boring of treating illness, you might as well tap the cabinet or toolbox to see whether you can do something different, for there are always many surprises waiting for you to find out in Libii Games!!! Features: · 5 kinds of patients to choose, such as human beings, vampire, dinosaur, monster · 31 different mini games you can play in this app · Various medical instruments to use · Multiple themes of the treatment room to see · Medical vehicles such as ambulance and helicopter to see Need You Know: This app is totally free to download and play, some basic items are also free to use, but some additional items need you to purchase and pay to unlock. Therefore, if you do not want to use these items, please turn off the in-app purchase in your settings. Navigate the unprecedented global wave of urbanization with Urban World. Compare GDP, population and household income for more than 2,600 cities worldwide. Track the earth’s shifting economic center of gravity from 1 CE to 2025. Discover surprising facts and share them via Facebook or Twitter. The growth of cities in emerging markets is driving the most significant economic transformation in history. Urban World offers a sense of how economic power will move as this unprecedented urban expansion takes place. By 2025, the annual consumption of citizens in these emerging markets will reach $30 trillion and the GDP of these markets will exceed that of developed countries. China’s economy is changing at ten times the speed of the British Industrial Revolution—which was itself a turning point in the history of the world—and at 100 times the scale. Comprehending the sheer scale and sweeping nature of this urban transformation is difficult. Urban World can help, by presenting an interactive economic and demographic map of the evolving urban landscape. • Spin the globe, and pinch to zoom in on individual countries and cities and compare their population, household incomes, or GDP side-by-side. • Use the search function to move quickly to a specific city, country, or region. • Explore GDP from 1 CE to 2025 and view the shift in the world’s economic center of gravity over that same time period. Urban World is based on more than five years of research by the McKinsey Global Institute (MGI), the business and economics research arm of McKinsey, the global management consultancy. 导航前所未有的全球城市世界城市化浪潮。比较GDP，人口和家庭收入为全球超过2600个城市。 1 CE追踪地球上的经济重心转移到2025年。发现令人吃惊的事实，他们通过Facebook或Twitter分享。 在新兴市场城市的增长是推动历史上最重要的经济转型。世界城市提供了一个前所未有的城市扩张，因为这发生的经济实力如何将移动感。 到2025年，公民在这些新兴市场的年消费量将达到30万亿美元，这些市场的国内生产总值将超过发达国家。中国的经济正在改变速度十倍于英国工业革命本身就是一个转折点，在历史的世界，在100倍的规模。 理解庞大的规模和性质席卷这个城市的转型是困难的。可以帮助城市世界，呈现一个交互式地图的经济和人口的不断变化的城市景观。 旋转地球，捏放大，对个别国家和城市，并比较他们的人口，家庭收入，或GDP的侧端。 •使用搜索功能，快速移动到一个特定的城市，国家或地区。 •探索1 CE到2025年，国内生产总值超过同一时期在世界经济重心转移。 城市世界是基于超过五年的研究，麦肯锡全球研究院（MGI），商业和经济研究部门，全球管理咨询公司麦肯锡。

到海外升学并不是草率的决定,而是需要经过详尽的数据搜集及深思熟虑的计划。现今信息发达,同学及家长要搜集留学的数据并不困难。但网上数据繁多,要找到详尽而客观的分析和建议亦不容易。 所以香港教育信息网─海外升学辅导组每年均会更新出版《海外升学指南》,为有意到海外留学的学生及家长提供多方面的实用数据。2013 – 2014的新版经已推出,今年更设有Andriod version免费download!丰富内容如下: 海外升学顾问服务 海外升学Step by Step 大学衔接班课程 英、澳、美、加大学申请指南 副学位同学的留学选择 升读海外中学 延续及职业专科学院 热门专业学科 英国- 院校专访 澳洲- 院校专访 加拿大- 院校专访 美国 - 院校专访 迎接留学生活 学生专访 留学生心声 出发前准备: 收拾行李 申办学生签证须知 海外院校的建议 院校探访 活动回顾 香港教育信息网于1996年成立,是香港最早开发的海外升学进修信息网络。「海外升学辅导组」的功能是为同学及家长提供计划、辅导、申请、出发前准备及开课后支持五方面的个人化海外升学顾问服务。 地址: 香港湾仔轩尼诗道48-62 号上海实业大厦901室 电话: (852) 2272 2800 传真: (852) 2272 2828 电邮: ieu@education.com.hk 网址: www.education.com.hk facebook: www.facebook.com/hongkongeducationweb

Would you like to control your digital media at home with just one single device? With the Sitecom Media Controllerl you can easily manage your movies, photos or music from a DLNA (UPnP) device present in your wireless home network. The Sitecom Media Controller allows you to search for media in all DLNA (UPnP) servers, such as a NAS-server or computer, and to play it on your Android device or on any DLNA (UPnP) certified player such as the Sitecom TV Media Player. The Sitecom Media Controller has the following features: - Automatically detects DLNA (UPnP) certified servers and players at home - Allows you to browse the content in an extremely easy and simple way - Play multiple media at the same time on different players - Supports multitasking; you can continue to play music while using a different application - "Cover flow" functionality to preview your photos or your album cover arts Easily turn your Android device into a remote control that allows you to control your digital media in all the rooms of your home with just a push on the button. What is DLNA? DLNA (UPnP) is short for Digital Living Network Alliance, and defines a standard for easily recognizing movies, photos, music and other media stored within your network. With which devices does the Sitecom Media Controller work? DLNA (UPnP) servers, like for example the MD-253 Sitecom Home Storage Center (NAS), can without any setup or configuration stream media to DLNA (UPnP) certified players such as the Sitecom TV Media Player or DLNA (UPnP) TVs. In addition, Windows Media Player 12 is both a DLNA (UPnP) server and compliant player. This means you can stream media from/to your Windows PC without any configuration. Activate this feature by clicking “Allow remote control of my Player” and “Automatically allow devices to play my media...” (under Library->Stream). How does the Sitecom Media Controller work? 1. An overview of DLNA certified media providers, such as NAS-servers and computers, is presented 2. Select the media provider that you want to access 3. Browse through your media files 4. Select the file that you want to play 5. An overview of DLNA certified network devices that can play media, such as media players, computers and DLNA TV's, is given 6. Select the device that you want to use to play the file. Play the file on your Android device or any DLNA certified device within your network. If there are no DLNA certified devices in your network, the file is automatically played on your Android device
