UltraTools Mobile for Android includes fourteen useful tools for DNS, website, and network administration. Turn your Android mobile device into a true network-troubleshooting device. Get the most useful tools from a single application brought to you by Neustar UltraDNS, the industry leader in Managed DNS. Domain Health Report Check the health of your DNS configuration from your smartphone. The Domain Health Report tool evaluates a domain configuration with over seventy tests in nine different categories, and shows you what can be changed to optimize your domain. Visual Traceroute Check the route between your mobile device to a server — both over the network and around the world! The Visual Traceroute tool uses traceroute information and GeoIP data to give you a better sense of the route and physical distance that packets travel over the network from you to the server. DNS Lookup Query any domain nameserver for information from your phone or tablet! You may even select the type of query. The DNS Lookup tool gives you a way to check DNS answers over the mobile or WiFi network so that you can understand what your users may be experiencing with your DNS. WHOIS Lookup Check DNS domain registration and owner information from the datacenter or conference room — without having to open a laptop. The WHOIS Lookup tool provides a quick way to query WHOIS data from multiple providers. SSL Examination Is the SSL certificate of a website present — or more importantly, is it valid? Check right from your phone or tablet with the SSL Examination tool. DNS Speed Test Does your website seem a little slow? Use the DNS Speed Test to check the response time for DNS queries directly from your mobile device — and show the database team that it's their problem, not DNS. Ping Is the server up? Is the IP address being used? Now with the Ping tool, you can check from anywhere your mobile device has connectivity. GeoIP Lookup: Where in the world is that IP address hosted? The GeoIP Lookup tool will show you the location information and plot the results on Google Maps. RBL Lookup: Are your mail servers listed on real-time black lists (RBL)? Now you can check & remove them easily right from your mobile device with the RBL Lookup tool. Port Scanner: Do you know which TCP ports are open on your network connected servers? The Port Scanner tool performs a quick check for common services — and custom ports. Now you can check if a network service is available (or if you should turn it off). Connection Speed: Does the network seem slow to you? Check — and compare — network download and upload speeds from your device over whichever network you may be connected to with the Connection Speed tool. IPv4 to IPv6 converter: Planning to support IPv6 on your network? If you have any transition strategy, you’ll want to know the IPv6 equivalent of IPv4 addresses. You can convert addresses conveniently with the IPv4 to IPv6 Conversion tool IPv6 Compatibility: Can you reach a domain using IPv6 addressing? Find out if your domain is ready for IPv6 with the IPv6 Compatibility tool. Device Information: The Device Information tool is a single location for critical information about your mobile device hardware, operating system and connected networks. With it, you no longer need to hunt through the device menus, searching for hard to find device or connection information.

Timelapse Calc is a calculator for dslr time-lapse shootings. The app calculates for example the number of required images for a given sequence length. To plan the shoot, you can calculate the duration of the shooting session by the interval, the desired clip length and frame rate. Features: + Comes now with the new Android 5 "Material" Theme + Calculate the number of images + Calculate the interval + Calculate the amount of data + Calculate the record duration + Calculate the clip length + Calculate the slider steps + For devices with flashlight a torch is available + Preferences for file size, sliderlength, framerate and the unit of length + + + Notes on the app permissions + + + The app needs permission for accessing the camera flashlight led. column4: 広岛の交通系ICカード Reader
column19: 広岛(と各地)の交通系ICカード(と电子マネー)の残额と利用履歴を表示するアプリです。 Android2.3.3以降で、NFCカードリーダーを内蔵している端末（スマートフォン、タブレット）で动作します。 NFCに対応していない端末は、ICカードを読めないため、デモンストレーション用のデータを表示します(デモモード)。 PASPYに加えて同じエリアで利用できるICOCAの残额・履歴も表示できます。 ICOCAと互换のSuica、Kitaca、SMART ICOCA、PASPMO、nimoca、SUGOCAについても表示できることを确认しました。 　 広岛の隣県である四国香川県のIruCaの残额・履歴を表示できます。 四国爱媛県のICい～カード、四国高知県のですかを読めます(表示できる駅名は、データ登录・更新オプションで追加できます)。 札幌地下鉄のSAPICAの残额、残ポイント、履歴を表示できます。 九州の长崎スマートカード、ひまわりバスカードを読めます(停留所名は、データ登录・更新オプションで追加できます)。 Rapica、いわさきICカードも読めますが、一部の停留所名は表示できません。 　 电子マネー（nanaco, WAON, Edy）の残额と履歴を表示できます。 おサイフケータイのモバイルい～カード、モバイルSuica、nanacoモバイル、WAONモバイル、Edyアプリ、モバイル长崎スマートカードの残额と履歴を表示できます。 利用履歴をファイルまたはクリップボードに出力できます。 他のアプリから机能部品として利用できます。ActivityまたはServiceとして呼び出すことが出来ます。 详细は别途公开するサンプルアプリ（TestActivity および TestService）を参照下さい。 设置でICカードを検知してアプリ起动する机能をon/offできます。 offの场合、カードをかざしてもアプリ起动しません。アプリアイコンを选択して起动した后、カードをかざすと読み取ります。 アプリアイコンを选択して起动した场合、Android 4.4以降ならNFC Reader Modeを使用します。 カードの种类をタイトル栏に表示します（PASPY, ひろぎんPASPY, ICOCAなど 等）。 おサイフケータイの场合、タイトル栏にはおサイフケータイと表示して、个々の名称は别途表示します。 它是一个显示广岛运输系统的IC卡（和周围）（和电子货币）的平衡和使用历史的应用进程。   在Android2.3.3后，将工作，其具有内置NFC读卡器（智能电话，平板电脑）在终端上。 不支持NFC，因为你无法读取IC卡，并为演示（演示模式）显示的数据终端。   ICOCA平衡 - 历史，可以用在同一个区域，除了PASPY也可以显示。 ICOCA和兼容的Suica卡，证实Kitaca，SMART ICOCA，PASPMO，nimoca，你也可以看到SUGOCA。 我可以看到四国的IruCa平衡的历史，香川县是广岛的邻近县。 四国爱媛县IC电子贺卡，你读的是高知县四国（可显示的站名，您可以添加在数据登记和更新选项）。 平衡札幌地铁SAPICA，剩下的一点，我可以查看历史记录。 九州长崎智能卡，就可以读取向日葵公交卡（站名，可以在数据登记和更新选项添加​​）。 Rapica，你也可以阅读岩崎IC卡，但有些站名无法显示。 电子货币（nanaco，WAON，伊迪）我可以显示的平衡和历史。 手机钱包手机有卡，移动Suica卡，nanaco移动，WAON移动，伊迪的应用进程，我可以显示移动长崎智能卡余额和历史。   您可以输出的使用历史文档或复制到剪贴板。 我可以从其他应用进程的功能组件。您可以根据活动或服务调用。 请参见单独发布的示例应用进程（TestActivity和TestService的）了解更多信息。   可以打开/关闭，通过检测该组中的IC卡，以启动应用进程的能力。 在关闭的情况下，并没有应用进程开始通过持有该卡。在启动通过选择应用进程的图标，你可以阅读它，持有该卡。 如果你开始选择应用进程的图标，你可以使用NFC阅读器模式，如果Android的4.4或更高版本。   显示卡中的标题栏（PASPY，Hirogin PASPY，如ICOCA等）的类型。 在手机钱包，在标题领域通过显示一个手机钱包，个人名义投注显示的情况。

猴子历险记是一款很酷的奔跑和跳跃的冒险游戏。 猴子是一个勇敢，敏捷和可爱的猴子，在一个美丽的一天，他走进丛林摘香蕉， 丛林充满了危险，他需要你的帮助来走出，你想加入他开始在丛林中令人兴奋的冒险？ 12345GO. ***如何玩*** 1.点击屏幕向上箭头让猴子跳、点击左/右箭头移动。 2.躲避障碍物，收集所有的香蕉和运行，而不被愤怒的主人抓住。 3.运行并完成所有的水平与三颗星，到达猴子的家园。 ***产品特点*** 1.具有良好轻松的音乐和声音效果。 2.具有挑战性和趣味性的冒险世界。 3.流畅的控制和美丽的动画。

一款非常美观易用的「短信验证码助手」轻App，可以在验证码短信来临的时，自动识别验证码，悬浮并且自动复制到剪切板，不用记忆不用输入，只要长按粘贴即可输入验证码。 它可以在手机接收到验证码短信的时候，自动浮现验证码，并且自动复制验证码到用户的剪切板。当用户接收到短信验证码，用户只要长按验证码的输入框，粘贴验证码即可。 除此之外，我们还可以让用户批量删除无用验证码短信，帮助用户反向推理出绑定了哪些业务。 我们做得非常轻，也秉承了一贯的好设计和用户友好，Material Design，在闲时它不会自启动、不会偷跑流量、不会占用任何内存(这些点都欢迎大家进行各种监督、抓包测试)。

Decibel Calculator. Translate ratios into decibel (dB) and back. There are two types of translations: 10*log(P/P0) and 20*log(U/U0). From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia: "A decibel (dB) is one tenth of a bel (B), i.e. 1B = 10dB. The bel is the logarithm of the ratio between two power quantities of 10:1, and between two field quantities in the ratio. A field quantity is a quantity such as voltage, current, sound pressure, electric field strength, velocity and charge density, the square of which in linear systems is proportional to power. A power quantity is a power or a quantity directly proportional to power, e.g. energy density, acoustic intensity and luminous intensity. The calculation of the ratio in decibels varies depending on whether the quantity being measured is a power quantity or a field quantity. Two signals that differ by one decibel have a power ratio of 1.258925411794167 and an amplitude ratio of 1.122018454301963." 分贝计算器。 转化率成分贝（dB）和背部。 有两种类型的翻译： 10 *日志（P / P0）和20 *日志（U / U0）。 维基百科，自由的百科全书： “一个分贝（dB）是一个贝尔（B），即1B =10分贝的十分之一的贝尔是两个功率量10之间的比的对数：1，和两个场量之间的比率的字段数量是一个数量，如电压，电流，声压，电场强度，速度和电荷密度，方形其中线性系统的正比于功率。的功率量是一个功率或正比于功率的量，如能量密度，声强和发光强度。 以分贝之比的计算取决于被测量的数量是否是一个功率量或场数量。 两个信号相差一个分贝有1.258925411794167的功率比和1.122018454301963振幅比“。

AUTOMEMO iti ofera si o multime de functii noi, de tip "MEMO" care au asociate "ALERTE", utile pentru gestionarea tuturor grijilor legate de masina, motocicleta ..si nu numai. - MEMO-urile pot fi: "nr. masina", "nr. motocicleta" dar si "facturi casa" ori "rate banca"; -La fiecare MEMO poti crea mai multe ALERTE (RCA, ITP, CASCO, Rovigneta, respectiv gaz, apa, curent electric, ori ipoteca, credit personal, etc.); - MEMO-urile pentru masini sau motociclete au deja predefinite o serie de ALERTE uzuale; Poti seta orice alta alerta care te ajuta sa nu uiti o multime de lucruri din viata ta, pe care le ai de facut de maine incolo. Pentru fiecare, iti reamintim cu un SMS GRATUIT sau cu email. AUTOMEMO te mai ajuta cu ceva: iti poti reinnoi RCA, inaintea expirarii, direct de pe telefonul mobil: introduci datele masinii (din certificatul de inmatriculare) iar aplicatia te conduce catre o lista de oferte cu discount, din care poti alege cea mai convenabila RCA. VAT Calculator allows you to calculate the VAT and the gross amount including VAT from a percentage and a net amount excluding VAT, you can also find the net amount from an amount including this tax and a rate applicable for your country, finally you can find the net amount and the gross amount from a value-added tax amount. By pressing the calculator icon, the calculator will appear and you can calculate, then you will see two displays for seeing the result either with your own formatting numeric which you can edit from the settings or without formatting numeric but with your calculating details. It enables you to manage your country's rates by pressing the plus button, you can add more custom percentages easily or delete it. Settings menu allows to change the background color, to edit the format number, to keep your screen on, to make buttons vibrating according to the user's choice... and to reset. The description of Polly. Your Parking Fairy פולי היא פיית חניה אורבאנית שמכירה את כל הרחובות ,החניונים, השלטים והסודות הקטנים של העיר הגדולה. היא פה כדי לעזור לך למצוא חניה בדרך שאתה רוצה. מתוך בחירה, וחסכון של זמן, כסף והרבה עצבים. כן, רק צריך להקיש כתובת יעד, ופולי תדאג לשאר. יש חניות שרק פיות מכירות ... פולי מכירה את כל רחובות העיר, ויודעת איפה למצוא חניות... כשמגיעים לאזור בו קשה למצוא חניה, קוראים לה - והיא לוקחת אתכם דרך רחובות אלו. במקרים נדירים, אפילו פיות כמו פולי לא מצליחות למצוא עבורנו חניית רחוב. עזרו לפולי והגדירו את החניון אליו תרצו להגיע, במקרים הנדירים בהם הקסם פג... פולי מנסה לתת לך הכל : - מידע על כל אפשרויות החניה - מסלולי ניווט מיוחדים למציאת חנייה ברחוב - מחיר וזמינות חניונים - חישוב מרחק וזמן הליכה מהחניה ליעד - תזכורות יומן להגעה לפגישות בזמן, המאפשרות שיגור השירות בלחיצה קטנה אחת! - שילוט חניית רחוב בתוך האפליקציה (פולי מכירה את כל השלטים בעיר..) - התראות על מגבלות חנייה - תזכורות למיקום הרכב - מסלולי הליכה רגליים ליעד וחזרה למכונית בכוחה של פולי לעזור כבר עכשיו ומזה היא מתפרנסת ( כך היא מקבלת את אבקת הכוכבים שלה ) , אבל היא גם תשמח ללמוד וכאן אתם נכנסים לתמונה - פולי השאירה לכם הרבה מקום כדי שתעדכנו אותה אודות מידע שגוי או חניונים מלאים ועוד ועוד. תזכרו , פולי היא פיה והיא בת 420 שנים , וזה מאוד צעיר בשנים של פיות.....עם פולי חניות מתחילות להתגשם. Polly is an urban parking Fairy. It knows about all streets, parking lots, parking signs and little secrets of the big city... She’s here to help you find parking - the way you want it. She saves you time, money and a lot of nerves. Yeah, tell her where your meeting point is and don’t worry about the rest. When you get to the area where it's hard to find parking, ask her for assistance - and she will vocally navigate you, turn-by-turn, via the powdered path of cheap, nearby on-street parking... In rare cases, even fairy like Polly cannot find on-street parking. Polly will lead you to the parking lot choice, where you wish to reach, in those rare cases where the magic disappears... Polly tries to give you everything: - Information on all parking options - Special navigation paths to find on street parking - Price and availability of parking lots - Calendar notifications that ensure you get there on time, and for launching the service with one simple click! - The calculation of distance and time walking from the parking destination - Street parking signage within the app (Polly knows all the signs in the city ...) - Alerts about parking restrictions - Reminders of vehicle location - Walking navigation route to destination and back to the car Polly’s power is here for you from day one (that’s how she gets her powder), but she will be happy to keep learning and this is where you come in – Polly is leaving you plenty of room to update her on disinformation, parking lots availability, and much more. Remember, Polly is 420 years old, which is very early for fairies..... With Polly ,parking is not wishful thinking…..
